tty according to the user&#39;s ability (recommended strength: 4oz)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/1_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/1_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/1_3.jpg,assets/products_image/650/1_4.jpg,assets/products_image/650/1_5.jpg', 1, '2023-04-15 18:30:05', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
