(9, 1, 0, 'SM5', '110', '專注及小肌肉蓋印練習本', 'Stamping Exercise Booklet', '45.00', 2.86, '<p>每天做幾分鐘的桌面練習，能讓孩子學習安坐和專注。此蓋印練習可以提升孩子的專注丶視覺追蹤丶視覺感知能力丶手眼協調和手指力量。訓練小肌肉外，同時學習數字和英文字。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>套裝包括：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. 24 頁全彩練習本 (尺寸30x21cm)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. 加送 1 個動物印章 （隨機款式）&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：幼稚園學童 &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>A few minutes of tabletop exercises each day will help your child learn to sit still and concentrate. This stamping exercise improves attention, visual tracking, visual perception, eye-hand coordination and finger strength. It trains small hand muscles and teaches children numbers and English words.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Set includes:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. 24-page colour-printed exercise booklet (size 30x21cm)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. 1 animal stamp for free (type of animal sent in random)&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children in kindergarten</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/9_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/9_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/9_3.jpg,assets/products_image/650/9_4.jpg', 1, '2023-04-15 19:14:31', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(10, 1, 0, 'SM6', '60', '髮型創造小手工', 'Be a Hairdresser Handcraft Kit', '25.00', 6.06, '<p>剪、撕、揉、搓...&nbsp; 為不同的家庭成員創造出天馬行空的髮型！</p>\r\n\r\n<p>教材可以訓練孩子的手指遠端控制、靈活性、手眼協調等，</p>\r\n\r\n<p>還可以提供手指豐富的觸感刺激。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>手工套裝包括：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. 4 張工作紙 共7款人物造型</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. 300張5cm彩色手揉紙</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. 美國ELMER&#39;S無毒紫色漿糊筆6g一支</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3歲-初小學童 &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Create hairstyles for different family members by cutting, tearing, kneading, rubbing ...&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Train children&#39;s remote finger control, dexterity, eye-hand coordination, etc and</p>\r\n\r\n<p>provide plenty of tactile stimulation for the fingers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The handcraft kit includes:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. 4 worksheets with 7 characters</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. 300 sheets of 5cm coloured kneaded paper</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. 1 ELMER&#39;S non-toxic purple glue pen 6g</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old - year 3 primary school children</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/10_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/10_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/10_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-15 19:16:34', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(11, 1, 0, 'SM7', '85', '刮刮聖誕卡遊戲套裝 ', 'Christmas Scratch Card Set', '45.00', 6.20, '<p>Wayshk 的聖誕教材，以人手組合製作。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>在感受節日氣氛同時，讓孩子訓練手指力量。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>刮刮刮，刮出驚喜～不知道下一個聖誕波波是什麼顏色的呢？</p>\r\n\r\n<p>更可以自行寫上祝福字句，貼上附送的刮刮貼紙，再送给朋友，</p>\r\n\r\n<p>分享刮刮之樂。使用小鏟子/硬幣/ 間尺/指甲均可刮掉塗層。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>套裝包括 ：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. 三款約A4 size 刮刮遊戲聖誕卡</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. 兩款約A5 size 聖誕卡 （需自行剪開）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. 心型刮刮貼紙x2 （自行寫上祝福句子後貼上）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. 刮刮卡專用小鏟子</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>適合： 3歲-初小學童使用</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Christmas scratch card set designed by Wayshk&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Improve children&rsquo;s finger strength while celebrating Christmas</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Scratch for surprises - wonder what colour the next Christmas bauble will be</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can even write Christmas wishes and put the included scratch stickers on the scratch card to send to your friends to share the joy of scratching</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Simply use a scraper/ coin/ ruler/ fingernail can scratch away the black film to reveal the beautiful colourful patterns underneath</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Set includes:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. 3 x approx. A4 size Christmas scratch cards</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. 2 x A5 size Christmas cards (to be cut out by yourself)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Heart-shaped scratch-off stickers x 2 (write your own message and stick it on the cards)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. Scratching card scraper</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old - year 3 primary school children</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/11_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/11_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-15 19:18:18', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(12, 1, 0, 'SM8', '180', '蠟繩交通工具遊戲包 ', 'Wikki Stix Transportation Game Set', '75.00', 11.71, '<p>Wikki Stix 蠟繩安全無毒， 美國製造的蠟繩符合兒童安全法規。打了蠟的紗線，只要用手指輕輕按壓，就可以粘在光滑的表面上或互相黏合，沒有漿糊膠水，非常整潔。可以做成各種2D或3D的造型。除了提供觸感刺激，也可以訓練雙手及手眼協調、手指靈活性。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>套裝包括：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. 8 張A4 雙面遊戲卡 （包括交通工具連線遊戲/建造馬路遊戲）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. 24條15cm Wikki Stix 蠟繩</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. 迷你車一架</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. 無痕膠2張（可以貼在牆壁/門上使用教材）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>使用方法：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 利用蠟繩做連線遊戲 【兩種難度 1-10/1-20連點點】</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 可以做成不同道路，控制車子移動到達不同地方</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 做出不同3D圖案，自由玩耍</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：幼稚園-初小學童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Wikki Stix are made of hand-knitting yarn enhanced with a microcrystalline, food-grade non-toxic wax and made in the USA which conforms to child safety standards. Just press them down with light fingertip pressure on any smooth surface and they will stick to each other without using any glue. They can be used in making different 2D or 3D patterns. They are perfect for training bilateral hand or eye-hand coordination and finger dexterity apart from providing tactile stimulation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Set includes:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. 8 x A4 double-sided game cards (including connect the dots with transport/ road building game)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. 24 x 15cm Wikki Stix&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. One mini car</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. 2 x damage-free adhesive tape (can stick to walls/doors when playing the game)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>How to play:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Connect the dots game [two levels of difficulty 1-10/1-20 with dots].</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Build different roads and control the car to reach different places</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Make different 3D patterns&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: Kindergarten - Year 3 primary school children</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/12_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/12_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/12_3.jpg,assets/products_image/650/12_4.jpg,assets/products_image/650/12_5.jpg,assets/products_image/650/12_6.jpg', 1, '2023-04-15 19:22:15', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(13, 1, 0, 'SM10', '25', '打孔火車圖卡', 'Picture Cards (train)', '25.00', 15.00, '<p>Wayshk 自家人手製作火車圖卡 （一套8張）。配搭圖形扣環/長型扣環一同使用，從趣味遊戲中訓練手眼協調、雙手協調及手指靈活性。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>示範影片： https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mV3vIFLexKE</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：幼稚園學童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Picture cards with train patterns made by Wayshk (set of 8). Cards to be used with circular or oval shaped rings to develop eye-hand coordination, bilateral hand coordination and finger dexterity through games.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Demonstration video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mV3vIFLexKE</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children in kindergarten</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/13_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/13_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-15 19:23:39', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(14, 2, 0, 'PU2Y', '75', '黃色/超軟 治療膠 2oz', '2oz Theraputty (Yellow/Extra soft)', '58.00', 18.40, '<p>Alimed品牌2oz治療膠， 由美國製造，共有四種阻力度，為不同程度手抓力的使用者而設。 透過擠壓、捏、拉伸或扭動治療膠，可以有效增強手部肌肉力量，改善小肌肉技巧及減輕手部壓力。 治療膠物料不含麩質、乳膠和酪蛋白，且不含毒性，安全可靠，不論任何年齡都可安心使用。 提供方便開合和收藏的獨立盒裝治療膠，方便使用者在家中使用。</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>注意：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* 治療膠表面有油份為正常現象，第一次使用時搓勻即可</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* 每次使用治療膠前請徹底清潔雙手，避免沾染塵埃</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* 避免使用酒精清潔/使用酒精搓手液後立即觸碰治療膠，會導致染色</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* 避免穿著毛衣/於地毯上使用治療膠，以免粘著</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* 使用者可向物理治療師／職業治療師查詢適合的治療膠硬度及容量。</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>以下資料 僅供參考：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>幼兒  2oz 黃色（超軟）/4oz 黃色 （超軟）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>幼稚園初班/中班   4oz 黃色（超軟）/ 2oz 紅 (軟) / 4oz紅 (軟)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>幼稚園高班學童/初小學生  2oz  綠 (中)/4oz 綠 (中)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>小學生  4oz  綠 (中)/ 2oz  藍 (硬）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>中學生/成人 4oz 藍 (硬）</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>玩法介紹：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>https://youtu.be/O15JHjUyV3M </p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n', '<p>Alimed 2oz Theraputty is made in the USA. Available in four resistance levels and is designed for users with different levels of hand grip. It can be used to strengthen hand muscles, improve dexterity and reduce stress on the hands by doing hand exercises in squeezing, stretching or twisting the theraputty. The putty is gluten, latex and casein free and non-toxic, making it safe for use at all ages. Each putty is also packed in an individual box for convenient use and storage&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>at home.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Precautions:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Oil on the surface of the putty is normal and should be rubbed in during first time use</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Wash hands before use to prevent soiling&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Avoid cleaning with alcohol or using the theraputty immediately after using alcohol-based hand rubs as this may cause staining</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Avoid wearing jumpers / using the putty on carpets as it can stick to clothing and carpets</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Users should consult their physiotherapist/occupational therapist for the appropriate resistance level and size of putty</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The following information is for reference only:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Preschool toddlers: 2oz yellow (extra soft) / 4oz yellow (extra soft)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kindergarten year 1/2: 4oz yellow (super soft) / 2oz red (soft) / 4oz red (soft)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kindergarten year 3 / Primary school students up to year 3 : 2oz Green (Medium) / 4oz Green (Medium)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Primary school Students: 4oz Green (Medium) / 2oz Blue (Hard)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Secondary school students / Adults: 4oz Blue (Hard)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Demonstration of putty exercise:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>https://youtu.be/O15JHjUyV3M</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/14_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/14_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/14_3.jpg,assets/products_image/650/14_4.jpg,assets/products_image/650/14_5.jpg', 1, '2023-04-15 19:37:24', '2023-04-15 19:45:26'),
(15, 2, 0, 'PU2R', '75', '紅色/軟 治療膠 2oz', '2oz Theraputty (Red /Soft)', '58.00', 19.32, '<p>Alimed品牌2oz治療膠， 由美國製造，共有四種阻力度，為不同程度手抓力的使用者而設。 透過擠壓、捏、拉伸或扭動治療膠，可以有效增強手部肌肉力量，改善小肌肉技巧及減輕手部壓力。 治療膠物料不含麩質、乳膠和酪蛋白，且不含毒性，安全可靠，不論任何年齡都可安心使用。 提供方便開合和收藏的獨立盒裝治療膠，方便使用者在家中使用。</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>注意：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* 治療膠表面有油份為正常現象，第一次使用時搓勻即可</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* 每次使用治療膠前請徹底清潔雙手，避免沾染塵埃</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* 避免使用酒精清潔/使用酒精搓手液後立即觸碰治療膠，會導致染色</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* 避免穿著毛衣/於地毯上使用治療膠，以免粘著</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* 使用者可向物理治療師／職業治療師查詢適合的治療膠硬度及容量。</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>以下資料 僅供參考：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>幼兒  2oz 黃色（超軟）/4oz 黃色 （超軟）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>幼稚園初班/中班   4oz 黃色（超軟）/ 2oz 紅 (軟) / 4oz紅 (軟)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>幼稚園高班學童/初小學生  2oz  綠 (中)/4oz 綠 (中)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>小學生  4oz  綠 (中)/ 2oz  藍 (硬）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>中學生/成人 4oz 藍 (硬）</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>玩法介紹：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>https://youtu.be/O15JHjUyV3M </p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n', '<p>Alimed 2oz Theraputty is made in the USA. Available in four resistance levels and is designed for users with different levels of hand grip. It can be used to strengthen hand muscles, improve dexterity and reduce stress on the hands by doing hand exercises in squeezing, stretching or twisting the theraputty. The putty is gluten, latex and casein free and non-toxic, making it safe for use at all ages. Each putty is also packed in an individual box for convenient use and storage&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>at home.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Precautions:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Oil on the surface of the putty is normal and should be rubbed in during first time use</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Wash hands before use to prevent soiling&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Avoid cleaning with alcohol or using the theraputty immediately after using alcohol-based hand rubs as this may cause staining</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Avoid wearing jumpers / using the putty on carpets as it can stick to clothing and carpets</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Users should consult their physiotherapist/occupational therapist for the appropriate resistance level and size of putty</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The following information is for reference only:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Preschool toddlers: 2oz yellow (extra soft) / 4oz yellow (extra soft)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kindergarten year 1/2: 4oz yellow (super soft) / 2oz red (soft) / 4oz red (soft)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kindergarten year 3 / Primary school students up to year 3 : 2oz Green (Medium) / 4oz Green (Medium)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Primary school Students: 4oz Green (Medium) / 2oz Blue (Hard)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Secondary school students / Adults: 4oz Blue (Hard)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Demonstration of putty exercise:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>https://youtu.be/O15JHjUyV3M</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/15_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/15_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/15_3.jpg,assets/products_image/650/15_4.jpg,assets/products_image/650/15_5.jpg', 1, '2023-04-15 19:42:11', '2023-04-15 19:45:13'),
