(22, 2, 0, 'PUT1', '75', '麵粉泥膠擀棍', 'Small Rolling Pin', '18.00', 6.19, '<p>亞加力膠實心透明膠棍，配合治療膠使用，可訓練各項小肌肉能力。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>精選挑選小型尺寸，適合小童使用。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：長20cmx直徑2cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡： 3 歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>A transparent acrylic plastic rolling pin to be used with therapy putty to train small hand muscles.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Small size which is suitable for children.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 20cm long x 2cm diameter</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: Children aged 3 years and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/22_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/22_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/22_3.jpg,assets/products_image/650/22_4.jpg', 1, '2023-04-15 20:10:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(23, 2, 0, 'PUT2', '40', '雜錦壓印模具 ', 'Assorted Stamping Mold Set', '25.00', 8.10, '<p>適合切蛋糕、餅乾、巧克力、蛋糕裝飾、蔬菜水果；或供兒童玩DIY，&nbsp;配合治療膠/動力沙使用，玩樂同時訓練小肌肉能力。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式： 船、貨車、長頸鹿、大象、樹熊、豬（一套6款）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：直徑約3.8cm-7cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Suitable for cutting cakes, biscuits, chocolates, cake decorations, vegetables and fruits; or for children to DIY with therapy putty/kinetic sand to train small muscles&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Pattern: boat, truck, giraffe, elephant, koala, pig (6 patterns in a set)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: approx. 3.8cm - 7cm diameter</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/23_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/23_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-15 20:12:53', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(24, 2, 0, 'PUT3', '60', '動物壓印模具 ', 'Animal Stamping Mold Set', '25.00', 8.10, '<p>適合切蛋糕、餅乾、巧克力、蛋糕裝飾、蔬菜水果；或供兒童玩DIY，&nbsp;配合治療膠/動力沙使用，玩樂同時訓練小肌肉能力。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式： 魚、兔、熊、雞、狗、大象（一套6款）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸： 高 3.5cm ; 直徑：約4cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Suitable for cutting cakes, biscuits, chocolates, cake decorations, vegetables and fruits; or for children to DIY with therapy putty/kinetic sand to train small muscles&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Pattern: fish, Rabbit, bear, chicken, dog, elephant (6 patterns in a set)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: Height: 3.5cm; Diameter: approx. 4cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/24_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/24_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-15 20:15:46', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(25, 2, 0, 'PUT4', '15', '迷你水果簽', 'Mini Fruit Picks', '25.00', 12.30, '<p>水果簽配合治療膠使用，可以訓練手指力量及手眼協調等小肌肉能力。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>日本製造，有質素保證。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款色：綠色及黃色心形 （20支）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>產品尺寸：約寬 0.4 x 長 1.8 英寸（1cm x 4.5cm）&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>材質：苯乙烯樹脂</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡： 3 歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Mini fruit picks can be used with therapy putty to train finger strength and eye-hand coordination&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Made in Japan. Quality production&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: green and yellow in heart shape (20 pieces)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Product size: approx. 0.4 wide x 1.8 inches long (1cm x 4.5cm)&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Material: Styrene resin</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 3 years and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/25_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/25_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-15 20:17:19', '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
INSERT INTO `product` (`id`, `category_id`, `store_id`, `product_code`, `product_weight`, `p_name`, `p_name_en`, `product_price`, `cost`, `description`, `description_en`, `p_image`, `status`, `inserted_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(26, 8, 0, 'FY26', '215', '手握青蛙餵食玩具', 'Froggy Feeding Toy', '258.00', 152.96, '<p>青蛙很飢餓，需要孩子捏開青蛙的嘴巴來進行餵食。 此玩具可以訓練手握力，增加手部弓形紋穩定性及手眼協調能力，同時加強數字、計算和區分顏色的認知。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>套裝包括：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1.&nbsp; 2 隻橡膠青蛙 【約53cm直徑】</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. ６種顏色的60 隻蒼蠅</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. 數字骰</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. 顏色骰</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：4歲以上兒童（幼兒請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Children need to squeeze the frog&rsquo;s mouth to feed the starving frog. This toy can train hand grip strength, improve hand stability and hand-eye coordination. It can also enhance number recognition, counting and colour recognition.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Set includes:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. 2 plastic frogs (approx. 53cm diameter)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. 60 foam flies in 6 colours</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. number dice</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. colour dice</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 4 years old and above (please use under parental supervision to avoid choking hazard)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/26_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/26_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 13:43:17', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(27, 8, 0, 'FY27', '290', '可愛怪獸吸盤玩具 ', 'Suction Cup Set', '258.00', 132.67, '<p>可愛吸盤玩具套裝包括32個不同形狀和顏色的吸盤玩具，可以粘在無孔表面或彼此粘在一起，鼓勵孩子發揮想像力創作不同的結構，同時訓練小肌肉及視覺思維能力。 吸盤適用於窗戶、浴缸、地板、桌子光滑表面上。這款吸盤玩具由優質矽膠製成，安全環保，吸力大而且防水。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：每個吸盤約長5cm<br />\r\n建議使用年齡：3 歲以上兒童（幼兒請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>This suction cup set includes 32 suction cups in different shapes and colours that stick to non-porous surfaces or stick to each other. It encourages children to use their imagination as well as aids the development of motor skills and visual perception ability. The suction cups are ideal for use on windows, bathtubs, floors and tables with smooth surfaces. Made of high quality silicon rubber which is safe and environmentally friendly. Offer a secure grip and water resistant.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: Each suction cup is approximately 5cm long</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 3 years and above (please use under parental supervision to avoid choking hazard)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/27_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/27_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/27_3.jpg,assets/products_image/650/27_4.jpg,assets/products_image/650/27_5.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 13:49:22', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(28, 3, 0, 'FT1', '170', '幾何圖形螺絲 (8件)', 'Bolts Set (8 pieces)', '58.00', 13.80, '<p>幾何圖形螺絲套裝有正方形、三角形、六邊型、十字型狀四種不同顏色的螺絲，可以用來練習形狀顏色配對。有效訓練小肌肉能力，提升雙手協調、手眼協調及手指靈活性。台灣製造，使用安全無毒高級塑料，通過台灣ST安全玩具認證。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款色： 8件分裝/64件原裝</p>\r\n\r\n<p>顏色： 紅藍黃綠</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：長 6.5 厘米 x 直徑約 5厘米</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3 歲以上兒童 （幼兒請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Bolts set comes with four types of bolts in different colour and shapes - square, triangular, hexagonal and cross-shaped for practising shape and colour matching. It is an effective way to train small muscles, improve eye-hand coordination and finger dexterity. Made in Taiwan with safe and non-toxic plastic. Certified by Taiwan ST Toys.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Packages: 8 pieces / 64 pieces&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: Red, Blue, Yellow and Green</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: Length 6.5cm x Diameter approx. 5cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above (please use under parental supervision to avoid choking hazard)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/28_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/28_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 13:51:25', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(29, 8, 0, 'FY28', '290', '蛋蛋怪獸吸盤玩具', 'Suction Cup Set with Eggshell Storage', '218.00', 83.19, '<p>恐龍蛋殼收納設計， 內有 27 個吸盤玩具不同形狀和顏色的吸盤玩具，可以粘在無孔表面或彼此粘在一起，鼓勵孩子發揮想像力創作不同的結構，同時訓練小肌肉及視覺思維能力。 吸盤適用於窗戶、浴缸、地板、桌子等無孔表面上。這款吸盤玩具在美國通過 CPC CPSIA 和 ASTM F963-17 認證。 由 100% 高品質矽膠製成,不含雙酚 A ,不含乳膠。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：每個吸盤約長5cm<br />\r\n建議使用年齡：3 歲以上兒童（幼兒請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n', '<p>This suction cup set with eggshell storage contains 27 suction cups in different shapes and colours that stick to non-porous surfaces or stick to each other. It encourages children to use their imagination as well as aids the development of motor skills and visual perception ability. The suction cups are ideal for use on windows, bathtubs, floors and tables with smooth surfaces. This suction cup is CPC CPSIA and ASTM</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/29_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 13:53:09', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(30, 3, 0, 'FT1S', '670', '幾何圖形螺絲原包 (64 件)', 'Bolts Set (64 pieces)', '390.00', 110.37, '<p>幾何圖形螺絲套裝有正方形、三角形、六邊型、十字型狀四種不同顏色的螺絲，可以用來練習形狀顏色配對。有效訓練小肌肉能力，提升雙手協調、手眼協調及手指靈活性。台灣製造，使用安全無毒高級塑料，通過台灣ST安全玩具認證。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款色： 8件分裝/64件原裝</p>\r\n\r\n<p>顏色： 紅藍黃綠</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：長 6.5 厘米 x 直徑約 5厘米</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3 歲以上兒童 （幼兒請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Bolts set comes with four types of bolts in different colour and shapes - square, triangular, hexagonal and cross-shaped for practising shape and colour matching. It is an effective way to train small muscles, improve eye-hand coordination and finger dexterity. Made in Taiwan with safe and non-toxic plastic. Certified by Taiwan ST Toys.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Packages: 8 pieces / 64 pieces&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: Red, Blue, Yellow and Green</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: Length 6.5cm x Diameter approx. 5cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above (please use under parental supervision to avoid choking hazard)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/30_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/30_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 13:53:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(31, 3, 0, 'FT2', '180', '大C字扣環 (40個)', 'Large C Shaped Rings (40 pieces)', '65.00', 25.36, '<p>USL品牌的大C字連環扣，可用作練習顏色配對。有效訓練小肌肉能力，</p>\r\n\r\n<p>提升手腕控制、雙手協調、手眼協調及手指靈活性。也可以改善視覺專注及視覺感知能力等等。台灣製造，使用安全無毒高級塑料，通過台灣ST安全玩具認證。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款色： 40件分裝/200件原裝</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸： 5.1 x 7.1 厘米</p>\r\n\r\n<p>顏色： 紅藍黃綠</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3 歲以上兒童 （幼兒請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>USL large c shaped rings can be used to practice colour matching. It is also effective for training small hand muscle, improving wrist control, bilateral hand coordination, eye-hand coordination and finger dexterity. It can also improve visual attention and visual perception. Made in Taiwan with safe and non-toxic plastic. Certified by Taiwan ST Toys.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Packages: 40 pieces / 200 pieces&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 5.1 x 7.1 cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: Red, Blue, Yellow and Green</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above (please use under parental supervision to avoid choking hazard)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/31_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/31_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/31_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 13:55:04', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(32, 8, 0, 'FY30', '650', '爆谷夾夾蟲蟲玩具 ', 'Wriggleworms Set', '298.00', 111.90, '<p>Learning resources 的爆谷夾可以在&ldquo;無筆&rdquo;狀態下輕鬆學習及鍛鍊執筆技巧，強化前三指肌力，提昇小肌肉技巧。這款夾蟲蟲遊戲非常可愛和有趣，提升孩子學習的動力。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>套裝包括：&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. 20條彩色蟲蟲</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. 20張活動卡</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. 4 個膠圍欄</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. 一 個爆谷夾</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. 一張海綿墊</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6. 一個轉盤</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：爆谷夾 -- 11cm長x3.5cm寬</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n建議使用年齡：4歲以上兒童（幼兒請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n', '<p>Specially designed tri-grip tong by Learning Resources make it easy for children to strengthen their first three fingers strength and practice pencil grip without using a pencil. It is a fun way for children to learn through the game.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Set includes:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. 20 colourful worms</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. 20 activity cards</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. 4 plastic fences</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. one ti-grip tong</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. one foam activity board</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6. one spinner</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: tri-grip tong - 11cm long x 3.5cm wide</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 4 years and above (please use under parental supervision to avoid choking hazard)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/32_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/32_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/32_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 13:56:27', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(33, 3, 0, 'FT2S', '835', '大C字扣環原包(200個)', 'Large C Shaped Rings (200 pieces)', '280.00', 126.78, '<p>USL品牌的大C字連環扣，可用作練習顏色配對。有效訓練小肌肉能力，</p>\r\n\r\n<p>提升手腕控制、雙手協調、手眼協調及手指靈活性。也可以改善視覺專注及視覺感知能力等等。台灣製造，使用安全無毒高級塑料，通過台灣ST安全玩具認證。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款色： 40件分裝/200件原裝</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸： 5.1 x 7.1 厘米</p>\r\n\r\n<p>顏色： 紅藍黃綠</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3 歲以上兒童 （幼兒請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>USL large c shaped rings can be used to practice colour matching. It is also effective for training small hand muscle, improving wrist control, bilateral hand coordination, eye-hand coordination and finger dexterity. It can also improve visual attention and visual perception. Made in Taiwan with safe and non-toxic plastic. Certified by Taiwan ST Toys.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Packages: 40 pieces / 200 pieces&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 5.1 x 7.1 cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: Red, Blue, Yellow and Green</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above (please use under parental supervision to avoid choking hazard)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/33_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/33_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/33_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 13:57:17', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
