(43, 8, 0, 'FY32M ', '475', '動物餵食夾夾玩具 (猴子)', 'Feeding Animal Set (Monkey)', '428.00', 300.00, '<p>美國Lakeshore品牌創智玩具，受全球職業治療師推薦的訓練產品。孩子可以使用鑷子夾起美味的零食，放入動物的嘴巴裏面餵食，在趣味的遊戲中，訓練前三指控制、手指力量及手眼協調能力。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童</p>\r\n', '<p>Designed by the Lakeshore brand in the USA, a highly recommended tool by occupational therapists worldwide for training. Children can use tweezers to pick up snacks and put them in the animal&#39;s mouth to feed them. It can strengthen the first three finger control, finger strength and hand-eye coordination</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 3 years and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/43_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/43_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/43_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 14:17:43', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(44, 3, 0, 'FT6', '30', '蘑菇釘 (50粒)', 'Mushroom Pegs (50 pieces)', '25.00', 5.00, '<p>USL品牌蘑菇釘是小肌肉訓練的小配件。可以配合不同工具，例如治療膠等，訓練手指力量、手指靈活性、前二指控制、手眼協調....等等。 台灣製造，使用安全無毒高級塑料，通過台灣ST安全玩具認證。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：2x1厘米</p>\r\n\r\n<p>顏色： 紅藍黃綠白</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3 歲以上兒童 （幼兒請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>USL mushroom pegs are add-on items for small muscle training. They can be used with different tools such as therapy putty to train finger strength, finger dexterity, front two-finger control, eye-hand coordination, etc. Made in Taiwan with safe and non-toxic plastic. Certified by Taiwan ST Toys.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 2x1 cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: Red, Blue, Yellow, Green and White</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above (please use under parental supervision to avoid choking hazard)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/44_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 14:20:06', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(45, 8, 0, 'FY35P', '290', '寵物洞洞板穿繩玩具', 'Animal Lacing Board Set (Pet Set)', '168.00', 102.95, '<p>被譽為「幼兒遊戲的黃金標準」超過 30 年歷史的Melissa &amp; Doug 品牌的穿繩玩具，培養早期腦部發展，透過遊戲讓孩子獲得重要的生活技能。提升孩子手眼/雙手協調能力，以及專注力。 使用可再生和耐用的木板製造。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>套裝包括：&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. 五個雙面動物主題板&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;【農場版：&nbsp;牛、羊、雞、豬和馬】<br />\r\n【寵物版： 狗、貓、兔、魚和龜】<br />\r\n2. 五條彩色鞋帶繩<br />\r\n<br />\r\n尺寸：1.6 x 6.7 x 8.2 英吋<br />\r\n材質：木材、紡織品、紙板&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>適合3 歲以上兒童<br />\r\n（請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食/ 繩子纏繞頸部）</p>\r\n', '<p>Designed by Melissa &amp; Doug which is a renowned brand in designing toys for toddlers for over 30 years, this animal lacing board set can promote early brain development. Children can practice lacing skills and strengthen hand-eye coordination and attention span. Made from renewable and durable wooden boards.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Set includes:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. 5 double-sided animal theme lacing panels</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;[Farm: cow, sheep, chicken, pig and horse]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;[Pet: dog, cat, rabbit, fish and turtle]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. 5 colourful shoelaces</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 1.6 x 6.7 x 8.2 inches</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Material: wood, textile, cardboard&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Suitable for children aged 3 years and above (Please use under parental supervision to avoid choking risk)</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/45_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/45_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 14:21:44', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(46, 3, 0, 'FT7', '155', '洞洞板蘑菇釘套裝 (一份)', 'Mushroom Peg Board Set', '78.00', 41.82, '<p>USL品牌洞洞板蘑菇釘套裝包含一塊10x10洞洞板及120粒蘑菇釘。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>可協助訓練手眼協調、手指靈活性、前二指控制和空間感等等。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>使用安全無毒高級塑料，台灣製造，通過台灣ST安全玩具認證</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：洞洞板尺寸：16x16x1厘米； 蘑菇釘尺寸：2x1厘米</p>\r\n\r\n<p>顏色：洞洞板-白色；蘑菇釘-紅藍黃綠白</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3 歲以上兒童 （幼兒請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>USL mushroom peg board set includes a 10x10 peg board and 120 pieces of mushroom pegs. It helps to train eye-hand coordination, finger dexterity, front two-finger control and spatial awareness, etc. Made in Taiwan with safe and non-toxic plastic. Certified by Taiwan ST Toys.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: peg board size: 16x16x1cm; mushroom peg size: 2x1cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: peg board - white; mushroom pegs - red, blue, yellow, green and white</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above (please use under parental supervision to avoid choking hazard)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/46_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/46_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 14:23:13', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(47, 8, 0, 'FY35F', '265', '農場洞洞板穿繩玩具', 'Animal Lacing Board Set (Farm Set)', '168.00', 102.95, '<p>被譽為「幼兒遊戲的黃金標準」超過 30 年歷史的Melissa &amp; Doug 品牌的穿繩玩具，培養早期腦部發展，透過遊戲讓孩子獲得重要的生活技能。提升孩子手眼/雙手協調能力，以及專注力。 使用可再生和耐用的木板製造。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>套裝包括：&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. 五個雙面動物主題板&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;【農場版：&nbsp;牛、羊、雞、豬和馬】<br />\r\n【寵物版： 狗、貓、兔、魚和龜】<br />\r\n2. 五條彩色鞋帶繩<br />\r\n<br />\r\n尺寸：1.6 x 6.7 x 8.2 英吋<br />\r\n材質：木材、紡織品、紙板&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>適合3 歲以上兒童<br />\r\n（請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食/ 繩子纏繞頸部）</p>\r\n', '<p>Designed by Melissa &amp; Doug which is a renowned brand in designing toys for toddlers for over 30 years, this animal lacing board set can promote early brain development. Children can practice lacing skills and strengthen hand-eye coordination and attention span. Made from renewable and durable wooden boards.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Set includes:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. 5 double-sided animal theme lacing panels</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;[Farm: cow, sheep, chicken, pig and horse]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;[Pet: dog, cat, rabbit, fish and turtle]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. 5 colourful shoelaces</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 1.6 x 6.7 x 8.2 inches</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Material: wood, textile, cardboard&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Suitable for children aged 3 years and above (Please use under parental supervision to avoid choking risk)</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/47_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/47_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 14:23:51', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(48, 3, 0, 'FT8', '365', '2cm小方粒連盒 (24粒)', '2cm Cubes with storage box (24 pieces)', '48.00', 32.26, '<p>USL品牌2cm小方粒有四種顏色，是訓練數數、仿砌和小肌肉能力的好幫手。使用安全無毒高級塑料，台灣生產，通過台灣ST安全玩具認證。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款色： 24粒分裝（連收納膠盒）/100粒原裝</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：2x2x2厘米</p>\r\n\r\n<p>顏色： 紅藍黃綠&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3 歲以上兒童 （幼兒請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>USL 2cm cubes come in four colours and are great for counting, copying patterns and small muscle training. Made in Taiwan with safe and non-toxic plastic. Certified by Taiwan ST Toys.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Quantity: 24 pieces (with storage box) / 100 pieces</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 2x2x2cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: Red, Blue, Yellow and Green&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above (please use under parental supervision to avoid choking hazard)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/48_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/48_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/48_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 14:27:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(49, 8, 0, 'FY36', '640', '衫鈕穿繩玩具', 'Button Race Set', '258.00', 160.00, '<p>將鈕扣繫在襯衫上，可以訓練顏色識別、手眼/雙手協調，同時提高自理能力。遊戲可以最多可供 4 名玩家使用，競賽與圖片卡上的顏色匹配，繫出相應的順序。無論是個人還是團體遊戲，都可以提高專注力。玩具由優質零件和兒童安全材料製成。光滑的飾面和圓潤的邊緣讓小手可以安全、輕鬆地抓握和玩耍。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>套裝包括：4 件襯衫、4 條鞋帶、30 張挑戰卡和一堆彩色鈕扣</p>\r\n\r\n<p>適合3 歲以上兒童（請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食/ 繩子纏繞頸部）</p>\r\n', '<p>Threading buttons onto the shirts can enhance children&rsquo;s colour recognition, hand-eye/ bilateral hand coordination and self-care ability. Up to 4 players can join the game by competing to thread buttons according to the picture cards at the fastest speed. It can also be played individually to improve attention. The toy is made of high quality materials which are safe for children&rsquo;s use. Smooth and rounded edges also ensure safety.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Set includes: 4 shirts, 4 shoelaces, 30 picture cards and colourful buttons</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Suitable for children aged 3 and above (Please use under parental supervision to avoid choking risk)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/49_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/49_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/49_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 14:29:57', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(50, 3, 0, 'FT8S', '820', '2cm小方粒原包(100粒)', '2cm Cubes (100 pieces)', '170.00', 130.74, '<p>USL品牌2cm小方粒有四種顏色，是訓練數數、仿砌和小肌肉能力的好幫手。使用安全無毒高級塑料，台灣生產，通過台灣ST安全玩具認證。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款色： 24粒分裝（連收納膠盒）/100粒原裝</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：2x2x2厘米</p>\r\n\r\n<p>顏色： 紅藍黃綠&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3 歲以上兒童 （幼兒請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>USL 2cm cubes come in four colours and are great for counting, copying patterns and small muscle training. Made in Taiwan with safe and non-toxic plastic. Certified by Taiwan ST Toys.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Quantity: 24 pieces (with storage box) / 100 pieces</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 2x2x2cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: Red, Blue, Yellow and Green&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above (please use under parental supervision to avoid choking hazard)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/50_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/50_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/50_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 14:30:12', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(51, 8, 0, 'FY40', '460', '英文字母釣魚玩具', 'Magnetic Alphabet Fishing Game', '268.00', 136.69, '<p>由香港設計師集團創立的CozyBomB磁性木製釣魚玩具，有兩個場景，讓孩子在冰湖下/海洋中釣魚，學習字母/顏色，同時訓練小肌肉（手腕控制、手眼協調等）及視覺感知能力。玩具以無毒物料及環保油漆製成，通過 ASTM 和 CPC 認證，木塊表面光滑不傷手。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>套裝包括：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>木製遊戲板 x 1（冰湖 + 海洋場景）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>字母魚 x 26（包括所有字母）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>魚類收納袋 x 1</p>\r\n\r\n<p>釣魚竿 x 2</p>\r\n\r\n<p>帶磁鐵的貓娃娃 x 1</p>\r\n\r\n<p>彩色包裝附遊戲說明 x 1</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸： 魚4.5cm長；魚竿18cm 長；遊戲板22cm直徑x2cm厚</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n適合：3 歲以上兒童 （請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食/ 繩子纏繞頸部）</p>\r\n', '<p>Designed by Hong Kong Designer Group CozyBomB. This magnetic alphabet fishing game has two designs that allow children to practice fishing in a pond or in the ocean. It can help children to learn alphabets and colour classification while training small muscles (wrist control, hand-eye coordination, etc.) and visual perception at the same time. Made with non-toxic materials and eco-friendly paints, the toy is ASTM and CPC certified. All wooden pieces have a smooth contour which is safe for children&#39;s use.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Set includes:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wooden Board x 1 (pond + ocean)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Alphabet fish x 26 (includes all alphabets)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fish storage bag x 1</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fishing rod x 2</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Cat doll with magnet x 1</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Game instructions x 1</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: fish 4.5cm long; fishing rod 18cm long; wooden board 22cm diameter x 2cm thick</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nSuitable for: children aged 3 years and above (Please use under parental supervision to avoid choking risk)</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/51_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/51_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 14:33:23', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(52, 9, 0, 'VP1', '460', '木製拼圖積木', 'Wooden Shape Puzzles', '298.00', 127.80, '<p>Coogam 木製拼圖積木套裝包含，36 個木塊和 60 種不同的圖案卡片，包括動物、昆蟲、鳥類等。孩子們可以嘗試找出卡片上的圖案是什麼部件，並創造自己的設計。採用環保木材製成，表面光滑。是訓練空間感和小肌肉能力的有趣玩具！</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3.5歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Coogam wooden shape puzzles contain 36 wooden puzzles and 60 different pattern cards including animals, insects, birds, etc. Children can choose to build what is shown on the cards or create their own designs. Made of nontoxic and 100% wood with a smooth edge design for safety.&nbsp;It is a great tool for training visual-spatial ability and building small muscle skills.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3.5 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/52_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/52_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/52_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 14:46:08', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(53, 9, 0, 'VP2', '210', 'Spot it! 視覺訓練卡牌 ', 'Spot It! Visual Training Cards', '218.00', 104.10, '<p>每張Spot it! 視覺訓練卡牌，跟另一張卡牌都有一個匹配的符號或圖片，可以進行多種有趣的配對遊戲。加強孩子的視覺分辨、形狀恆常、空間旋轉等視覺感知能力，同時訓練視覺專注、反應力，配合其他工具也可以訓練小肌肉能力！這時可以跟朋友和家長一起玩的社交比賽遊戲～</p>\r\n\r\n<p>產品包括：55 張圓形卡&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\r\n1-8 名玩家,平均遊戲時間為 15 分鐘。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：4歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Spot it! visual training cards is a great tool for matching game. Any two cards have exactly one symbol in common.&nbsp;It can strengthen children&#39;s visual perception skills such as visual discrimination, form constancy as well as training visual attention and processing speed. It can also build small muscle skills when used with other training tools. Ideal for playing with friends and parents.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Includes 55 cards&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For 1-8 players, each game last for approx 15 minutes</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 4 years and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/53_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/53_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 14:48:33', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(54, 9, 0, 'VP3', '380', '橡皮圈矩陣創作板', 'Wooden Geoboard', '298.00', 173.70, '<p>在堅固安全的創作板上用橡皮圈做成不同的2D圖案及字母，訓練手指力量，手眼/雙手協調和視覺空間。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>橡皮圈矩陣創作板套裝包括：<br />\r\n1. 1 塊木板 【6x6釘子】17.7cm x 17.7cmx 2.3 cm<br />\r\n2.多條彩色橡皮圈釘板<br />\r\n3. 30 張圖案卡及5 張空白卡</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3.5歲以上學童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Use rubber bands to make different 2D patterns and letters on the geoboard to build finger strength, hand-eye/ bilateral hand coordination and visual perception skills.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Set includes:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. 1 wooden geoboard [6x6 pegs] 17.7cm x 17.7cm x 2.3 cm&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Coloured rubber bands</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. 30 pattern cards and 5 blank cards</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3.5 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/54_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/54_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/54_3.jpg,assets/products_image/650/54_4.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 14:51:15', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(55, 9, 0, 'VP4', '395', '小精靈方塊遊戲 ', 'Pixy Cubes', '258.00', 144.30, '<p>方塊骰子可以重組成不同圖案，比賽速度，考驗敏捷性、創造力、記憶力及視覺感知能力。遊戲適合 1 至 4 名玩家。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>套裝包括：<br />\r\n1. 16 粒方塊骰子<br />\r\n2. 80 個設計模板<br />\r\n3. 13 張挑戰卡</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：6 歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Pixy Cubes can be used to form different patterns. It is a game racing for speed and testing your creativity, memory and visual perception skills. The game is suitable for 1 to 4 players.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Set includes:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. 16 cubes</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. 80 templates</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. 13 challenge cards</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 6 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/55_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/55_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 14:53:18', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(56, 18, 0, 'SIB1', '800', '45cm防爆治療球', '45cm Fitness Ball', '140.00', 86.40, '<p>台灣製造45cm防爆健身球，配合不同感統訓練活動提供前庭覺及本體覺刺激，改善感覺調節能力，提升肌肉力量及姿勢控制等等。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式：綠色</p>\r\n\r\n<p>適合150cm以下人士使用</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Made in Taiwan, the 45cm explosion-proof fitness ball provides vestibular and proprioceptive stimulation for different sensory integration activities, improves sensory modulation, muscle strength and postural control, etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style: Green&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Suitable for people under 150cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/56_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/56_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 14:58:30', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(57, 10, 0, 'HW1', '525', '韓國蛋形蠟筆 (12枝)', 'Wowkids Eggyon (12 colours)', '288.00', 188.00, '<p>Wowkids Eggyon水性蠟筆於韓國設計及製造，通過無毒安全測試 （KC approved）。 可以在紙、黑板、書桌、鏡子、浴盤...等地方塗鴉，之後用濕紙巾輕易清潔。轉動蠟筆就可以調整長度，不會弄髒雙手且不會容易斷掉。底部有磁鐵，可以貼在白板/冰箱上使用。雞蛋形狀讓幼兒容易抓握，配合小肌肉的發展，慢慢加強寫前技巧，推薦成為孩子的第一套蠟筆。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>套裝： 12種顏色--- 12支蠟筆<br />\r\n建議使用年齡：1歲以上兒童 （請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n', '<p>Wowkids Eggyon is designed and manufactured in Korea which is KC approved. It can be used on paper, blackboards, desks, mirrors, bath tubs, etc. then easily erased with surface wipes. The length of the crayon can be adjusted by twisting the crayon which won&rsquo;t break the crayon easily while keeping your hands clean. The magnet on the bottom allows you to stick it to a whiteboard/fridge. The egg shape makes it easy for children to grasp and train their pre-writing skills.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Set: 12 colours - 12 crayons</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 1 year old and above (please use under parental supervision to avoid choking hazard)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/57_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/57_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 14:59:17', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(58, 10, 0, 'HW2', '95', '日本插插積木蠟筆 (6枝)', 'Baby Color Crayon (6 colours)', '78.00', 39.93, '<p>日本製造的插插積木蠟筆，把蠟筆疊高整潔存放之餘，也可以用作訓練孩子手眼協調能力的玩具。非常容易握持，尤其適合手部發展仍未成熟的幼兒。 堅固耐用不會斷裂。 安全物料製造，可以放進口中。蠟筆可以用水洗清潔，畫畫過程不易弄髒雙手及衣服，在衣服上的痕跡容易在洗滌過程中去除。 這款蠟筆曾經榮獲兒童設計獎。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>套裝：6色蠟筆----紅橙黃綠藍黑<br />\r\n尺寸：7 x 3.6 x 3.5cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：1.5歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Baby colour crayon is made in Japan. Its stacking design is for easy storage and can be a training of hand-eye coordination for children. Easy to grasp and especially ideal for toddlers with immature hand grip. Durable and not easy to break. Made of safe material and can be put in the mouth. Crayon stains can be washed with water which will not easily stain hands or clothes. The crayon has won the children&#39;s design award.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Set: 6 colour crayons ---- red, orange, yellow, green, blue and black</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 7 x 3.6 x 3.5cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 1.5 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/58_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:02:26', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(59, 3, 0, 'FT9', '85', '1cm串珠連盒 (32粒)', '1cm Threading Beads (32 pieces)', '40.00', 20.98, '<p>USL品牌 1cm串珠&nbsp; 有圓形、正方形、圓柱形、長圓形四種不同顏色的小珠，可訓練形狀顏色配對。 玩串珠/疊高高等遊戲，有效提升雙手協調、手眼協調及手指靈活性。使用安全無毒高級塑料，台灣製造，通過台灣ST安全玩具認證。套裝已包含小串珠及串珠繩。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款色： 32粒分裝（連收納膠盒）/320粒原裝</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸： 每粒小珠直徑 約 2.1厘米 ；繩子長度：75 厘米</p>\r\n\r\n<p>顏色： 紅藍黃綠（* 珠子形狀顏色隨機）</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n建議使用年齡： 3歲以上兒童<br />\r\n（請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食/ 繩子纏繞頸部）</p>\r\n', '<p>USL 1cm threading beads come in four different shapes - circular, square, cylindrical and oblong and colour which can be used for colour and shape matching. Threading beads or stacking beads can improve bilateral hand coordination, eye-hand coordination and finger dexterity. Made in Taiwan with safe and non-toxic plastic. Certified by Taiwan ST Toys. Set includes beads and string.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Quantity: 32 beads (with storage box) / 320 beads</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: Each bead is approximately 2.1cm in diameter; Length of string: 75cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: Red, blue, yellow and green (* bead shapes and colours are random)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(Please use under parental supervision to avoid choking risk)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/59_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/59_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:03:55', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(60, 10, 0, 'HW3', '115', '日本戒指蠟筆 (6枝)', 'Ring crayon (6 colours)', '98.00', 42.42, '<p>日本製造的戒指蠟筆，使用安全的材料製造，可放進口中。 不會黏手，也不會弄髒雙手。沒有蠟筆異味，是花香的味道，刺激感官開發。 利用水和肥皂可以把觸摸過/弄髒的蠟筆清洗。 獨特設計，還沒有開始使用筆的孩子也很容易握持。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>套裝：6色蠟筆---- 紅橙黃綠藍粉紅蠟筆 + 一個擦子膠</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：2歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Ring crayon is made in Japan with safe materials and can be placed in the mouth. It does not stick to your hands and does not easily make stains on hands. Come with a floral scent that stimulates the senses of children. Water and soap can be used to wash used crayons or soiled crayons. The unique design is easy for children to grasp even for children who are still doing pre-writing training.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Set: 6 colour crayons ---- red, orange, yellow, green, blue, pink and red + an eraser</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 2 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/60_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/60_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:04:40', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(61, 18, 0, 'SIB2', '0', '55cm防爆治療球', '55cm Fitness Ball', '150.00', 110.00, '<p>台灣製造55cm防爆健身球，配合不同感統訓練活動提供前庭覺及本體覺刺激，改善感覺調節能力，提升肌肉力量及姿勢控制等等。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式：藍色/紅色（隨機發放一款）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>適合150cm-160cm 人士使用</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Made in Taiwan, the 55cm explosion-proof fitness ball provides vestibular and proprioceptive stimulation for different sensory integration activities, improves sensory modulation, muscle strength and postural control, etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style: blue/red (randomly released)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Suitable for 150cm-160cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/61_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/61_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:05:06', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(62, 3, 0, 'FT9S', '925', '1cm串珠原包 (320粒)', '1cm Threading Beads (320 pieces)', '340.00', 166.39, '<p>USL品牌 1cm串珠&nbsp; 有圓形、正方形、圓柱形、長圓形四種不同顏色的小珠，可訓練形狀顏色配對。 玩串珠/疊高高等遊戲，有效提升雙手協調、手眼協調及手指靈活性。使用安全無毒高級塑料，台灣製造，通過台灣ST安全玩具認證。套裝已包含小串珠及串珠繩。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款色： 32粒分裝（連收納膠盒）/320粒原裝</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸： 每粒小珠直徑 約 2.1厘米 ；繩子長度：75 厘米</p>\r\n\r\n<p>顏色： 紅藍黃綠（* 珠子形狀顏色隨機）</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n建議使用年齡： 3歲以上兒童<br />\r\n（請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食/ 繩子纏繞頸部）</p>\r\n', '<p>USL 1cm threading beads come in four different shapes - circular, square, cylindrical and oblong and colour which can be used for colour and shape matching. Threading beads or stacking beads can improve bilateral hand coordination, eye-hand coordination and finger dexterity. Made in Taiwan with safe and non-toxic plastic. Certified by Taiwan ST Toys. Set includes beads and string.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Quantity: 32 beads (with storage box) / 320 beads</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: Each bead is approximately 2.1cm in diameter; Length of string: 75cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: Red, blue, yellow and green (* bead shapes and colours are random)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(Please use under parental supervision to avoid choking risk)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/62_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/62_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:07:34', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(63, 18, 0, 'SIB3', '1300', '65cm防爆治療球', '65cm Fitness Ball', '160.00', 114.00, '<p>台灣製造65cm防爆健身球，配合不同感統訓練活動提供前庭覺及本體覺刺激，改善感覺調節能力，提升肌肉力量及姿勢控制等等。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式：灰色</p>\r\n\r\n<p>適合160 cm以上人士使用</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Made in Taiwan, the 65cm explosion-proof fitness ball provides vestibular and proprioceptive stimulation for different sensory integration activities, improves sensory modulation, muscle strength and postural control, etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style: Grey</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Suitable for people over 160 cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/63_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/63_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:08:57', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(64, 3, 0, 'FT10', '135', '2cm串珠連盒 (16粒)', '2cm Threading beads with storage box (16 pieces)', '40.00', 12.34, '<p>USL品牌 2cm串珠&nbsp; 有圓形、正方形、圓柱形、長圓形四種不同顏色的小珠，可訓練形狀顏色配對。 玩串珠/疊高高等遊戲，有效提升雙手協調、手眼協調及手指靈活性。使用安全無毒高級塑料，台灣製造，通過台灣ST安全玩具認證。套裝已包含小串珠及串珠繩。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款色： 16粒（連收納膠盒）/160粒</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸： 每粒小珠直徑 約 2.1厘米 ；繩子長度：75 厘米</p>\r\n\r\n<p>顏色： 紅藍黃綠 （* 珠子形狀顏色隨機）</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n建議使用年齡：3 歲以上兒童<br />\r\n（請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食/ 繩子纏繞頸部）</p>\r\n', '<p>USL 2cm threading beads come in four different shapes - circular, square, cylindrical and oblong and colour which can be used for colour and shape matching. Threading beads or stacking beads can improve bilateral hand coordination, eye-hand coordination and finger dexterity. Made in Taiwan with safe and non-toxic plastic. Certified by Taiwan ST Toys. Set includes beads and string.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Quantity: 16 beads (with storage box) / 160 beads</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: Each bead is approximately 2.1cm in diameter; Length of string: 75cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: Red, blue, yellow and green (* bead shapes and colours are random)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(Please use under parental supervision to avoid choking risk)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/64_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/64_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/64_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:09:13', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(65, 10, 0, 'HW4', '165', '日本特大三角蠟筆 (12枝)', 'Jumbo Triangle Crayons (12 colours)', '128.00', 52.08, '<p>日本製造櫻花牌特大蠟筆採用三角設計，讓孩子的小手容易抓握。蠟筆不容易斷，不會粘手也不會把雙手弄髒。 使用安全的著色劑製造，幼兒可放心使用。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：17.7 x 11.4 x 2.1 cm 【每支蠟筆長7cm，直徑1.4cm】<br />\r\n<br />\r\n建議使用年齡：2歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Jumbo crayons with a triangular design is easy to grasp by children. The crayons do not break easily and will not stick to hands. Made with a safe colouring agent, safe for children&rsquo;s use.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 17.7 x 11.4 x 2.1 cm [each crayon is 7cm long and 1.4cm in diameter]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 2 years and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/65_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/65_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/65_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:09:26', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(66, 3, 0, 'FT10S', '910', '2cm串珠原包 (160粒)', '2cm Threading beads (160 pieces)', '340.00', 123.36, '<p>USL品牌 2cm串珠&nbsp; 有圓形、正方形、圓柱形、長圓形四種不同顏色的小珠，可訓練形狀顏色配對。 玩串珠/疊高高等遊戲，有效提升雙手協調、手眼協調及手指靈活性。使用安全無毒高級塑料，台灣製造，通過台灣ST安全玩具認證。套裝已包含小串珠及串珠繩。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款色： 16粒（連收納膠盒）/160粒</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸： 每粒小珠直徑 約 2.1厘米 ；繩子長度：75 厘米</p>\r\n\r\n<p>顏色： 紅藍黃綠 （* 珠子形狀顏色隨機）</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n建議使用年齡：3 歲以上兒童<br />\r\n（請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食/ 繩子纏繞頸部）</p>\r\n', '<p>USL 2cm threading beads come in four different shapes - circular, square, cylindrical and oblong and colour which can be used for colour and shape matching. Threading beads or stacking beads can improve bilateral hand coordination, eye-hand coordination and finger dexterity. Made in Taiwan with safe and non-toxic plastic. Certified by Taiwan ST Toys. Set includes beads and string.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Quantity: 16 beads (with storage box) / 160 beads</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: Each bead is approximately 2.1cm in diameter; Length of string: 75cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: Red, blue, yellow and green (* bead shapes and colours are random)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(Please use under parental supervision to avoid choking risk)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/66_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/66_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/66_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:11:39', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(67, 10, 0, 'HW8', '335', '特大粉筆 (16枝)', 'Jumbo Chalk Set (16 colours)', '50.00', 27.10, '<p>16 種不同顏色的特大粉筆，方便抓握。 色彩繽紛，發揮無窮創意。適用於紙上，黑板上，地板上.....任何表面 塗鴉，可水洗。優質安全，產品通過美國玩具安全測試，符合標準。附送膠盒方便儲存。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>套裝包括：16支粉筆<br />\r\n尺寸：粉筆直徑約1寸，長4寸<br />\r\n<br />\r\n建議使用年齡：2歲以上兒童</p>\r\n', '<p>Jumbo chalk set comes with extra large chalk in 16 different colours which is easy to grasp by children. Children can use their imagination to do their drawings with these colourful chalk. Suitable for use on any surface including paper, blackboard, floor, etc. Chalk stain is washable by water. High quality and safe to use by children. Passed safety toy test in the USA. Comes with a plastic case for easy storage.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Set includes 16 chalk</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: Chalk is approximately 1 inch in diameter and 4 inches in length</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 2 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/67_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/67_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:11:57', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(68, 3, 0, 'FT11', '5', '75cm穿珠繩', '75cm Threading String', '4.00', 2.02, '<p>此串珠繩可用來串各種珠子/飲管/通粉，訓練雙手及手眼協調。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸： 75cm長</p>\r\n\r\n<p>顏色：紅/橙/青/藍/紫&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n建議使用年齡：3 歲以上兒童<br />\r\n（請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食/ 繩子纏繞頸部）</p>\r\n', '<p>This threading string can be used to thread a variety of beads/straws/macaroni to train bilateral hands and eye-hand coordination.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 75cm long</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colour: red/orange/green/blue/purple&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(Please use under parental supervision to avoid choking risk)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/68_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:12:49', '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
INSERT INTO `product` (`id`, `category_id`, `store_id`, `product_code`, `product_weight`, `p_name`, `p_name_en`, `product_price`, `cost`, `description`, `description_en`, `p_image`, `status`, `inserted_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(69, 10, 0, 'HW15', '8', '洞洞三角幼鉛筆', 'Triangular pencil', '4.00', 1.47, '<p>LYRA 德國品牌粗木質三角筆，使用FSC 優質木材製造，堅硬防水。三角凹槽設計，引導孩子把拇指、食指和中指放到正確執筆姿勢。筆身容易抓握，同時提供觸感刺激。 筆芯為HB鉛筆。筆身可以寫名字。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：長17.5cm x 粗0.72cm<br />\r\n顏色：紅/黃/綠/淺藍/藍/湖水藍（隨機款式1支），</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n建議使用年齡：3歲以上</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Wooden triangular pencil designed by LYRA brand from Germany, is made from FSC wood and is hard and water resistant. The triangular grooves enables children to put thumb, index finger and middle finger at a correct position to facilitate a proper pencil grip. It also provides tactile stimulation to children. The hardness of the pencil is HB. Name can be marked on the pencil.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 17.5cm long x 0.72cm thick</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: red/yellow/green/light blue/blue/lake blue (colour to be sent in random)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/69_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:14:52', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(70, 3, 0, 'FT12', '925', '花花片連盒 (50塊)', 'Flower tokens with storage box (50 pieces)', '25.00', 5.14, '<p>USL 品牌花花片可以讓孩子自由創作和組合出不同圖案，提升手指力量、手指遠端控制能力、手眼協調能力... 也可以配合治療膠做不同小肌肉訓練，同時學習數數和顔色概念。台灣製造，使用安全無毒高級塑料，通過台灣ST安全玩具認證。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款色： 50塊（連收納膠盒）/1400塊</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：直徑約 2.5厘米</p>\r\n\r\n<p>顏色： 紅藍黃綠白<br />\r\n<br />\r\n建議使用年齡：3 歲以上兒童 （請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n', '<p>USL flower tokens allow children to create different patterns to improve finger strength, distal finger control, eye-hand coordination, etc. They can also be used with therapy putty to train different small muscles while learning counting and sorting colour at the same time. Made in Taiwan with safe and non-toxic plastic. Certified by Taiwan ST Toys.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Quantity: 50 pieces (with storage box) / 1400 pieces</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: approx. 2.5cm diameter</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: Red, Blue, Yellow, Green and White</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(Please use under parental supervision to avoid choking risk)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/70_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/70_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/70_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:15:50', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(71, 10, 0, 'HW16', '70', '幼身白板筆 (6枝)', 'Whiteboard Pen Set(6 colours)', '48.00', 20.70, '<p>雄獅彩繪白板筆採用環保顏料製作而成，可彩繪與書寫於一般白板上，共有紅、藍、黑、綠、棕、紫六種顏色，色彩飽和鮮艷，環保筆桿材質搭配日本進口1.0mm筆尖，書寫起來得心應手，享受彩繪白板新樂趣。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>套裝：一套6支，包括紅、綠、黑、藍、紫、棕色</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>The whiteboard pen is made by environmentally friendly paint and can be used for drawing and writing on whiteboard. It comes in six bright colours: red, blue, black, green, brown and purple. Comes with 1.0mm diameter leads importing from Japan, it is a great tool for writing and drawing on whiteboard.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A pack of 6 pens, including red, green, black, blue, purple and brown</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/71_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:17:18', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(72, 18, 0, 'SIB4P', '460', '迷你跳跳球', 'Mini Hop Ball', '218.00', 114.08, '<p>美國品牌 Hedstrom 歷史悠久，一直致力於製造優質耐用的跳跳球。有孩子們喜歡的有趣圖案。在跳跳球上彈跳可以提供豐富的前庭及本體覺刺激，滿足孩子的感覺需要，同時可以訓練身體協調、平衡力和動作計劃能力等。產品可以在室內或戶外使用。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* 商品不含氣泵，需要自行透過任何手動或電動打氣筒充氣<br />\r\n* 可輕鬆放氣,方便收納或旅行</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式：汪汪巡邏隊/冰雪奇緣/復仇者聯盟/蜘蛛俠<br />\r\n【請於下單時說明款式,不特別說明款式則隨機發放】<br />\r\n尺寸：充氣後連手柄高 40-45cm；迷你跳跳球直徑約30-35cm<br />\r\n<br />\r\n適合：2.5-4 歲體型學童（需在成人監督下使用產品確保安全）</p>\r\n', '<p>American brand Hedstrom has a long history of making quality and durable hop balls. They are available in interesting patterns that children love. Bouncing on the hop ball provides great vestibular and proprioceptive stimulation to meet the sensory needs of children, while building coordination, balance and motor planning skills. The product can be used indoors or outdoors.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* No air pump is included, you will need to inflate the ball&nbsp; with any manual or electric pump.<br />\r\n* Easy to deflate for storage or usage during travel</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style: Woof Patrol / Frozen / Avengers / Spider-Man<br />\r\n[Please specify the style when placing your order, if you do not specify the style, it will be released randomly]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 40-45cm high after inflation including handle; mini hop ball approx. 30-35cm in diameter</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Suitable for: children aged 2.5-4 years old (adult supervision is required to ensure safety)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/72_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/72_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/72_3.jpg,assets/products_image/650/72_4.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:18:15', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(73, 3, 0, 'FT12S', '65', '花花片原包 (1400塊)', 'Flower tokens (1400 pieces)', '450.00', 138.66, '<p>USL 品牌花花片可以讓孩子自由創作和組合出不同圖案，提升手指力量、手指遠端控制能力、手眼協調能力... 也可以配合治療膠做不同小肌肉訓練，同時學習數數和顔色概念。台灣製造，使用安全無毒高級塑料，通過台灣ST安全玩具認證。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款色： 50塊（連收納膠盒）/1400塊</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：直徑約 2.5厘米</p>\r\n\r\n<p>顏色： 紅藍黃綠白<br />\r\n<br />\r\n建議使用年齡：3 歲以上兒童 （請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n', '<p>USL flower tokens allow children to create different patterns to improve finger strength, distal finger control, eye-hand coordination, etc. They can also be used with therapy putty to train different small muscles while learning counting and sorting colour at the same time. Made in Taiwan with safe and non-toxic plastic. Certified by Taiwan ST Toys.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Quantity: 50 pieces (with storage box) / 1400 pieces</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: approx. 2.5cm diameter</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: Red, Blue, Yellow, Green and White</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(Please use under parental supervision to avoid choking risk)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/73_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/73_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/73_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:18:31', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(74, 3, 0, 'FT13', '70', '橡皮釘板', 'Geoboard with rubber bands', '68.00', 25.10, '<p>USL 品牌橡皮釘板可以讓孩子自由創作和組合出不同圖案，訓練手指力量、手指遠端控制能力、手眼協調能力... 也能同時學習空間概念, 提升視覺感知能力。 台灣製造，使用安全無毒高級塑料，通過台灣ST安全玩具認證。 釘板雙面使用 (方形及圓形面），每套包24條彩色橡皮。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：釘板直徑 約 15厘米</p>\r\n\r\n<p>顏色： 紅黃藍綠橙紫 （隨機發放一款）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：4 歲以上兒童 （請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>USL geoboard with rubber bands allows children to create different patterns to build finger strength, distal finger control, and eye-hand coordination, etc. It is also a great way to learn spatial concepts and improve visual perception. Made in Taiwan with safe and non-toxic plastic. Certified by Taiwan ST Toys. The geoboard can be used on both sides (square and circular shape) and each set contains 24 coloured rubber bands.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: diameter of geoboard approx. 15cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: Red, yellow, blue, green, orange, purple (colour in random)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 4 years old and above (Please use under parental supervision to avoid choking risk)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/74_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:20:08', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(75, 10, 0, 'HW20', '115', '加重手腕帶', 'Weighted Wristband', '168.00', 77.69, '<p>以絲絨製成的TTS加重手腕帶，從英國進口，在書寫的過程中提供額外的感官輸入，有助增強手部和手腕的力量、穩定性和意識。這些手腕帶具有可調節的鉤環扣件，可提供恰到好處的定制貼合度。 裡面的填充物為 PVC 顆粒。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>重量：113g （10%誤差）<br />\r\n尺寸；23cm全長 x 4cm 寬<br />\r\n款色：黑色一條</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：一般適合5-14歲學童/ 或按治療師意見使用</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>TTS weighted wristbands imported from the UK are made in velvet which provide additional sensory input when doing handwriting practice, strengthen hand and wrist strength, stability and awareness. These wristbands have adjustable hook and loop fasteners to provide a custom fit for children with different wrist size. The filling is PVC pellets.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Weight: 113g (10% difference)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 23cm full length x 4cm wide</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colour: black</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 5-14 years / or as advised by therapist</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/75_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/75_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:20:08', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
