(77, 3, 0, 'FT18', '35', '積木眼鏡', 'Lego glasses', '35.00', 12.95, '<p>每套包括1個積木眼鏡框和1包小積木，讓孩子可以創造自己獨特的眼鏡設計，發揮無限創意，在過程中好好的運用小手指的技巧，提升手指力量及靈活性。由優質塑料製成。無毒無味，安心使用。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸： 柄長15.2cm，眼鏡寬15.8cm ； 小積木：約1cm直徑</p>\r\n\r\n<p>顏色： 紅/藍/黃&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3 歲以上兒童 （幼兒請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Each set includes 1 pair of lego glasses and 1 small pack of lego which allows children to create their own unique designs and improve finger strength and dexterity in the process. Lego is made from high-quality non-toxic plastic which is safe for children&#39;s use.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: Glasses length 15.2cm, Glasses width 15.8cm;&nbsp; Lego: approx. 1cm diameter</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colour: Red/Blue/Yellow&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above (Please use under parental supervision to avoid choking risk)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/77_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/77_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/77_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:22:41', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
