(81, 10, 0, 'HW25E', '200', '英文書寫磁板 (4件)', 'English Style Magnetic Whiteboard (4 pieces)', '100.00', 43.50, '<p>每款包含4塊台灣成功牌書寫軟性磁白板，正面可用白板筆書寫，背面有磁性，可吸在金屬平面上。 中文版有田字格仔，英文版有橫線，適合教導學童寫字，訓練書寫空間感。 把白板連起來使用，可以書寫短句。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸： 每塊 15x15cm<br />\r\n款式：中文/英文 (一包4塊)&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Each pack contains 4 pieces of magnetic whiteboard designed by Taiwanese brand Success. Children can do handwriting practice on the whiteboard using whiteboard pen and magnets are on the back stick whiteboard on any metal surface. The Chinese version has a grid and the English version has horizontal lines on the whiteboard which makes them ideal for teaching children to practice writing and training their visual spatial ability. Children can write short sentences when using several boards together.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 15x15cm each</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style: Chinese/English (a pack of 4)&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/81_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/81_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/81_3.jpg,assets/products_image/650/81_4.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:25:24', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
