(84, 18, 0, 'SI1', '375', '絨毛震動坐墊', 'Woolen Vibrating Seat Cushion', '350.00', 279.92, '<p>震動坐墊提供震動感覺刺激，滿足感覺需要，紓緩壓力及焦慮，任何年齡人士可以使用。枕頭的外套使用藍色的天鵝絨布料製造，柔軟及透氣，適合敏感肌膚。小型尺寸，方便隨身攜帶，可放在沙發/床/車或輪椅上。需要自行放入2 顆AA電池使用。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n顏色：藍色<br />\r\n尺寸：約30.4cm x 30.4cm</p>\r\n', '<p>The vibrating cushion provides a vibrating sensory stimulus to meet sensory needs. It can relieve stress/anxiety and can be used by people of all ages. The cushion&#39;s cover is made from a blue velvet fabric which is soft and breathable for sensitive skin. Compact size, easy to carry around and can be placed on the sofa/bed/car/wheelchair. Requires 2 AA batteries for use.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colour: Blue</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: approx. 30.4cm x 30.4cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/84_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/84_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:28:23', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(85, 18, 0, 'SI2', '310', '布面震動坐墊', 'Cloth vibrating seat Cushion', '350.00', 262.04, '<p>震動坐墊提供溫和的震動感覺刺激，可以滿足感覺需要，紓緩壓力及焦慮，任何年齡人士可以使用，有效幫助使用者保持專注。小型尺寸，方便隨身攜帶，可放在沙發/床/車或輪椅上。需要放入2 顆AA 電池使用，能提供數小時的震動。柔軟布罩可水洗，但所有其他部件都需要進行局部清潔和消毒。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式及尺寸：<br />\r\nA. 綠色正方形&nbsp; 【約25.4cm x 24.1cmx7.6cm高】<br />\r\nB. 藍色圓形 【約24.2cm 直徑 x 7.6cm高】<br />\r\n* 款式隨機發放，請聯絡我們查詢現貨詳情</p>\r\n', '<p>The vibrating cushion provides a vibrating sensory stimulus to meet sensory needs. It can relieve stress/anxiety and can be used by people of all ages. The cushion&#39;s cover is made from a blue velvet fabric which is soft and breathable for sensitive skin. Compact size, easy to carry around and can be placed on the sofa/bed/car/wheelchair. Requires 2 AA batteries for use. The soft cloth cover is washable but all other parts need to be topically cleaned and disinfected.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A. Green square [approx. 25.4cm x 24.1cm x 7.6cm high<br />\r\nB. Blue Round [approx. 24.2cm diameter x 7.6cm height</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Please contact us for in-stock details.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/85_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/85_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:29:33', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(86, 10, 0, 'HW30', '455', '英文大楷木片組裝黑板學習套', 'Reading and Writing Kit', '218.00', 110.90, '<p>Learning Without tears 品牌美國直送學習套包含各種材料，可以讓孩子以多感官學習，加強字母記憶。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>套裝包括：<br />\r\n木片4條大線，3條大曲線，3條小線，3條小曲線（可以建構出大寫字母）; 木片墊 (1) ; 小黑板 (1) ; 小海綿塊 (2); 小粉筆 (4); 小手使用鉛筆 (2)；大塑料袋 (1)； 使用說明書</p>\r\n\r\n<p>** 可下載電子版使用說明書</p>\r\n\r\n<p>https://shopping.lwtears.com/LWTstore/s/sfsites/c/cms/delivery/<br />\r\nmedia/MCQDG2W7NPCFE25ES2CL6VE7XW7A?recordId=01t4V00<br />\r\n0007a2qA&amp;buyerId=3K04V0000010wJl</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童</p>\r\n', '<p>This reading and writing kit designed by US brand Learning Without tears. It includes a variety of tools which provide multisensory input and enhance learning of alphabets.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Set includes:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>13 wood pieces: 4 Big Lines, 3 Big Curves, 3 Little Lines, 3 Little Curves.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4 large lines of wooden pieces, 3 large curved lines, 3 small lines, 3 small curved lines (to form capital letters); mat for wood pieces (1); small chalkboard (1); small sponge (2); small chalk (4); pencil for small hands (2); large plastic bag (1); instruction manual</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>** Instruction manual for download:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>https://shopping.lwtears.com/LWTstore/s/sfsites/c/cms/delivery/</p>\r\n\r\n<p>media/MCQDG2W7NPCFE25ES2CL6VE7XW7A?recordId=01t4V00</p>\r\n\r\n<p>0007a2qA&amp;buyerId=3K04V0000010wJl</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/86_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/86_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:29:40', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(87, 3, 0, 'FT21', '35', '綁鞋帶紙板', 'Shoe Lacing Board', '12.00', 2.80, '<p>練習綁鞋帶的雙面紙板， 訓練孩子手眼協調和雙手協調， 提升自理能力。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>一面色彩繽紛，一面則為黑白，可以讓孩子填上自己喜歡的顏色。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式：球鞋（圖左）/ 布鞋 （圖右）【款色隨機發放】</p>\r\n\r\n<p>如購買數量為2，將會發放同款鞋子紙板</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：18cm長</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：5歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Double-sided shoe lacing board designed for children to practice tying shoelaces in training their eye-hand coordination and enhancing self-care ability. One side is colour printed and the other side is black and white that children do their own colouring.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style: Sneakers (picture on the left) / Canvas shoes (picture on the right) [type of shoes sent in random]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You will receive the lacing board of the same style if you purchase a quantity of 2</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 18cm long</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 5 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/87_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/87_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/87_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:29:55', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(88, 18, 0, 'SI3', '1210', '觸感平衡坐墊', 'Tactile Balance Cushion', '218.00', 120.00, '<p>GOMA品牌台灣製造平衡墊，可用於訓練平衡力和協調。雙面可用，尖刺表面滿足觸感刺激，提升安坐能力。也可以用作背墊，舒緩背部壓力。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>圓形直徑：34 cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>The GOMA balance cushions is made in Taiwan. It can be used to train balance and coordination. The spiked surface provides tactile stimulation and enhances siting tolerance. Can also be used as a back cushion to relieve back pressure.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Round diameter: 34 cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/88_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/88_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:30:43', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(89, 3, 0, 'FT24', '125', '彩色粗雪條棍 (50支)', 'Multi-coloured Wooden Craft Sticks (50 sticks)', '15.00', 4.60, '<p>50 支1.8 cm 粗彩色雪條棍，是進行各種 DIY 的好材料。使用環保優質原木製造。除了做手工外，也可以用來進行仿砌圖型、畫隧道等訓練寫前技巧的活動。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n顏色：紅橙黃綠藍紫 (共50支)<br />\r\n尺寸：15cm長</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>50 x 1.8 cm width multi-coloured wooden craft sticks are great for all kinds of DIY. Made from environmentally friendly, high-quality wood. They can also be used for copying patterns, drawing tunnels and other pre-writing activities apart from doing crafts.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: Red, Orange, Yellow, Green, Blue, Purple (50 sticks in total)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 15cm long</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/89_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:31:40', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(90, 18, 0, 'SI10', '1800', '火山搖搖椅', 'Weplay Volcano rocking chair', '720.00', 555.00, '<p>Weplay 火山搖搖椅，台灣製造，造型如小火山，底部圓弧設計，可以360度搖擺旋轉。搖搖椅可以提供前庭覺刺激，滿足孩子感覺需要，提升安坐及專注能力。坐在搖搖椅上，需要用到核心肌肉力量保持平衡。成人也能使用搖搖椅放鬆因久坐而緊繃的肌肉。建議在地墊上使用。<br />\r\n* 以上產品照片及描述來至Weplay 官方網站</p>\r\n\r\n<p>承重：60 KG ；商品重量：1.85 KG<br />\r\n包裝尺寸： 長38.2x寬38.2x高32.5 (cm)<br />\r\n包裝重量： 2.7 KG<br />\r\n商品尺寸：直徑35.7cm &times; 高30cm，座位直徑26.2cm<br />\r\n商品材質：PE</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>通過歐盟CE產品品質認證與美國ASTM安規</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p>he Weplay Volcano Rocking chair is made in Taiwan. It is shaped like a small volcano with a rounded base that can be swung 360 degrees. The rocking chair provides vestibular stimulation to meet the child&#39;s sensory needs that improves sitting tolerance and concentration. Sitting in the rocking chair requires core muscles to maintain balance. Adults can also use the rocking</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/90_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/90_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/90_3.jpg,assets/products_image/650/90_4.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:32:20', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(91, 3, 0, 'FT28 ', '45', '小掃把套裝', 'Mini Dustpan Set with Brush', '12.00', 1.60, '<p>小掃把套裝，鼓勵孩子自己進行打掃工作，提升從事日常生活活動的獨立性。使用小掃把清潔桌面/地板/抽屜&hellip;各個地方，同時訓練孩子的雙手及手眼協調能力，是有趣而實際的訓練活動！ 邊緣光滑不傷手，邊緣有掛鉤，收納方便。</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n顏色：紅/綠/藍 (隨機發放一款)<br />\r\n尺寸：小掃把 約17cmx11cm ； 垃圾鏟 約19cmx13cm</p>\r\n', '<p>Mini dustpan set with brush encourages children to do their own cleaning to promote their independence in everyday activities. They can use it to clean the table/ drawer or sweep the floor in building up their bilateral hand and eye-hand coordination. Soft grip to ensure safety and with hanging hole for storage purposes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: red/green/blue (colour sent in random)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: brush approx. 17cmx11cm; dustpan approx. 19cmx13cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/91_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:32:47', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(92, 10, 0, 'HW10', '15', '叉叉筆', 'Twist N Write Pen', '28.00', 21.32, '<p>叉叉筆是一支自動鉛筆。擁有特別的外形，為孩子書寫帶來樂趣和娛樂性。每邊末端有2個橡皮擦，可以把筆痕刷去。 符合人體工程學的三腳架手柄，改善執筆姿勢，同時減輕書寫壓力。需要時用磨筆芯器把筆芯磨尖使用。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>顏色：粉紅/藍/綠/紫 （隨機款式1支），裏面已包含一支筆芯<br />\r\n建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童</p>\r\n', '<p>This Twist N Write Pen comes with a special design to make handwriting fun for children. It comes with 2 erasers on the end of each side to remove to easy erase pencil mark. The wishbone shaped design also facilitate children in learning tripod grasp for holding a pencil while reducing stress on the hand. Pencil lead can be sharpened using pencil sharpeners when needed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: pink/blue/green/purple (colour to be sent in random), a pencil lead included</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 3 years and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/92_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/92_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:32:53', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(93, 18, 0, 'SI11', '000', '搖滾威力平衡板', 'Weplay Rocking Balance Board', '920.00', 768.00, '<p>Weplay搖滾威力平衡板以魚躍龍門為設計概念，台灣製造，符合人體工學設計，適合幼兒坐立或站立，進行平衡搖擺遊戲，提供前庭覺刺激。平衡板底部波浪突起設計，加強幼兒在搖擺時的震動感，促進孩子觸覺感知的發展。可用於障礙賽時踩踏，提升幼兒動作計劃能力。<br />\r\n* 以上產品照片及描述來至Weplay 官方網站</p>\r\n\r\n<p>重量：1.5 KG ；商品材質：PE<br />\r\n尺寸：長62cm &times; 寬39.5cm &times; 高17cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>★ 通過歐盟CE產品品質認證與美國ASTM安規</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>The Weplay Rocking Balance Board is designed with the concept of a fish leaping over a dragon gate and is made in Taiwan. Its ergonomic design makes it suitable for children to sit or stand and play balance rocking games, providing vestibular stimulation. The wave design at the bottom of the board enhances the child&#39;s sense of vibration when swinging . This promotes the child&#39;s tactile sensory development. Can be used for stepping during obstacle courses to enhance children&#39;s motor planning skills.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Photos and descriptions above are from the official Weplay website</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Weight: 1.5 KG; Material: PE<br />\r\nSize: 62cm long &times; 39.5cm wide &times; 17cm high<br />\r\n★ CE certified and ASTM certified</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/93_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/93_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/93_3.jpg,assets/products_image/650/93_4.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:33:23', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(94, 18, 0, 'SI13 ', '790', '比力寶旋轉盤子', 'Bilibo Spinning Disc', '450.00', 322.00, '<p>MOLUK 瑞士品牌的比力寶旋轉盤子屢獲殊榮，由兒童發展專家設計。坐在旋轉盤子裡面旋轉，滿足前庭覺刺激。或用一條線綁住，家長幫忙拉著走，就成了有趣的滑板車。將盤子反蓋在地上，跳上跳下、單腳站上去、玩「石頭過河」的遊戲，訓練動作計劃及平衡力。小朋友用旋轉盤子蓋住頭部，雙眼從兩個洞洞看出去，玩你追我跑遊戲。比力寶盤子像一個龜殼，放在背部，一起來裝扮成小烏龜來一場爬行比賽。另外，盤子同時可以成為玩沙玩水的好工具。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n顏色：嬰兒粉、夢幻紫、冰河藍、薄荷綠</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：39x39x22cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>重量：750g</p>\r\n\r\n<p>材料：HD-PE，即使在低溫下也耐久且抗衝擊。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>不含BPA，不含鄰苯二甲酸酯，不含乳膠 100％可回收</p>\r\n\r\n<p>耐重：80公斤(Kg)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>The award-winning MOLUK Swiss brand Billibo spinning discs are designed by child development experts. Sitting inside the spinning disc, is a great way to satisfy vestibular needs. Tie it with a cord and let parents help pull it along for a fun scooter board race. Place the disc on the floor upside down and jump up and down, stand on one foot and play &#39;rock crossing&#39; to develop motor planning and balance. Children use the rotatingdisc to cover their heads and look through the two holes to play chase and run. The Billibo disc resembles the shell of a turtle and can be placed on the back for a turtle crawling race . The disc is also a great tool for playing in the sand and water.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: Baby Pink, Dreamy Purple, Glacier Blue, Mint Green</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 39x39x22cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Weight: 750g</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Material: HD-PE, durable and impact resistant even at low temperatures.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>BPA free, phthalate free, latex free 100% recyclable</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Weight resistance: 80kg (Kg)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/94_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/94_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/94_3.jpg,assets/products_image/650/94_4.jpg,assets/products_image/650/94_5.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:34:29', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(95, 10, 0, 'HW10R', '10', '叉叉筆筆芯', 'Twist N Write Pencil Lead', '40.00', 15.80, '<p>叉叉筆替換筆芯。一盒有5 支筆芯 [2毫米]，包括插入筆芯的工具和說明。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n叉叉筆是一支自動鉛筆。擁有特別的外形，為孩子書寫帶來樂趣和娛樂性。每邊末端有2個橡皮擦，可以把筆痕刷去。 符合人體工程學的三腳架手柄，改善執筆姿勢，同時減輕書寫壓力。需要時用磨筆芯器把筆芯磨尖使用。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童</p>\r\n', '<p>Pencil lead for Twist N Write Pencil. A box of 5 [2mm], including the tool and instructions to replace the lead.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This Twist N Write Pen comes with a special design to make handwriting fun for children. It comes with 2 erasers on the end of each side to remove to easy erase pencil mark. The wishbone shaped design also facilitate children in learning tripod grasp for holding a pencil while reducing stress on the hand. Pencil lead can be sharpened using pencil sharpeners when needed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 3 years and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/95_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:35:22', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(96, 10, 0, 'HW12', '190', '震震筆', 'Squiggle Wiggle Pen', '168.00', 89.10, '<p>Hart toys 震震筆是一支較重的振動原子筆，振動感覺非常有趣，能引起孩子對書寫的興趣，並在遊戲中愉快學習。同時能帶給孩子本體感和動感，滿足感覺需要。學習寫字的時候，運用不同感官方法能協助孩子更容易認字。而震震筆三角形的握筆位置，符合人體工學設計，能訓練前三指手指力，改善執筆姿勢，同時改善筆控能力。 特別適合寫字不夠力/字體不工整的孩子使用。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>顏色： 紅/藍/紫/綠（隨機款式1支），每套各配有5色筆芯<br />\r\n<br />\r\n建議使用年齡：4歲以上</p>\r\n', '<p>This squiggle wiggle pen designed by Hart Toys is a battery operated vibrating pen which makes writing practice fun for children. It can also provide proprioception and sensory stimulation for children, which makes it easier for children to learn handwriting by utilizing different senses. The triangular design enables a firmer grasp of the pencil, strengthen the first three fingers strength and improve pencil grip and pencil control. It is particularly suitable for children who have weak pencil grip or have poor handwriting skills.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: Red/Blue/Purple/Green (colour to be sent in random), each set comes with lead in 5 colours</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 4 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/96_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/96_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:38:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(97, 4, 0, 'FC1', '135', '機械手臂玩具夾', 'Robot Toy Grabber', '75.00', 26.00, '<p>機械手臂玩具夾用優質塑料製造，拉動把手的扳機，機器爪就會合上夾起物件。此活動可以訓練孩子的上肢力量，手握力及手眼協調能力等等。 力度不足的孩子可以先用雙手抓握，待能力進步後可用單手操作。 是非常受孩子歡迎的訓練小玩具！可以配合豆袋/ 乒乓球/ 觸感軟球/絨毛球等配件一同使用，遊戲中有效學習。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：長度 41cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>This robot toy grabber is made from high-quality plastic. By squeezing the handle, the gripper claw closes to pick items up. The use of the grabber can build the children&rsquo;s upper body strength, hand grip strength and eye-hand coordination.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Children who are not strong enough can start by using both hands to use the grabber and then use one hand only as they progress. This is a very popular training toy for children! Can be used with bean bags/ ping pong balls/ tactile balls/ fluffy balls, etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: Length 41cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/97_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:38:34', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(98, 18, 0, 'SI14', '805', '彩色爬行隧道', 'Crawling Tunnel', '380.00', 160.00, '<p>美國進口SweHouse兒童遊戲隧道以 ASTM 認證的低過敏性優質聚酯纖維物料製成，柔軟且抗撕裂。隧道為兒童提供安全探索和鍛煉不同技能的環境。除了來回爬行，也可以玩躲貓貓和各種障礙賽遊戲，發展大肌肉能力、動作計劃、方向感等。​鮮豔的色彩增加多巴胺分泌，培養孩子樂觀和外向的個性。彈簧便攜式設計，容易展開及收納，同時適合戶外/室內使用。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n尺寸：68 x 18 x 18 英吋</p>\r\n', '<p>The US imported SweHouse children&#39;s play tunnel is made from ASTM certified hypoallergenic, high quality polyester material that is soft and tear- resistant. The tunnel provides a safe environment for children to explore and practice different skills. In addition to crawling back and forth, they can also play peek-a-boo and various obstacle courses to develop large muscle skills, motor planning, sense of direction and more. The bright colours increase dopamine production and foster an optimistic and outgoing personality. The spring loaded portable design is easy to expand and store and is suitable for outdoor/indoor use.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 68 x 18 x 18 inches</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/98_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:38:37', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(99, 18, 0, 'SI15', '7550', '太空人訓練轉板', 'Astronaut Board', '3200.00', 2140.00, '<p>進行太空人訓練（Astronaut Training Protocol）使用的旋轉板。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式：軟羊毛墊款/ Vinyl&nbsp;膠面藍色款/ Vinyl&nbsp;膠面紅色款<br />\r\n尺寸：直徑 33吋 x 20吋；高 3吋<br />\r\n重量： 16 磅<br />\r\n可承受重量 : 165 磅</p>\r\n\r\n<p>** 產品價錢已經包含送貨運費</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Rotating board for Astronaut Training Protocol.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Styles: Soft Wool Pad / Vinyl Gel Blue / Vinyl Gel Red</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 33&quot; diameter x 20&quot;; 3&quot; high<br />\r\nWeight: 16 lbs<br />\r\nWeight capacity: 165 lbs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>** Price includes delivery</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/99_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/99_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/99_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:41:33', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(100, 18, 0, 'SI16', '60', '太空人訓練眼睛電筒', 'Eye Torches', '80.00', 29.50, '<p>進行眼球掃視及追蹤等遊戲的專用電筒，燈光柔和。輕輕按著按鈕即可啟動電筒，放手就會關閉。套裝包含2隻半透明怪獸，吸引孩子注意力。怪獸顔色隨機發放。此電筒不能換電。</p>\r\n', '<p>Special torches with soft light&nbsp; for eye saccade and tracking games. Gently press the button to activate the torch and let go to turn it off. The Set includes 2 translucent monsters to attract children&#39;s attention. The colours of the monsters are randomly distributed. This torch cannot be recharged.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/100_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:42:52', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(101, 18, 0, 'SI20S', '330', 'Lycra彈力感官身體襪 (S)', 'Lycra Dynamic Movement Sensory Body Sock   (S)', '328.00', 192.14, '<p>彈力感官身體襪由柔軟高品質布料製成，通過多項美國實驗室測試，環保染料不會引起皮膚刺激。感官身體襪可以提供豐富的觸感及本體感刺激，滿足孩子的感覺需要，增加身體和空間意識，減少好動。在彈力衣中釋放壓力和慢慢嘗試放鬆。適合在冷靜角使用，讓孩子自我調節，令情緒穩定。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：<br />\r\n細碼101cm長 X 68cm闊&nbsp; 適合 3-5歲 （高度：83-106cm） &nbsp;<br />\r\n中碼119cm長X 68cm闊 &nbsp; 適合 6-9歲 （高度：109-129cm） &nbsp;<br />\r\n溫馨提示：<br />\r\n1. 請盡可能購買接近孩子高度的身體襪。切勿購買比孩子大的感官襪。<br />\r\n2. 洗滌時請與其他顏色的衣物分開；可手洗或機洗；<br />\r\n&nbsp; 只能自然晾曬，不能用乾衣機<br />\r\n3. 兒童須在成人監督下使用</p>\r\n', '<p>The stretchy sensory body socks are made from soft, high quality fabric that has been tested in many US laboratories and the environmentally friendly dyes do not cause skin irritation. The sensory body socks provide a rich tactile and proprioceptive stimulus to meet the child&#39;s sensory needs, increase body and spatial awareness and reduce fidgety. Release pressure and slowly try to relax in the stretchy garment. Ideal for use in a calm corner, allowing children to self-regulate and stabilise their emotions.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Small 101cm long X 68cm wide Suitable for 3-5 years (height: 83-106cm) &nbsp;<br />\r\nMedium 119cm long X 68cm wide Suitable for 6-9 years old (Height: 109-129cm)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tips.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. Please buy body socks with size as close to your child&#39;s height as possible. Do not buy sensory socks that are larger than your child.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Wash separately from other colour clothes; hand or machine washable.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/101_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/101_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:44:30', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(102, 8, 0, 'FY1', '200', '洗澡撈魚玩具', 'Fishing Bath Toy Set', '58.00', 21.67, '<p>有很多寶寶都不願意洗澡，所以讓他們洗澡的時光變得有趣非常重要。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>打撈可愛的海洋生物，還可以訓練手眼協調、手指力量等等小肌肉能力。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>用ABS軟膠材料製成，表面光滑無異味。套裝包括撈網一個及7件海洋生物。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>海龜&amp;海獅----- 擠壓會發出叫聲</p>\r\n\r\n<p>八爪魚&amp;海星----- 遇上約38度水溫會變色</p>\r\n\r\n<p>鯊魚&amp;鯨魚----- 會噴水</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：每個海洋生物約有4cm-7.5cm 直徑</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>It is common for toddlers to refuse to take a bath so it is important to make bath time fun for them. Playing with this fishing bath toy set is a great way to train hand-eye coordination, finger strength and other small muscle. Bath toys are smooth in texture and odourless by making from ABS soft plastic. The set includes a fishing net and 7 pieces of sea animal bath toys.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sea turtles &amp; sea lions ----- Squeeze to make a sound</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Octopus &amp; Starfish ----- Colour will change if put in water higher than about 38 degrees</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sharks &amp; Whales ----- spout water</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: Each sea animal bath toy is approximately 4cm - 7.5cm in diameter</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/102_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/102_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/102_3.jpg,assets/products_image/650/102_4.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:46:58', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(103, 18, 0, 'SI20M', '390', 'Lycra彈力感官身體襪 (M)', 'Lycra Dynamic Movement Sensory Body Sock   (M)', '358.00', 216.18, '<p>彈力感官身體襪由柔軟高品質布料製成，通過多項美國實驗室測試，環保染料不會引起皮膚刺激。感官身體襪可以提供豐富的觸感及本體感刺激，滿足孩子的感覺需要，增加身體和空間意識，減少好動。在彈力衣中釋放壓力和慢慢嘗試放鬆。適合在冷靜角使用，讓孩子自我調節，令情緒穩定。 </p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：<br />\r\n細碼101cm長 X 68cm闊  適合 3-5歲 （高度：83-106cm）  <br />\r\n中碼119cm長X 68cm闊   適合 6-9歲 （高度：109-129cm）  <br />\r\n溫馨提示：<br />\r\n1. 請盡可能購買接近孩子高度的身體襪。切勿購買比孩子大的感官襪。<br />\r\n2. 洗滌時請與其他顏色的衣物分開；可手洗或機洗；<br />\r\n  只能自然晾曬，不能用乾衣機<br />\r\n3. 兒童須在成人監督下使用</p>\r\n', '<p>The stretchy sensory body socks are made from soft, high quality fabric that has been tested in many US laboratories and the environmentally friendly dyes do not cause skin irritation. The sensory body socks provide a rich tactile and proprioceptive stimulus to meet the child&#39;s sensory needs, increase body and spatial awareness and reduce fidgety. Release pressure and slowly try to relax in the stretchy garment. Ideal for use in a calm corner, allowing children to self-regulate and stabilise their emotions.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Small 101cm long X 68cm wide Suitable for 3-5 years (height: 83-106cm) &nbsp;<br />\r\nMedium 119cm long X 68cm wide Suitable for 6-9 years old (Height: 109-129cm)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tips.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. Please buy body socks with size as close to your child&#39;s height as possible. Do not buy sensory socks that are larger than your child.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Wash separately from other colour clothes; hand or machine washable.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/103_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/103_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:51:03', '2023-04-16 19:10:04'),
(104, 4, 0, 'FC2', '25', '小手掌矽膠夾', 'Mini Hand-shaped Tongs', '20.00', 8.00, '<p>小手掌矽膠夾適合兒童抓握，可以夾起冰、糖果、蔬菜、水果、薯片、爆米花、沙律&hellip; 在學習自理同時，訓練小肌肉。 使用高品質不鏽鋼製成，搭配環保矽膠手小手掌頭，安全、防鏽、易於清潔。迷你尺寸和重量輕，特別適合攜帶去戶外野餐使用。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式：藍、綠、紅、紫、橙 (隨機發放一款)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：約 13 cm x 3cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>The mini hand-shaped tongs is suitable for children to grip ice, candy, vegetables, fruits, chips, popcorn, salad, etc. It can enhance the self-care ability of children and train small hand muscles at the same time. Made from high-quality stainless steel and eco-friendly silicone. It is safe, stain resistant and easy to clean. The mini size and light weight make it ideal for use in picnics.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style: Blue, Green, Red, Purple, Orange (colour sent in random)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: approx. 13 cm x 3 cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 3 years and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/104_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/104_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/104_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:51:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(105, 4, 0, 'FC4', '10', '八爪魚膠夾 ', 'Octopus Tweezers', '12.00', 3.00, '<p>利用USL品牌八爪魚膠夾夾小物，可以鍛煉幼兒精細的小肌肉技能，並建立成熟的手指抓握，同時訓練手眼協調能力。 有5種不同顏色可選，為遊戲和訓練活動加添趣味。使用安全無毒高級塑料製造，台灣製造，通過台灣商檢局認證。可以配合絨毛球/小橡皮等配件一同使用，遊戲中有效學習。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：9.5x2x3厘米</p>\r\n\r\n<p>顏色： 粉紅/綠/黃/藍/紫 (隨機發放一款)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：2歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Using USL octopus tweezers to pick up small objects can improve children&rsquo;s small muscle skills to develop mature finger grasp and develop hand-eye coordination. Available in 5 different colours. Made in Taiwan with safe and non-toxic plastic and certified by the Taiwan BSMI. Can be used with other toys such as fluffy balls / small rubber bands to promote effective learning.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 9.5x2x3 cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: Pink/Green/Yellow/Blue/Purple (colour to be sent in random)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 2 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/105_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/105_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/105_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:53:04', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(106, 18, 0, 'SI22', '60', '椅子帶（兩條）', 'Chair Elastic Bands (a set of 2)', '68.00', 19.99, '<p>只需在椅子的前兩腳圍上這些拉開的彈力帶，能夠讓兒童在坐下時透過不同踏法獲取動覺刺激，豐富的本體感覺能夠提昇安坐能力，改善專注，減輕焦慮。特別適合有感統失調，過度活躍症，專注力缺乏，自閉症等的有特殊學習需要的兒童使用。簡單的一條椅子彈力帶，是課室和家中的好幫手。適合任何椅子尺寸。方便安裝和替換。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n彈力帶在完全伸展下可達70cm長。但為安全起見，不建議安裝到完全伸展狀態 （安全伸展範圍~50cm）。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>一套2條</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>These stretchy bands are simply placed around the front legs of the chair, allowing the child to receive kinesthetic stimulation through stimulation during sitting. The rich proprioceptive sensations enhance the ability to sit, improve concentration and reduce anxiety. It is particularly suitable for children with special learning needs such as sensory disorders, hyperactivity disorder, attention deficit disorder and autism. A simple chair elastic band is a great tool in classroom and home Fits any chair size. Easy to install and replace.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The elastic strap is up to 70cm long when fully extended. However, for safety reasons, it is not recommended to install it in the fully extended position (safe extension range ~50cm).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>One set includes&nbsp; 2 stretchy bands</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/106_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/106_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/106_3.jpg,assets/products_image/650/106_4.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:53:29', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(107, 8, 0, 'FY5', '350', '雞蛋形狀配對玩具', 'Egg Shape Matching Toy', '288.00', 128.00, '<p>全套12個雞蛋，有12款不同形狀和鮮豔的顏色，孩子們可以輕鬆拆開並拼砌一起，學習排序和配對。雞蛋形狀非常適合小手指抓握，訓練雙手及手眼協調。產品用高品質材料製成，不含雙酚 A，由 CPSC 認可的實驗室根據 ASTM標準進行測試，經久耐用，兒童使用安全。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：1.5歲以上</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>A set of 12 eggs with 12 different shapes and colours that children can easily take it out and put together for matching or sorting exercises. The egg shape is perfect for training tripod grasp and developing hand-eye coordination. Made from high-quality materials, this product is BPA-free and tested by a laboratory accredited by CPSC according to ASTM standards. It is safe and durable for children&rsquo;s use.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 1.5 years and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/107_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/107_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:53:42', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(108, 4, 0, 'FC4S', '40', '八爪魚膠夾 (5件)', 'Octopus Tweezers (5 pieces)', '50.00', 15.00, '<p>利用USL品牌八爪魚膠夾夾小物，可以鍛煉幼兒精細的小肌肉技能，並建立成熟的手指抓握，同時訓練手眼協調能力。 有5種不同顏色可選，為遊戲和訓練活動加添趣味。使用安全無毒高級塑料製造，台灣製造，通過台灣商檢局認證。可以配合絨毛球/小橡皮等配件一同使用，遊戲中有效學習。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：9.5x2x3厘米</p>\r\n\r\n<p>顏色： 粉紅/綠/黃/藍/紫 (隨機發放一款)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：2歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Using USL octopus tweezers to pick up small objects can improve children&rsquo;s small muscle skills to develop mature finger grasp and develop hand-eye coordination. Available in 5 different colours. Made in Taiwan with safe and non-toxic plastic and certified by the Taiwan BSMI. Can be used with other toys such as fluffy balls / small rubber bands to promote effective learning.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 9.5x2x3 cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: Pink/Green/Yellow/Blue/Purple (colour to be sent in random)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 2 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/108_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/108_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/108_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:55:27', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(109, 8, 0, 'FY6', '480', '恐龍配對玩具', 'Dinosaur Matching Toy', '258.00', 184.00, '<p>可以按顏色、物種或背面印刷的形狀，對這些兩件式恐龍進行排序和匹配。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>孩子們可以輕鬆拆開並拼砌一起，搭配成幾乎無窮無盡的組合。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>專為小孩子而設計，適合幼兒使用，訓練雙手及手眼協調等精細運動技能。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：1.5歲以上</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Dinosaur matching toys come in pairs that children can do sorting or matching based on their colour, types of dinosaurs or patterns printed on the dinosaurs.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Children can use their imagination to create numerous combinations. Suitable for toddlers to use in developing fine motor skills and hand-eye coordination.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 1.5 years or above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/109_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/109_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/109_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:56:25', '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
INSERT INTO `product` (`id`, `category_id`, `store_id`, `product_code`, `product_weight`, `p_name`, `p_name_en`, `product_price`, `cost`, `description`, `description_en`, `p_image`, `status`, `inserted_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(110, 18, 0, 'SI30', '650', '數字保齡球', 'Foam Bowling Toy Set', '368.00', 160.92, '<p>數字保齡球玩具套裝由無毒安全的 PU泡棉材料製成, 適合孩子進行手眼協調及空間感訓練的室內玩具。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸 保齡球樽：17.8cm高；保齡球 7.6cm 直徑</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>The number bowling set is made of non-toxic and safe PU foam material and is suitable for children&#39;s hand-eye coordination and spatial awareness training.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dimensions Bowling bottle: 17.8cm high; bowling ball 7.6cm diameter</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/110_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/110_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:56:29', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(111, 18, 0, 'SI31', '160', '豆袋4色', 'Beanbag Set (4 colours)', '75.00', 38.67, '<p>GOMA四色豆袋為康文署規格豆袋，適合進行拋接協調訓練，也可以配合其他負重遊戲玩耍。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸： 10 X 15CM ; 重量約110g<br />\r\n顏色：紅、藍、黃、綠各一個</p>\r\n', '<p>The GOMA 4-colour bean bags ( Leisure and Cultural Services Department standard) are suitable for throwing and catching coordination training, or for playing with other weighted games.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 10 X 15CM; weight approx. 110g</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: red, blue, yellow and green</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/111_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:58:22', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(112, 8, 0, 'FY11', '930', '切水果蔬菜玩具', 'Fruits and Vegetables Cutting Toy Set', '298.00', 190.55, '<p>玩具由安全環保的材料製成，邊緣光滑。套裝包含5 種不同顏色的 19 件水果/蔬菜、5 個籃子、2 把玩具刀和一塊砧板。玩具配件可以拆開和組裝， 增強孩子的手部力量並改善手眼協調能力，同時培養食物基礎詞彙認識、顏色識別和分類技能，學習早期數學計算。 適合訓練小肌肉、認知、玩假裝互動遊戲。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：食物配件直徑 3.5cm-12cm；砧板13.5cmx8cm；刀子3cmx13.5cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>適合：3 歲以上兒童 （幼兒請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>This toy set is made from safe and eco-friendly material. The set includes 19 pieces of fruit or vegetable in 5 different colours, 5 baskets, 2 toy knives and a chopping board. Cutting and the ability to stick fruits and vegetables back together helps children to build motor skills and hand-eye coordination. They can also build basic vocabulary about fruits and vegetables, colour recognition, sorting skills and learn basic calculations. Also ideal for small muscle and cognitive training and pretend play.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: fruit or vegetable toys 3.5cm-12cm diameter; chopping board 13.5cmx8cm; knife 3cmx13.5cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Suitable for: children aged 3 years and above (please use under parental supervision to avoid choking hazard)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/112_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/112_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/112_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 15:59:56', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(113, 18, 0, 'SI32', '290', '老虎不倒翁', 'Inflatable Blow Up Punching Bag', '80.00', 20.65, '<p>Intex充氣袋使用食品級PVC 無毒環保材料製成，充氣後會變成一個不倒翁，成為投擲的目標。也可以讓孩子搬運和推動，提供本體感刺激，訓練大肌肉能力。是舒服情緒的好幫手！ 尺寸：98cm高 x 44cm 寬。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>使用方法：<br />\r\n1. 先充入少部份氣體<br />\r\n2. 往底部的水袋，裝滿水/沙子/米等物料，再緊閉蓋子<br />\r\n3. 往水袋充入7-8成氣體</p>\r\n\r\n<p>** 注意：請勿把氣體充滿後再往底部水袋加入水，會令充氣袋無法站立或不能使用！<br />\r\n** 注意：請勿用尖銳物品刺中充氣袋/以過份暴力毆打充氣袋，以免破損！</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Intex inflatable bags are made from food grade PVC non-toxic and environmentally friendly material. It can also be moved and pushed by the child, providing proprioceptive stimulation and training gross motor skills. Great for emotional comfort! Size: 98cm high x 44cm wide.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>How to use.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. Fill with a small amount of gas first<br />\r\n2. Fill the bottom water bag&nbsp; with water/sand/rice etc. and close the lid tightly<br />\r\n3. Fill the water bag with 70-80% gas.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>**Note: Do not fully fill the inflatable bag bag with gas and then add water , as this may make the bag unstable or unusable!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>** Caution: Do not pierce the inflatable bag with sharp objects/beat it with excessive violence to avoid damage!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children over 3 years old</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/113_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/113_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 16:00:32', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(114, 4, 0, 'FC6', '15', '鱷魚夾', 'Crocodile Tweezers', '18.00', 9.00, '<p>Learning resources鱷魚夾，這些專門為小肌肉技巧訓練打造的夾子可以有效鍛煉精細的小肌肉技能並建立成熟的前三指抓握。鱷魚造型為遊戲和訓練活動加添趣味。可以配合絨毛球/小橡皮等配件一同使用，遊戲中有效學習。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：8.5cm長 x 4cm 寬</p>\r\n\r\n<p>顏色：紅/橙/黃/綠/藍/紫 (隨機發放一款)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：2歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Learning resources crocodile tweezers are specifically designed for small muscle training to build a mature tripod grasp. The crocodile shape adds fun to the training. Can be used with other toys such as fluffy balls / small rubber bands to promote effective learning.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 8.5cm long x 4cm wide</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: Red/Orange/Yellow/Green/Blue/Purple (colour to be sent in random)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 2 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/114_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/114_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/114_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 16:01:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(115, 18, 0, 'SI35', '370', '瑜珈轉盤遊戲', 'Yoga Spinner', '228.00', 120.00, '<p>遊戲包含54張瑜珈姿勢卡片，一個附帶收納小格的轉盤，可以以個人或團隊形式進行遊戲。遊戲前先熱身和拉筋。旋轉轉盤，按照相應的瑜伽姿勢卡片擺出姿勢10 秒鐘，就可以保留卡片。按圖卡做出不同瑜珈姿勢，能訓練平衡、協調、動作計劃、核心肌肉力量等等。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>產品曾獲得創意兒童雜誌精選獎；2016 年玩具展經過父母測試、父母認可的首選玩具。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>The game includes 54 yoga posture cards and a spinner with a small storage compartment. The game can be played individually or in teams. Do some warm up and stretching before play. Spin the reels and follow the corresponding yoga pose cards for 10 seconds to keep the cards. Perform different yoga postures according to the cards to build balance, coordination, movement planning, core muscle strength and more.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Winner of the Creative Child Magazine Award; Parent Tested and Parent Approved Preferred Toy at Toy Fair 2016.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/115_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/115_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/115_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 16:02:25', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(116, 8, 0, 'FY16', '805', '電鑽扭螺絲玩具', 'Drill Toy Set', '298.00', 100.63, '<p>Educational Insights 的電鑽扭螺絲玩具是訓練小肌肉的好幫手！ 遊戲中訓練孩子的手腕控制、手指力量、手指靈活性和手眼協調能力。 也可以使用附送的設計卡片,或創造自己的圖案和形狀，同時訓練視覺空間。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>套裝包括：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. 19.1cm x 19.1cm 設計板</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. 電動鑽頭 （需要自行入3 顆AAA電池）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. 十字鑽頭的迷你螺絲刀</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. 五張雙面圖案卡</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. 50 個彩色螺絲</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童（幼兒請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n', '<p>Educational Insights&#39; electric drill toy set is great for building small muscles! The game can improve wrist control, finger strength, finger dexterity and hand-eye coordination. Children can also use the included pattern cards or create their own patterns and shapes to train visual perception ability at the same time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Set includes:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. 19.1cm x 19.1cm design board</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Electric drill (3 x AAA batteries required)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. Mini screwdriver&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. Five double-sided pattern cards</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. 50 coloured bolts</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 3 years and above (please use under parental supervision to avoid choking hazard)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/116_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/116_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 16:03:31', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(117, 8, 0, 'FY20', '625', '疊疊熱香餅玩具', 'Pancake Pile-up', '258.00', 132.28, '<p>遊戲中玩家需要按照訂單卡片堆疊並端出鬆餅，訓練孩子的專注及反應，學習順序及數數，加強前臂和手腕控制、手眼協調能力。比賽社交模式：用鏟子托著熱香餅跑到自己的盤子上堆疊，完成後跑回來將鏟子遞給下一個玩家接力。 正確地完成一疊熱香餅，然後加上牛油在頂上就贏了！</p>\r\n\r\n<p>此玩具獲得專業玩具獎Oppenheim Toy Portfolio awards和Parents&rsquo; Choice Awards家長選擇獎。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>配件：</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 10個熱香餅 （5種口味）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 2份牛油</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 2個盤子</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 2個熱香餅鏟</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 10張訂單卡</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童（請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>The game requires players to stack and serve pancakes according to the order cards which trains children&#39;s attention, processing speed and learn counting and sequencing. It can also strengthen children&rsquo;s forearm and wrist control and hand-eye coordination. This game can be played in two teams that the first player use the spatula to hold the pancake and start stacking it on the plate. Pass the spatula to the second player after finishing stacking. The first team to correctly complete their stack wins the game!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This toy has received the Oppenheim Toy Portfolio Awards and the Parents&#39; Choice Awards.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Set includes:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 10 pancakes (in 5 flavours)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 2 servings of butter</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 2 plates</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 2 spatulas</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 10 order cards</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 3+ (please use under parental supervision to avoid swallowing)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/117_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/117_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 16:05:27', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(118, 4, 0, 'FC6S', '215', '鱷魚夾 (12件)', 'Crocodile Tweezers(12 pieces)', '190.00', 106.60, '<p>Learning resources鱷魚夾，這些專門為小肌肉技巧訓練打造的夾子可以有效鍛煉精細的小肌肉技能並建立成熟的前三指抓握。鱷魚造型為遊戲和訓練活動加添趣味。可以配合絨毛球/小橡皮等配件一同使用，遊戲中有效學習。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：8.5cm長 x 4cm 寬</p>\r\n\r\n<p>顏色：紅/橙/黃/綠/藍/紫 (隨機發放一款)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：2歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Learning resources crocodile tweezers are specifically designed for small muscle training to build a mature tripod grasp. The crocodile shape adds fun to the training. Can be used with other toys such as fluffy balls / small rubber bands to promote effective learning.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 8.5cm long x 4cm wide</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: Red/Orange/Yellow/Green/Blue/Purple (colour to be sent in random)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 2 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/118_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/118_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/118_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 17:19:30', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(119, 4, 0, 'FC7', '20', '爆谷夾', 'Popcorn Tongs', '48.00', 21.50, '<p>不再使用沈悶方法練習執筆！ 這款Learning resources 爆谷夾可以在&ldquo;無筆&rdquo;狀態下輕鬆學習及鍛鍊執筆技巧，強化前三指肌力，提昇小肌肉技巧，可以配合絨毛球/動物膠粒/小橡皮等配件一同使用，遊戲中有效學習。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：11cm長x3.5cm寬</p>\r\n\r\n<p>顏色：紅/橙/黃/綠/藍/紫(隨機發放一款)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3.5歲以上學童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>No more boring pencil control exercises! This Learning resources popcorn tongs make it easy to learn and practice pencil control without a pen by strengthening the tripod grasp and improving small muscle strength. Can be used with other toys such as fluffy balls / animal beads/ small rubber bands to promote effective learning.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 11cm long x 3.5cm wide</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: Red/Orange/Yellow/Green/Blue/Purple (colour to be sent in random)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3.5 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/119_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/119_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/119_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 17:21:16', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(120, 19, 0, 'PDMS3 ', '0', 'PDMS-3運動發育量表評估測試工具', 'PDMS-3 Motor Development Scale Assessment Test Tool', '9180.00', 6550.00, '<p>Peabody 運動發育量表 - 第三版 (PDMS-3) 是一項兒童早期運動發育測試，可提供大小肌肉發展的深入評估。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>年齡：出生到 5 歲 11 個月</p>\r\n\r\n<p>測試時間：60-90 分鐘</p>\r\n\r\n<p>發布年份： 2023年5月開售（最新版本）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*評估員需擁有專業資格</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>到貨期：4-6星期</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>The Peabody Motor Development Scale - Third Edition (PDMS-3) is an early childhood motor development test that provides an in-depth assessment of fine and gross motor development.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Age: Birth to 5 years and 11 months</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Testing time: 60-90 minutes</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Year of release: Available in May 2023 (latest version)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*Assessor must be professionally qualified</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Delivery time:4-6 weeks</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/120_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 17:21:21', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(121, 19, 0, 'BOT2', '0', 'BOT-2動作能力測驗', 'BOT-2 Motor Ability Test', '12500.00', 9562.00, '<p>評估視覺動作能力的整合。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>評估時間：短&nbsp;- 15-20 分鐘，完整&nbsp;- 45-60 分鐘</p>\r\n\r\n<p>小肌肉部分 - 25-30 分鐘，大肌肉部分 25-30 分鐘</p>\r\n\r\n<p>適用年齡：4-21歲</p>\r\n\r\n<p>發布年份： 2005&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*評估員需擁有專業資格</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>到貨期：4-12星期</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Assessment of integration of visual motor skills.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Assessment time: short - 15-20 minutes, complete - 45-60 minutes</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Small muscle component - 25-30 minutes, large muscle component 25-30 minutes</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Age: 4-21 years old</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Year of release: 2005&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*Assessor must be professionally qualified</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/121_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 17:22:41', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(122, 4, 0, 'FC7S', '130', '爆谷夾 (6件)', 'Popcorn Tongs(6 pieces)', '260.00', 103.90, '<p>不再使用沈悶方法練習執筆！ 這款Learning resources 爆谷夾可以在&ldquo;無筆&rdquo;狀態下輕鬆學習及鍛鍊執筆技巧，強化前三指肌力，提昇小肌肉技巧，可以配合絨毛球/動物膠粒/小橡皮等配件一同使用，遊戲中有效學習。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：11cm長x3.5cm寬</p>\r\n\r\n<p>顏色：紅/橙/黃/綠/藍/紫(隨機發放一款)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3.5歲以上學童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>No more boring pencil control exercises! This Learning resources popcorn tongs make it easy to learn and practice pencil control without a pen by strengthening the tripod grasp and improving small muscle strength. Can be used with other toys such as fluffy balls / animal beads/ small rubber bands to promote effective learning.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 11cm long x 3.5cm wide</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: Red/Orange/Yellow/Green/Blue/Purple (colour to be sent in random)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3.5 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/122_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/122_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/122_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 17:23:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(123, 19, 0, 'VMI', '0', 'Beery VMI  視覺—動作統合發展測驗', 'Beery VMI visual-motor integration development test', '2380.00', 1690.00, '<p>測試視覺感知和手部運動的整合及協調能力。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>評估時間：10 - 15 分鐘 ；補充視覺感知和運動協調測試：每個 5 分鐘適用年齡：2 至 100 歲 （完整）；2 至 7 年歲（簡表）<br />\r\n發布年份： 2010</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*評估員需擁有專業資格</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>到貨期：4-12星期</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Tests visual perception and hand-motor integration and coordination.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Assessment time: 10 - 15 minutes; supplemental visual perception and motor coordination tests: 5 minutes each<br />\r\nApplicable ages: 2 to 100 years old (complete); 2 to 7 years old (short form)<br />\r\nYear of release: 2010</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*Assessor must be professionally qualified</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Delivery time:4-12 weeks</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/123_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 17:24:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(124, 19, 0, 'TVPS4', '0', 'TVPS-4 視覺感知評估套裝', 'TVPS-4 Visual Perception Assessment Kit', '2680.00', 1950.00, '<p>評估出受測者視覺感知上的強項與弱項之處。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>評估時間：約25 分鐘</p>\r\n\r\n<p>適用年齡：5-21 歲</p>\r\n\r\n<p>發布年份： 2017&nbsp;（最新版本）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>完整套件包括：手冊、測試板、記錄表 (25份)&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*評估員需擁有專業資格</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>到貨期：4-6星期</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>To assess the strengths and weaknesses of the subject&#39;s visual perception.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Assessment time: approximately 25 minutes</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Age: 5-21 years old</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Year of release: 2017 (latest version)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Whole kit includes: manual, test board, record sheet (25 copies)&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*Assessor must be professionally qualified</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Delivery time: 4-6 weeks</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/124_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 17:25:33', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(125, 19, 0, 'MVPT4', '0', 'MVPT-4 視覺感知測試套裝 ', 'MVPT-4 Visual Perception Test Kit', '2680.00', 1910.00, '<p>為兒童和成人的整體視覺感知能力提供了一種快速、可靠和有效的測量方法。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>評估時間：20 到 25 分鐘</p>\r\n\r\n<p>適用年齡：4 到 80 歲以上</p>\r\n\r\n<p>發布年份： 2015&nbsp;（最新版本）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;完整套件包括：手冊、測試板、記錄表 (25份)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*評估員需擁有專業資格</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>到貨期：4-6星期</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Provides a quick, reliable and valid measure of overall visual perception for children and adults.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Assessment time: 20 to 25 minutes</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Age: 4 to 80+ years</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Year of release: 2015 (latest version)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Whole kit includes: manual, test board, record sheet (25 copies)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*Assessor must be professionally qualified</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Delivery time: 4-6 weeks</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/125_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 17:27:05', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(126, 19, 0, 'DVPT ', '0', 'DVPT-3視覺感知測試套裝 ', 'DVPT-3 Visual Perception Test Kit', '4080.00', 2600.00, '<p>為兒童的整體視覺感知能力提供了一種快速、可靠和有效的測量方法。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>評估時間：30分鐘</p>\r\n\r\n<p>適用年齡：4 到 12 歲</p>\r\n\r\n<p>發布年份： 2011&nbsp;（最新版本）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>完整套件包括：手冊、測試板、答題冊(25份)、測試員記錄表 (25份) 、評分模板</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*評估員需擁有專業資格</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>到貨期：4-6星期</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Provides a fast, reliable and valid measure of the overall visual perception of children</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Assessment time: 30 minutes</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Age: 4 to 12 years old</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Year of release: 2011 (latest version)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Whole kit includes: manual, test board, answer booklet (25 copies), tester record sheet (25 copies), scoring template</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*Assessor must be professionally qualified</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Delivery time: 4-6 weeks</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/126_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 17:29:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(127, 19, 0, 'GPB', '0', '鎖匙形釘板測試', 'key-shaped pegboard test', '2480.00', 1750.00, '<p>測試視覺-運動協調能力及操縱靈巧性。也非常適合測試偏側腦損傷。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>釘板有二十五個孔，這些孔帶有隨機不同定位的凹槽，受測者必須旋轉釘子以匹配孔才能插入。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>完整套件包括：釘板、釘子（25支）、測試員手冊</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>到貨期：4-6星期</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Tests visual-motor coordination and manipulative dexterity. It is also very suitable for testing lateralized brain damage.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The staple plate has twenty-five holes with randomly positioned notches, and the subject must rotate the staples to match the holes for insertion.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Whole kit includes: staple plate, staples (25), and tester&#39;s manual</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Delivery time: 4-6 weeks</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/127_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/127_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 17:30:21', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(128, 19, 0, 'PPB ', '0', '\"  普杜釘板測試\"', '\" Purdue pegboard test\"', '2580.00', 1850.00, '<p>用於確定精細運動協調的標準化評估。可以測量手、手指和手臂的粗略運動，並評估指尖的靈巧度。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>完整套件包括：釘板、項圈（25支）、墊圈（45個）、釘子（55支）、測試員手冊</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>到貨期：4-6星期</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Standardized assessment for determining fine-motor coordination. Allows measurement of hand, finger and arm movements and assessment of fingertip dexterity.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Whole&nbsp; kit includes: staple board, collar (25 pieces), washer (45 pieces), staples (55 pieces), tester&#39;s manual</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Delivery time: 4-6 weeks</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/128_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 17:31:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(129, 19, 0, 'OCTDT', '0', '奧康納鑷子靈活測試', 'Connor Forceps Flexibility Test', '3380.00', 2450.00, '<p>測試手眼協調及手指靈活性。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>使用鑷子將針插入每個孔中</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>完整套件包括：釘板、針（100支）、鑷子、測試員手冊</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>到貨期：4-6星期</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Test hand-eye coordination and finger dexterity.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Use the tweezers to insert the needles into each hole</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Whole kit includes: staple board, needles (100), tweezers, and tester&#39;s manual</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Delivery time: 4-6 weeks</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/129_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 17:35:17', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(130, 19, 0, 'JLRRT', '0', '\" 喬丹左右顛倒測試\"', '\" Jordan upside down test\"', '2080.00', 1310.00, '<p>測試對物體、字母、數字、單詞或字母序列有顛倒的問題。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>評估時間：20分鐘</p>\r\n\r\n<p>適用年齡：5 至 18 歲</p>\r\n\r\n<p>完整套件包括：測試員手冊、25 份記錄表格、25 份偏側檢查表和 25 份治療檢查表</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*評估員需擁有專業資格</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>到貨期：4-6星期</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Test for reversal of objects, letters, numbers, words or letter sequences.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Assessment time: 20 minutes</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Age: 5 to 18 years</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Whole kit includes: tester&#39;s manual, 25 record forms, 25 bias checklists and 25 treatment checklists</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*Assessor must be professionally qualified</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Delivery time: 4-6 weeks</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/130_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 17:36:21', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
