(132, 11, 0, 'PG1', '5', '大蛋蛋執筆膠', 'Jumbo Egg-shaped Pencil Grip', '38.00', 8.00, '<p>舒適和符合人體工程學的蛋形軟墊筆套，適合配合標準鉛筆使用，以改善書寫或繪畫時的力度控制和執筆舒適度。特別是需要長時間進行書寫，繪畫，填色時，能夠支撐手部關節，有效幫助減低對於手部和對於手指做成的壓力，避免長出瘡或繭 。適用於學前兒童及在學兒童，也適用於成人使用，如果在握筆時遇到困難,可提供更大的握力以增強穩定性。無論是慣用右手或慣用左手的人均可適用。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：約5cm長 x 直徑 3.5cm（內孔直徑 0.8cm ）<br />\r\n顏色：紅橙綠黃藍紫 （隨機款式一個）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：2歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>This egg-shaped pencil grip is ergonomically designed to fit standard size pencil which offers a more comfortable grip and better control of pencil when writing or drawing. It can particularly offer support to the hand joints and help to reduce pressure on the hand and fingers when writing, drawing or colouring for a long period of time. Suitable for preschool and children at school age, but also for adults who have difficulty holding a pencil in providing a stronger grip with greater stability. Suitable for both right and left-handed users.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: approx. 5cm long x 3.5cm diameter (good for pencil with a diameter of 0.8cm)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: red, orange, green, yellow, blue and purple (colour to be sent in random)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 2 years and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/132_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/132_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 17:45:59', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(133, 4, 0, 'FC8', '30', '珍寶大膠夾 ', 'Jumbo Tweezers(12 pieces)', '25.00', 8.80, '<p>利用Learning resources 珍寶大膠夾夾玩具小物，可以有效增強前三指抓握的力量強度和耐力。珍寶大膠夾具有符合人體工學的凹陷位，可引導兒童在適當位置抓握和用力。多使用珍寶大膠夾進行遊戲能夠協助提昇執筆技巧和筆控能力。可以配合絨毛球/橡皮膠粒等配件一同使用，遊戲中有效學習。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：15cm長 x 5.5cm 寬</p>\r\n\r\n<p>顏色：紅/橙/黃/綠/藍/紫 (隨機發放一款)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：4歲以上學童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Using Learning resources jumbo tweezer is a great way to increase the grasp strength and endurance of the first three fingers. The Jumbo Clip has an ergonomic design to guide children to make the grasp at the right place. Frequent practice with jumbo tweezers can improve pencil grasp and pencil control. Can be used with other toys such as fluffy balls / rubber beads to promote effective learning.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 15cm long x 5.5cm wide</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: Red/Orange/Yellow/Green/Blue/Purple (colour to be sent in random)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 4 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/133_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/133_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/133_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 17:48:52', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(134, 11, 0, 'PG2', '5', '長蛋蛋執筆膠', 'Long Egg-shaped Pencil Grip', '35.00', 8.10, '<p>舒適符合人體工程學的Special Supplies長蛋形軟墊筆套，適合配於標準鉛筆，鋼筆和蠟筆等等使用，以改善書寫或繪畫時的力度控制和執筆舒適度。帶有防滑功能的筆套握把為兒童書寫時增添了控制感和舒適感，使手部和手指保持舒適狀態。特別是需要長時間進行書寫，繪畫，填色時，有效幫助減低對於手部和對於手指做成的壓力，避免長出瘡或繭 。適用於學前兒童及在學兒童，也適用於成人使用，如果在握筆時遇到困難,可提供更大的握力以增強穩定性。無論是慣用右手或慣用左手的人均可適用。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：約4.7cm長 x 直徑 2.8cm（內孔直徑 0.7cm ）<br />\r\n顏色：紅橙綠黃藍紫（隨機款式一個）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>This long egg-shaped pencil grip is ergonomically designed by Special Supplies to fit standard size pencil, pen or crayon. It offers a more comfortable grip and better control of pencil when writing or drawing. The non-slip grip adds a sense of control and comfort. It can particularly offer support to the hand joints and help to reduce pressure on the hand and fingers when writing, drawing or colouring for a long period of time. Suitable for preschool and children at school age, but also for adults who have difficulty holding a pencil in providing a stronger grip with greater stability. Suitable for both right and left-handed users.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: approx. 4.7cm long x 2.8cm diameter (good for pencil with a diameter of 0.7cm)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: red, orange, green, yellow, blue and purple (colour to be sent in random)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 3 years and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/134_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/134_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/134_3.jpg,assets/products_image/650/134_4.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 17:49:18', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(135, 11, 0, 'PG3', '10', '盾牌執筆膠', 'Shield Pencil Grip', '35.00', 16.70, '<p>此款軟筆膠以符合人體工學標準設計，適合配於標準鉛筆，讓使用者舒適地長時間使用。尤其適合改善拇指鉗法等非有效執筆方法，提升前三指控制，改善書寫能力及耐力。無論是慣用右手或慣用左手的人均可適用。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：約3.8cm長 x 直徑2.6cm（內孔直徑0.7-0.8cm ）<br />\r\n顏色： 紅/橙/黃/綠/藍/深藍/粉紅（隨機款式一個）<br />\r\n<br />\r\n建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>This pencil grip is ergonomically designed to fit standard size pencils for a more comfortable pencil grip. It has a special finger guard to hold fingers in the correct position and prevent them from crossing over to help children learning a correct pencil grip. Suitable for both right and left handed users.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: approx. 3.8cm long x 2.6cm diameter (good for pencil with a diameter of 0.7-0.8cm)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/135_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/135_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 17:52:02', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(136, 11, 0, 'PG4', '10', '猴子款執筆膠', 'Monkey Pencil Grip', '55.00', 34.51, '<p>這款原創筆膠罕有地能同時協助五指放在適當的位置，有效促成正確的前三指執筆法，改善控筆，提高書寫耐力，養成良好的書寫習慣。由高質的有機矽製成，絕對安全和可靠，既無毒又耐用。無論是慣用右手或慣用左手的人均可適用。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：約4cm長（內孔直徑0.6-0.8cm ）<br />\r\n顏色：藍/綠/粉紅（隨機款式一個）<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>This pencil grip allows children to place all five fingers in a proper writing grip position, able to facilitate children to learn the tripod grip properly and better pencil control. Made of natural non-toxic silicone, safe and durable for use. Suitable for both right-handed and left-handed users.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: approx. 4cm long (good for pencil with a diameter of 0.6-0.8cm)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: Blue/Green/Pink (colour to be sent in random)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 3 years and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/136_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/136_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/136_3.jpg,assets/products_image/650/136_4.jpg,assets/products_image/650/136_5.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 17:54:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(137, 4, 0, 'FC8S', '355', '珍寶大膠夾 (12件)', 'Jumbo Tweezers(12 pieces)', '270.00', 105.60, '<p>利用Learning resources 珍寶大膠夾夾玩具小物，可以有效增強前三指抓握的力量強度和耐力。珍寶大膠夾具有符合人體工學的凹陷位，可引導兒童在適當位置抓握和用力。多使用珍寶大膠夾進行遊戲能夠協助提昇執筆技巧和筆控能力。可以配合絨毛球/橡皮膠粒等配件一同使用，遊戲中有效學習。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：15cm長 x 5.5cm 寬</p>\r\n\r\n<p>顏色：紅/橙/黃/綠/藍/紫 (隨機發放一款)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：4歲以上學童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Using Learning resources jumbo tweezer is a great way to increase the grasp strength and endurance of the first three fingers. The Jumbo Clip has an ergonomic design to guide children to make the grasp at the right place. Frequent practice with jumbo tweezers can improve pencil grasp and pencil control. Can be used with other toys such as fluffy balls / rubber beads to promote effective learning.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 15cm long x 5.5cm wide</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: Red/Orange/Yellow/Green/Blue/Purple (colour to be sent in random)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 4 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/137_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/137_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/137_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 17:54:51', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(138, 4, 0, 'FC10', '20', '不鏽鋼鐵夾', 'Stainless Steel Tweezers', '12.00', 3.30, '<p>使用不鏽鋼鐵夾夾小物，可以訓練前二指控制、手眼協調、 手指遠端操作能力等等。可以配合絨毛球/小珠等配件一同使用，遊戲中有效學習。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：12 cm 長</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：4歲以上學童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Use of the stainless steel tweezers can develop front two-finger control, hand-eye coordination, distal finger control, etc. Can be used with other toys such as fluffy balls/ beads to promote effective learning.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 12 cm long</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 4 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/138_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/138_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 17:56:18', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(139, 11, 0, 'PG5', '10', '大象款執筆膠', 'Elephant Pencil Grip', '55.00', 15.10, '<p>這款原創創意設計的執筆筆膠，結合市場上各種筆膠的優點而成。使用時可以將拇指和食指放入側面的孔中，然後用中指握住戒指位。控筆時可以確保三隻手指緊緊固定。能夠改善控筆，提高書寫耐力，養成良好的書寫習慣。適用於學前兒童及在學兒童，也適用於成人使用，如果在握筆時遇到困難,可提供更大的握力以增強穩定性。採用優質矽膠製成，安全且耐用。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n尺寸：約3.5cm長 x 直徑3.7cm（內孔直徑0.7-0.8cm ）<br />\r\n顏色：淺藍/綠/粉紅/深粉紅/橙/紫/藍/紫/黃（隨機款式一個）<br />\r\n建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>This elephant pencil grip is ergonomically designed which fits well with body physiology in combining the advantages of various pencil grip available on the market. Children can put thumb and index fingers in the two holes at the side and middle finger in the ring hole to form a firm tripod grip. It can help with better pencil control and improve handwriting skills. Suitable for preschool and children at school age, but also for adults who have difficulty holding a pencil in providing a stronger grip with greater stability. Made of natural silicone, safe and durable for use.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: approx. 3.5cm long x 3.7cm diameter (good for pencil with a diameter of 0.7-0.8cm)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: Light blue/green/pink/dark pink/orange/purple/blue/purple/yellow (colour to be sent in random)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 3 years and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/139_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/139_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/139_3.jpg,assets/products_image/650/139_4.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 17:56:34', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(140, 11, 0, 'PG6', '60', '重力執筆膠', 'Weighted Pencil Grip', '85.00', 34.00, '<p>在鉛筆上加裝這款重力筆膠，能夠為學童在書寫時手部加添關節本體感覺，給予豐富的動覺刺激，從而加強運筆時的動作協調，為感覺處理不良的學童改善書寫時的表現，有效改善字體的美觀性及整潔度。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：約4.5cm長 x 直徑1.6cm（內孔直徑0.8cm ）<br />\r\n顏色：金/銀/墨綠<br />\r\n建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Using this weighted pencil grip can provide additional tactile stimulation and proprioceptive stimulus to children which help them in the coordination of movements in pencil control. Particularly useful for children with poor sensory processing to improve handwriting performance.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: approx. 4.5cm long x 1.6cm diameter (good for pencil with a diameter of 0.8cm)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colour: Gold / Silver / Dark Green</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 3 years and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/140_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/140_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 17:58:04', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(141, 11, 0, 'PG7', '3', '條條執筆膠', 'Strip Pencil Grip', '10.00', 2.68, '<p>條條執筆膠可以按個人喜好和需要，把鉛筆加粗或在書寫時提供觸覺刺激，同時能舒緩太用力執筆的不適。 快來裝飾自己的書寫工具吧~</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：約長14cm（內孔未伸展直徑0.65cm，內孔有彈力可伸展 ）<br />\r\n顏色：紅/紫/橙/黃/綠（隨機款式一條）<br />\r\n<br />\r\n建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>This strip pencil grip can be used according to your needs and preference. It can provide a larger pencil grip or tactile stimulation to enhance the comfort in writing.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: approx. 14cm long (0.65cm diameter for inner layer but stretchable)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: red/purple/orange/yellow/green (colour to be sent in random)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children 3 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/141_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/141_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/141_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:01:58', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(142, 11, 0, 'PG8', '10', '鬚鬚捏捏執筆膠 (2件)', 'Squishy pencil grip(2 colours)', '12.00', 3.80, '<p>Special Supplies鬚鬚執筆膠由矽膠製成，豐富顏色可以隨意組合，創造出獨一無二的書寫工具。 富有彈性，可以套入常見尺寸的鉛筆、原子筆、鉛芯筆等等。上面的柔軟有紋理的鬚鬚，可以滿足觸覺刺激，緩解壓力和焦慮，同時協助提升注意力。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：3.8cm x 1.3cm<br />\r\n顏色：紅/橙/黃/綠/藍/紫（隨機款式2件）<br />\r\n<br />\r\n建議使用年齡：2歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Squishy pencil grip designed by Special Supplies are made in silicone with different colour which makes it attractive to children. It can easily stretch over to fit normal size pencil or pen. It comes with bristles on the grip which provides tactile stimulation to relieve stress and anxiety, while helping to improve attention.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 3.8cm x 1.3cm&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: red/orange/yellow/green/blue/purple (colour to be sent in random)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children 2 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/142_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/142_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:05:48', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(143, 4, 0, 'FC15', '30', '剪刀鏟鉗 ', 'Scoop Tongs', '48.00', 17.50, '<p>Skoolzy剪刀鏟鉗的剪刀式手柄易於使用，像剪刀一樣打開和關閉，幫助兒童增強工具操作、手眼協調和手指靈活性等能力。即使是剪刀初學者，也可以使用彩虹色鏟夾撿起各種小物件，在玩耍時建立良好的小肌肉技能！</p>\r\n\r\n<p>配合動物膠粒/絨毛球/小橡皮等配件一同使用，遊戲中有效學習。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：17.7cm長 x 5cm 寬</p>\r\n\r\n<p>顏色：紅/橙/黃/綠/藍/紫 (隨機發放一款)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：2歲以上學童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Skoolzy scoop tongs are designed with scissor handles which are easy to use. By opening and shutting the scissor handles can help train the tool use, hand-eye coordination and finger dexterity, etc. Even beginners can pick up all kinds of small objects with the rainbow-coloured scoops and build up fine muscle strength at the same time! Can be used with other toys such as animal beads/ fluffy balls/ small rubber bands to promote effective learning.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 17.7cm long x 5cm wide</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: Red/Orange/Yellow/Green/Blue/Purple (colour to be sent in random)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 2 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/143_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/143_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:06:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(144, 4, 0, 'FC15S', '200', '剪刀鏟鉗 (6件)', 'Scoop Tongs(6 pieces)', '260.00', 105.00, '<p>Skoolzy剪刀鏟鉗的剪刀式手柄易於使用，像剪刀一樣打開和關閉，幫助兒童增強工具操作、手眼協調和手指靈活性等能力。即使是剪刀初學者，也可以使用彩虹色鏟夾撿起各種小物件，在玩耍時建立良好的小肌肉技能！</p>\r\n\r\n<p>配合動物膠粒/絨毛球/小橡皮等配件一同使用，遊戲中有效學習。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：17.7cm長 x 5cm 寬</p>\r\n\r\n<p>顏色：紅/橙/黃/綠/藍/紫 (隨機發放一款)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：2歲以上學童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Skoolzy scoop tongs are designed with scissor handles which are easy to use. By opening and shutting the scissor handles can help train the tool use, hand-eye coordination and finger dexterity, etc. Even beginners can pick up all kinds of small objects with the rainbow-coloured scoops and build up fine muscle strength at the same time! Can be used with other toys such as animal beads/ fluffy balls/ small rubber bands to promote effective learning.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 17.7cm long x 5cm wide</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: Red/Orange/Yellow/Green/Blue/Purple (colour to be sent in random)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 2 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/144_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/144_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:07:54', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(145, 17, 0, 'TA1SF', '0', '觸覺探索套裝（一）', 'Tactile Exploration Set 1', '220.00', 106.53, '<p>觸覺探索套裝（一），包含了各種質地的觸感玩具，能帶來豐富的觸感刺激，讓孩子學習掌握自己的身體，認識身體與環境的關係。為動作協調、社交及適應能力的發展，建議良好的基礎。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n1. 刺蝟環 ($48)<br />\r\n2. 迷你刺蝟滾輪 ($38)<br />\r\n3. 觸感鬍鬚球 ($58)<br />\r\n4. 捏捏彈彈球 ($48)<br />\r\n5. 編織球 ($48)<br />\r\n6. 拉拉管 ($18)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>原價：$258&nbsp; 套裝價：$220</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>This Tactile Discovery Set contains a variety of sensory tactile toys which provide rich tactile stimulation to children to let them know more about themselves and their relationship with their environment. It aids the development of motor skills and social development.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. Sensory Bangle ($48)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Mini spiky roller ($38)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. Stringy Ball ($58)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. Squishy ball ($48)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. Tactile knitted ball ($48)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6. Pop tube ($18)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Original Price: $258&nbsp; Set Price: $220</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/145_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/145_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:08:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(146, 4, 0, 'FC16', '30', '球形剪刀', 'Handy Scooper', '58.00', 32.00, '<p>利用拇指、食指和中指開合Learning Resources球型剪刀，有效訓練手指肌肉，提升手指兩側分化、手眼協調及手指靈活性，改善工具使用及寫前能力。配合動物膠粒/絨毛球/小橡皮等配件一同使用，遊戲中有效學習。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：15cm長 x 6.5cm 寬</p>\r\n\r\n<p>顏色：橙/藍/綠/紫 (隨機發放一款)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：2歲以上學童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Using Learning Resources handy scoopers require good control of the thumb, index finger and middle finger which can effectively train intrinsic hand muscles, improve finger differentiation, hand-eye coordination and finger dexterity. It can also improve tool use and pre-writing skills. Can be used with other toys such as animal beads/ fluffy balls/ small rubber bands to promote effective learning.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 15cm long x 6.5cm wide</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: orange/blue/green/purple (colour to be sent in random)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 2 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/146_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/146_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:10:04', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(147, 4, 0, 'FC16S', '115', '球形剪刀 (4件)', 'Handy Scooper( 4 pieces)', '200.00', 128.00, '<p>利用拇指、食指和中指開合Learning Resources球型剪刀，有效訓練手指肌肉，提升手指兩側分化、手眼協調及手指靈活性，改善工具使用及寫前能力。配合動物膠粒/絨毛球/小橡皮等配件一同使用，遊戲中有效學習。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：15cm長 x 6.5cm 寬</p>\r\n\r\n<p>顏色：橙/藍/綠/紫 (隨機發放一款)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：2歲以上學童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Using Learning Resources handy scoopers require good control of the thumb, index finger and middle finger which can effectively train intrinsic hand muscles, improve finger differentiation, hand-eye coordination and finger dexterity. It can also improve tool use and pre-writing skills. Can be used with other toys such as animal beads/ fluffy balls/ small rubber bands to promote effective learning.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 15cm long x 6.5cm wide</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: orange/blue/green/purple (colour to be sent in random)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 2 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/147_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/147_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:11:12', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(148, 12, 0, 'SC1', '50', '彎形匙羹', 'Henro-Grip® Spoon', '120.00', 43.00, '<p>職業治療師開發的生活輔助產品，含CE標誌，丹麥製造，由 PP 和 TPE 製成，安全耐用。Henro-Grip&reg;產品採用弧形設計，無需彎曲手臂即可進食。讓運動技能較弱的人容易控制，有助於將食物送入口中，進食更輕鬆，提升自理能力。可用家用洗碗機清洗保持清潔。也可以放進微波爐。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>顏色：藍色（適合右手為主力手的人士使用）<br />\r\n尺寸：長16.5cm ；重量41 克</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡： 8 歲以上兒童/成人</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Henro-Grip&reg; Spoon is designed by occupational therapist. A CE-marked, Danish-made product made in PP and TPE which is safe and durable for use. The curved design enables eating without bending the arm, making eating easy for people with poor motor skills. It is microwave and dishwasher safe.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colour: Blue (suitable for right-handed user)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: Length 16.5cm; Weight 41g</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children over 8 years old and adults&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/148_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/148_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:11:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(149, 4, 0, 'FA1', '500', '彩色小熊膠粒 (12粒)', 'Bear Family (12 pieces)', '36.00', 15.20, '<p>Learning Resources 彩色小熊可以作小肌肉訓練的配件，也可以用來學習識別顔色，計數，排序等等。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：每隻小熊計的高度為1寸，重量4克</p>\r\n\r\n<p>顏色：紅/橙/黃/綠/藍/紫(隨機發放一款)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡： 3 歲以上兒童 （請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Learning Resources bear family can be used for small muscle training and learning to identify colours, counting, sorting, etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: Height of each bear is 1&quot; and weighs 4g</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: red/orange/yellow/green/blue/purple (colour to be sent in random)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above (Please use under parental supervision to avoid choking risk)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/149_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/149_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/149_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:12:48', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(150, 12, 0, 'SC2', '50', '彎形叉子', 'Henro-Grip® Fork', '120.00', 43.00, '<p>職業治療師開發的生活輔助產品，含CE標誌，丹麥製造，由 PP 和 TPE 製成，安全耐用。Henro-Grip&reg;產品採用弧形設計，無需彎曲手臂即可進食。讓運動技能較弱的人容易控制，有助於將食物送入口中，進食更輕鬆，提升自理能力。可用家用洗碗機清洗保持清潔。也可以放進微波爐。<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>顏色：藍色（適合右手為主力手的人士使用）<br />\r\n尺寸：長16.5cm ；重量41 克</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡： 8 歲以上兒童/成人</p>\r\n', '<p>Henro-Grip&reg; Fork is designed by occupational therapist. A CE-marked, Danish-made product made in PP and TPE which is safe and durable for use. The curved design enables eating without bending the arm, making eating easy for people with poor motor skills. It is microwave and dishwasher safe.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colour: Blue (suitable for right-handed user)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: Length 16.5cm; Weight 41g</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children over 8 years old and adults</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/150_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:13:24', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(151, 12, 0, 'SC3R', '50', '學習筷子 (右手)', 'Training Chopsticks (Right-handed)', '75.00', 21.60, '<p>韓國製造Edison 品牌學習筷子，採用精美的交通工具設計吸引孩子使用。手指可以套入套環內，施力點更集中，更容易掌握前三指控制，提升手指靈活與協調性，學習使用筷子的正確手勢。（適合右手為主力手的人士使用）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式：藍/綠/粉紅/黃 (隨機發送一款)<br />\r\n尺寸：約長18cm<br />\r\n<br />\r\n建議使用年齡：2.5歲以上</p>\r\n', '<p>This pair of training chopsticks are designed by Edison brand in Korea. Public transport character on top makes it attractive for children. Children can also learn the right finger placement in mastering the chopstick grip by using the silicone rings of the chopsticks. (Suitable for right-handed users)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style: blue/green/pink/yellow (colour to be sent in random)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: approx. 18cm long</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 2.5 years and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/151_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:14:38', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(152, 17, 0, 'TA1SA', '0', '觸覺探索套裝（二）', 'Tactile Exploration Set 2', '200.00', 73.75, '<p>觸覺探索套裝（二），包含了各種質地的觸感玩具，能帶來豐富的觸感刺激，讓孩子學習掌握自己的身體，認識身體與環境的關係。為動作協調、社交及適應能力的發展，建議良好的基礎。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>波子隧道4件 ($40)</li>\r\n	<li>蓬蓬球單色筒1件 ($25)</li>\r\n	<li>扭扭鎖鍊1件($25)</li>\r\n	<li>金屬手指環2件 ($18)</li>\r\n	<li>觸感拍尺手環1件($58)</li>\r\n	<li>珍寶彈力條2件 ($36)</li>\r\n	<li>長刺猬滾輪1件($38)</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>原價：$240 套裝價：$200</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>This Tactile Discovery Set contains a variety of sensory tactile toys which provide rich tactile stimulation to children to let them know more about themselves and their relationship with their environment. It aids the development of motor skills and social development.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. Marble tunnel fidgets x4&nbsp; ($40)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Bunchems cone (single colour) x1 ($25)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. Fidget Chain x1 ($25)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. Spiky metallic rings x2 ($18)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. 1 x Sensory Bracelet ($58)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6. Elastic tubes x2 ($36)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7. Spiky roller x1 ($38)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Original Price: $240&nbsp; Set Price: $200</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/152_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/152_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:15:20', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(153, 4, 0, 'FA1S', '505', '彩色小熊膠粒原包 (102粒)', 'Bear Family (102 pieces)', '250.00', 107.50, '<p>Learning Resources 彩色小熊可以作小肌肉訓練的配件，也可以用來學習識別顔色，計數，排序等等。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：每隻小熊計的高度為1寸，重量4克</p>\r\n\r\n<p>顏色：紅/橙/黃/綠/藍/紫(隨機發放一款)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡： 3 歲以上兒童 （請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Learning Resources bear family can be used for small muscle training and learning to identify colours, counting, sorting, etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: Height of each bear is 1&quot; and weighs 4g</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: red/orange/yellow/green/blue/purple (colour to be sent in random)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above (Please use under parental supervision to avoid choking risk)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/153_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:16:44', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(154, 12, 0, 'SC3L', '50', '學習筷子 (左手)', 'Training Chopsticks (Left-handed)', '75.00', 32.40, '<p>韓國製造Edison 品牌學習筷子，採用精美的交通工具設計吸引孩子使用。手指可以套入套環內，施力點更集中，更容易掌握前三指控制，提升手指靈活與協調性，學習使用筷子的正確手勢。（適合左手為主力手的人士使用）<br />\r\n<br />\r\n款色：poli 藍色<br />\r\n尺寸：約長18cm<br />\r\n<br />\r\n建議使用年齡：2.5歲以上</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>This pair of training chopsticks are designed by Edison brand in Korea. Public transport character on top makes it attractive for children. Children can also learn the right finger placement in mastering the chopstick grip by using the silicone rings of the chopsticks. (Suitable for left-handed users)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colour: poli blue</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: approx. 18cm long</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 2.5 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/154_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:16:50', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(155, 17, 0, 'TA2', '40', '感統治療刷', 'Wilbarger Brush', '68.00', 37.00, '<p>委百加治療刷能提供深層壓力及本體感刺激，實證研究顯示能減低觸覺過敏情況，提升感覺調節能力。新一代治療刷更符合人體工學，使用者更容易使用。正品產品由美國直送。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>注意：此產品必須有職業治療師親身指導才可以使用。本店沒有提供任何有關刷身教學供使用者參考。切勿隨意跟據任何網上片段自行進行刷身治療。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：2歲以上兒童</p>\r\n', '<p>Brushing with a Wilbarger brush can provide deep pressure and proprioceptive stimulation which reduce tactile hypersensitivity and improve sensory processing from research studies. This new version of brush is ergonomically designed which makes it easier to use. This product is directly imported from the USA.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Note: This product should only be used with a brushing protocol suggested by an occupational therapist. We do not provide any instructions on the use of the brush. Please do not do the brushing on your own.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 2 years and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/155_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/155_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/155_3.jpg,assets/products_image/650/155_4.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:16:55', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(156, 7, 0, 'ST1', '20', '紫色漿糊筆', 'Purple Glue Pen', '12.00', 3.20, '<p>美國ELMER&#39;S漿糊筆以無毒材料製成，專為小朋友而設，塗出的漿糊是紫色的，讓孩子清楚看到自己塗畫的地方。漿糊乾後會變會成透明，可水洗清潔。適用於紙張、木材、紙板、鈕扣、卡片紙、陶瓷、毛氈/織物等， 適合孩子做手工、小肌肉訓練使用。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>容量: 6g</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：2歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>ELMER&#39;S non-toxic purple glue pen is designed for children&#39;s use. It comes with a disappearing purple formula that helps children see where the glue is. The glue becomes transparent when it is dry and can be wiped with water. Suitable for use on paper, wood, cardboard, buttons, cardboard, ceramics, felt/fabric, etc. Ideal for children to do handcrafts and small muscle training.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Capacity: 6g</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 2 years and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/156_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/156_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:17:53', '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
