(157, 12, 0, 'SC8', '105', '雙耳吸管防漏水杯', 'Non-Spill Straw Cup', '120.00', 53.50, '<p>韓國製造Edison品牌雙耳吸管防漏水杯，不含BPA，寶寶安全使用，容易清潔。水杯有防漏設計，反轉/搖晃都不會把液體濺出。雙耳設計，鼓勵孩子自己獨立喝水，訓練雙手協調能力。使用吸管吸啜，可以訓練口肌，為語言發展打好基礎。杯身有度數，可以看到剩下的液體容量。如需替換吸管，可以自行購買Edison吸管127mm。請參閱圖片了解使用方法及清潔指引。<br />\r\n容量：200 ml (最多可剩載250ml)<br />\r\n尺寸：11cm闊 x 8 cm長 x 13cm 高<br />\r\n款式：紅/藍/啡 (隨機發送一款)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：1歲以上</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>This non-spill straw cup designed by Edison brand in Korea. It is BPA free which is safe for toddler use. Its non-spill function enables no water spillage even the cup is upside down or when tilted. The two handles also encourage children to drink water themselves and improve bilateral hand coordination. Drinking with a straw can also train oral motor skills. Measuring scale available in the cup to know how much liquid is left inside the cup. Additional straws with diameter 127mm can be purchased from Edison. Please see pictures for how to use and clean the straw cup.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Capacity: 200 ml (up to 250 ml)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 11cm width x 8cm length x 13cm height</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style: red/blue/brown (colour to be sent in random)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 1 year old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/157_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:18:12', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(158, 4, 0, 'FA2', '125', '恐龍膠粒 (30粒)', 'Mini Dinosaurs (30 pieces)', '75.00', 27.30, '<p>30 件侏羅紀王國中的不同類型的彩色恐龍! 由高品質、耐用的塑膠製成，達美國ASTM、Sedex、ICTI Care安全標準。可以作小肌肉訓練的配件，促進精細動作技能、手眼協調，使用恐龍玩具來進行象徵遊戲也可以促進創意表達。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：每隻恐龍直徑為2-2.5寸</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡： 3 歲以上兒童 （請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>30 different types of dinosaurs from Jurassic World! Made from high-quality, durable plastic and conform to ASTM, Sedex and ICTI Care safety standards of the United States. They can be used for small muscle training to promote fine motor skills and hand-eye coordination. Children can also learn to be creative when using dinosaurs for symbolic play.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: Each dinosaur is 2-2.5&quot; in diameter</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above (Please use under parental supervision to avoid choking risk)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/158_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/158_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:18:36', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(159, 17, 0, 'TA3', '25', '拉拉管', 'Pop tubes', '18.00', 4.30, '<p>讓你隨時隨地拉扯、擠壓、彎曲的拉拉管成爲滿足觸感需要的指尖玩具（Fidget toys）。 拉的時候會發出啵啵聲，帶來聽覺刺激。尤其適合觸感和聽覺尋求的孩子。還可以用做出數字字母，配合教學需要，以多感官學習法學習知識。做成不同大小的圈圈，配合大肌肉訓練。拉拉管玩具堅固，耐用，輕巧，方便攜帶到任何地方使用。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式：紅綠黃橙藍紫（隨機發放一款）/一套6色<br />\r\n產品介紹片段 ：<a href=\'https://youtu.be/CzKmkIpkTH8\'>https://youtu.be/CzKmkIpkTH8</a><br />\r\n尺寸：約18cm （可伸展到58cm）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：2歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Pop tube is an ideal fidget toy that allows you to pull, squeeze and twist whenever you want. It also produces sound when being pulled to offer auditory stimulation. Especially suitable for children who are tactile and auditory seeking. These tubes can also be used to make numbers or letters to facilitate learning in a multi-sensory approach. It can also be used to make circles of different sizes for hand muscle training. It is lightweight, strong and durable which makes it easy to bring to anywhere you like.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Styles: red, green, yellow, orange, blue and purple (colour to be sent in random) / 6 colours in a set</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Product description video: https://youtu.be/CzKmkIpkTH8</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: approx. 18cm (can be stretched up to 58cm)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 2 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/159_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/159_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/159_3.jpg,assets/products_image/650/159_4.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:19:13', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(160, 17, 0, 'TA3S', '155', '拉拉管 (6支)', 'Pop tubes (6 colours)', '98.00', 21.80, '<p>讓你隨時隨地拉扯、擠壓、彎曲的拉拉管成爲滿足觸感需要的指尖玩具（Fidget toys）。 拉的時候會發出啵啵聲，帶來聽覺刺激。尤其適合觸感和聽覺尋求的孩子。還可以用做出數字字母，配合教學需要，以多感官學習法學習知識。做成不同大小的圈圈，配合大肌肉訓練。拉拉管玩具堅固，耐用，輕巧，方便攜帶到任何地方使用。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式：紅綠黃橙藍紫（隨機發放一款）/一套6色<br />\r\n產品介紹片段 ：<a href=\'https://youtu.be/CzKmkIpkTH8\'>https://youtu.be/CzKmkIpkTH8</a><br />\r\n尺寸：約18cm （可伸展到58cm）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：2歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Pop tube is an ideal fidget toy that allows you to pull, squeeze and twist whenever you want. It also produces sound when being pulled to offer auditory stimulation. Especially suitable for children who are tactile and auditory seeking. These tubes can also be used to make numbers or letters to facilitate learning in a multi-sensory approach. It can also be used to make circles of different sizes for hand muscle training. It is lightweight, strong and durable which makes it easy to bring to anywhere you like.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Styles: red, green, yellow, orange, blue and purple (colour to be sent in random) / 6 colours in a set</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Product description video: https://youtu.be/CzKmkIpkTH8</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: approx. 18cm (can be stretched up to 58cm)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 2 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/160_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/160_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/160_3.jpg,assets/products_image/650/160_4.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:20:02', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(161, 12, 0, 'SC10', '40', '嬰兒口水肩', 'Baby Food Apron', '100.00', 47.30, '<p>日本製造，輕盈有彈性的柔軟面料，貼身且感覺舒適。口水肩背面經過防水處理，可防止污垢滴落和溢出。正面寬大的口袋可容納進食時溢出的食物。易於清潔和清洗。魔術貼位於側面，不會黏到寶寶頭髮。重量只有40.8 克，方便攜帶。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡 ：5個月-2歲</p>\r\n', '<p>Made in Japan. The soft, lightweight and stretchy fabric is snug and make babies feel comfortable. The back of the apron is waterproofed to prevent dirt dripping and spilling. Large front pocket can accommodate food spills during eating. Easy to clean and wash. Velcro tape on the side so it doesn&#39;t stick to baby&#39;s hair. Weight only 40.8 grams, easy to carry around.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Suitable for:&nbsp; 5 months - 2 years old</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/161_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/161_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:20:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(162, 7, 0, 'ST2', '45', '單孔打孔機', 'Single Hole Punch', '20.00', 8.70, '<p>因很多家長都反映難以購買單孔打孔機，所以Wayshk 特別在台灣訂購這款萬事捷 Tomato迷你打孔機，方便孩子單手抓握，用作訓練前三指力量，建立穩定的手拱紋。 可打孔頁數為10張75g紙。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式：淺藍/粉紅（隨機款式1個）<br />\r\n尺寸：孔徑 0.6 mm；&nbsp; 深寬：1.3 cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3歲以上學童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Wayshk ordered this single hole punch from Taiwan in particular as many parents find it difficult to find this product. Its small design makes it easier for children to grasp with one hand and to train first three fingers&#39; strength. Perforate up to 10 sheets of 75gsm paper.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colour: Light blue/pink (colour to be sent in random)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: create 0.6 mm hole; throat depth: 1.3 cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 3 years and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/162_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:20:37', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(163, 4, 0, 'FA3', '75', '迷你水果橡皮 (48粒)', 'Mini Fruits Erasers (48 pieces)', '25.00', 10.20, '<p>Mini Fruits Erasers 水果迷你橡皮粒連膠盒，是非常好的小肌肉訓練配件！</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式：水果款式隨機發送</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>數量：48-50粒</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：0.9cm-1.5cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3 歲以上兒童 （請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Mini fruits erasers is a good item for small muscle training!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style: type of fruits to be sent in random</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Quantity: 48-50 pieces</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 0.9cm-1.5cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above (Please use under parental supervision to avoid choking risk)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/163_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/163_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:21:05', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(164, 17, 0, 'TA4', '35', '迷你拉拉管喇叭玩具 ', 'Mini Stretch Tubes Set (8 pieces)', '48.00', 18.80, '<p>讓你隨時隨地拉扯、擠壓、彎曲的迷你拉拉管，成爲滿足觸感需要的指尖玩具（Fidget toys）。拉的時候會發出啵啵聲，帶來聽覺刺激。尤其適合觸感和聽覺尋求的孩子。還可以用做出數字字母，配合教學需要，以多感官學習法學習知識。做成不同大小的圈圈，配合大肌肉訓練。玩具堅固，耐用，輕巧，方便攜帶到任何地方使用。套裝還附送一個膠喇叭，接駁起來就可以當笛子一樣吹，訓練口部肌肉及核心肌肉力量。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>套裝包括：6條迷你拉拉管+黃色吹嘴+喇叭 <br />\r\n尺寸：約6.8cm （可伸展到15.1cm）<br />\r\n<br />\r\n建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n', '<p>Pop tube is an ideal fidget toy that allows you to pull, squeeze and twist whenever you want. It also produces sound when being pulled to offer auditory stimulation. Especially suitable for children who are tactile and auditory seeking. These tubes can also be used to make numbers or letters to facilitate learning in a multi-sensory approach. It can also be used to make circles of different sizes for hand muscle training. It is lightweight, strong and durable which makes it easy to bring anywhere you like. This set also comes with a plastic horn that can be connected to the tubes for whistling, training oral motor skills and core muscle strength as well.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Set includes: 6 mini stretch tubes + yellow mouthpiece + plastic horn&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: approx. 6.8cm (can be stretched up to 15.1cm)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/164_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/164_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:21:38', '2023-04-16 18:29:01'),
(165, 13, 0, 'EO1', '655', '情緒感官沙漏', 'Express Your Feelings Sensory Bottles', '298.00', 189.40, '<p>Hand2mind情緒沙漏一套有四個液體沙漏瓶子，每個都有獨特的情感顏色表達，代表著四個情緒&mdash;&mdash;快樂、憤怒、害怕或悲傷，讓孩子可以安靜自主地識別及連接自己的感受，從而慢慢平靜下來，是冷靜角 （time out corner）的必需品。 鼓勵孩子以積極和有成效的方式，來回應有關情緒的討論和對話。瓶子易於抓握、安全密封。把瓶子裡面的液體混合、搖晃或翻轉，都可以成為有趣的Fidget toys！</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3 歲以上兒童</p>\r\n', '<p>Hand2mind sensory bottles include 4 bottles with each bottle featuring a unique colour and emotion including happy, angry, scared and sad. It helps children learn to identify emotions in themselves and manage their own emotions. Ideal toys to be put in time out corner to encourage discussion with children about responding to emotions in positive, proactive ways. Each bottle is securely sealed and easy for little hands to hold. Its mesmerizing motion can be an ideal fidget toy for children too!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/165_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/165_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:22:17', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(166, 17, 0, 'TA5', '45', '刺猬環 ', 'Sensory Bangle', '48.00', 21.46, '<p>Impresa 品牌刺猬環採用100％高品質定製配方材料製成，並具有ASTM F963國際玩具標准證書。 無毒且不含BPAs、鄰苯二甲酸鹽和乳膠，確保安全使用。可以隨意簡單地拉伸、拉動、旋轉、擠壓這些玩具，然後讓它們彈回原來的形狀！成為出色的小工具，滿足觸感需要，有助於鎮定情緒，減輕壓力/焦慮並可以增加注意力。產品耐用及安全，適合不同年齡人士使用。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：外圍直徑約10cm，內圈直徑約5cm所有管長 30.5cm<br />\r\n款式：粉紅色/綠色/藍色（隨機發放一款）/一套三色</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Sensory bangle designed by Impresa is made from 100% high quality materials which is nontoxic, BPA, phthalates and latex free. Safe for children&#39;s use. Certified by ASTM F963 Standard Consumer Safety Specification for Toy Safety. The toy is flexible enough to enable pulling, twisting, and squeezing without changing its original shape. Ideal fidget toy in providing tactile stimulation. Able to calm emotions, reduces stress/anxiety and can enhance attention. Durable and suitable for all ages.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: outer diameter approx. 10cm, inner ring diameter approx. 5cm. All tubes 30.5cm long</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style: pink/green/blue (colour to be sent in random) / three colours in a set&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 3 years and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/166_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/166_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:23:13', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(167, 7, 0, 'ST3', '50', '可擦式工作紙膠套單個', 'Erasable Pockets with Marker Pen', '15.00', 12.63, '<p>孩子在學習時經常需要浪費大量紙張！ 可重複使用的透明膠套可作為工作簿和活動頁面印刷的保護套，因此您可以無限次地重複書寫和擦拭同一張活動工作紙或書本頁面，善用學習資源。也適合把治療膠放在膠面使用，配合不同工作紙，練習寫前/書寫技巧。 送原裝馬克筆一支。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式：單個/30個<br />\r\n顏色：紅/深粉紅/淺粉紅/橙/黃/綠/深藍/淺藍/紫/黑 （隨機款式1個）<br />\r\n工作紙膠套尺寸：約25x36cm</p>\r\n', '<p>Children often need to use a lot of paper when they learn! Workbooks or worksheets can be put into these reusable clear pockets. Write over the top with a dry-erase marker and wipe away when finished. Ideal for multiple practices on the same workbook or worksheet. Therapy putty can also be put on the pockets and used with worksheets for practising pre-writing/writing skills. Pockets come with a marker pen.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Quantity: 1 piece / 30 pieces</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: red/dark pink/light pink/orange/yellow/green/dark blue/light blue/purple/black (colour to be sent in random)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: approx. 25x36cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/167_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:23:39', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(168, 13, 0, 'EO2', '185', '趣味面孔遊戲', 'Funny Faces Game', '228.00', 103.20, '<p>這套以色列製學習玩具可以讓孩子貼魔術貼創作出不同趣味的面孔，鼓勵幼兒探索周圍的世界，學習各種概念，例如顏色、尺寸和紋理。在互動中建立詞彙量，提升手眼協調，訓練持續專注能力及視覺記憶，還可以認識和表達不同的情緒!</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n套裝包括：2張人物卡，76件小配件，16張樣本圖卡</p>\r\n', '<p>This funny faces game is made in Israel and allows children to create various funny faces by matching different face pieces with velcro connectors. Encouraging children to explore the world around them and learn concepts such as colour, size and pattern. It can also build vocabulary, improve hand-eye coordination as well as sustained attention and visual memory. Children can also learn to identify and express different emotions!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Set includes: 2 character cards, 76 face pieces and 16 sample cards</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/168_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/168_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/168_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:23:45', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(169, 17, 0, 'TA5S', '150', '刺猬環 (3件)', 'Sensory Bangle (a set of 3)', '135.00', 64.92, '<p>Impresa 品牌刺猬環採用100％高品質定製配方材料製成，並具有ASTM F963國際玩具標准證書。 無毒且不含BPAs、鄰苯二甲酸鹽和乳膠，確保安全使用。可以隨意簡單地拉伸、拉動、旋轉、擠壓這些玩具，然後讓它們彈回原來的形狀！成為出色的小工具，滿足觸感需要，有助於鎮定情緒，減輕壓力/焦慮並可以增加注意力。產品耐用及安全，適合不同年齡人士使用。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：外圍直徑約10cm，內圈直徑約5cm所有管長 30.5cm<br />\r\n款式：粉紅色/綠色/藍色（隨機發放一款）/一套三色</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Sensory bangle designed by Impresa is made from 100% high quality materials which is nontoxic, BPA, phthalates and latex free. Safe for children&#39;s use. Certified by ASTM F963 Standard Consumer Safety Specification for Toy Safety. The toy is flexible enough to enable pulling, twisting, and squeezing without changing its original shape. Ideal fidget toy in providing tactile stimulation. Able to calm emotions, reduces stress/anxiety and can enhance attention. Durable and suitable for all ages.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: outer diameter approx. 10cm, inner ring diameter approx. 5cm. All tubes 30.5cm long</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style: pink/green/blue (colour to be sent in random) / three colours in a set&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 3 years and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/169_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/169_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:24:22', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(170, 7, 0, 'ST3S', '1520', '可擦式工作紙膠套(30個)', 'Erasable Pockets with Marker Pen (30 pieces)', '380.00', 177.00, '<p>孩子在學習時經常需要浪費大量紙張！ 可重複使用的透明膠套可作為工作簿和活動頁面印刷的保護套，因此您可以無限次地重複書寫和擦拭同一張活動工作紙或書本頁面，善用學習資源。也適合把治療膠放在膠面使用，配合不同工作紙，練習寫前/書寫技巧。 送原裝馬克筆一支。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式：單個/30個<br />\r\n顏色：紅/深粉紅/淺粉紅/橙/黃/綠/深藍/淺藍/紫/黑 （隨機款式1個）<br />\r\n工作紙膠套尺寸：約25x36cm</p>\r\n', '<p>Children often need to use a lot of paper when they learn! Workbooks or worksheets can be put into these reusable clear pockets. Write over the top with a dry-erase marker and wipe away when finished. Ideal for multiple practices on the same workbook or worksheet. Therapy putty can also be put on the pockets and used with worksheets for practising pre-writing/writing skills. Pockets come with a marker pen.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Quantity: 1 piece / 30 pieces</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: red/dark pink/light pink/orange/yellow/green/dark blue/light blue/purple/black (colour to be sent in random)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: approx. 25x36cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/170_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:25:15', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(171, 14, 0, 'OM1', '20', '空心長管牙膠', 'Hollow Teether Tubes', '38.00', 10.80, '<p>空心牙膠管由食品級矽膠製成。耐高低溫（-50℃-230℃），可煮沸或放入冰箱。安全無毒，不含 BPA。堅固耐用，柔軟有彈性，有效保護牙齦，適合嬰兒/孩子磨牙使用。 也減少孩子咬指甲或吮吸拇指的行為。牙膠管是中空的，可以用清潔刷輕鬆清潔，也可以放進洗碗機。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n* 第一次使用之前和每次使用之後，請用溫水和肥皂徹底清洗。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：16cm 長<br />\r\n顏色： 紅/黃/藍/綠/灰/紫 （隨機款式一條）<br />\r\n<br />\r\n適合：三個月以上嬰兒（請在家長監督下使用）</p>\r\n', '<p>These hollow teether tubes are made of food-grade silicone, 100% non-toxic and BPA Free. Resistant to high and low temperatures (-50&deg;C-230&deg;C) which can be put in boiling water or placed in the fridge. Soft and flexible in texture, making it an ideal chewing tool for toddlers to relieve discomfort in developing teeth.&nbsp; Help reduce the nail biting or thumb sucking behaviour of toddlers. Can be easily cleaned with a cleaning brush and dishwasher safe.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Wash thoroughly with warm water and soap before and after use&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 16cm long</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: red/yellow/blue/green/grey/purple (to be sent in random)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Suitable for: babies over 3 months (please use under parental supervision)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/171_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:25:31', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(172, 4, 0, 'FA4M', '25', '0.8 cm絨毛球連盒 (100粒)', '0.8 cm Fluffy balls with storage box (Qty 100)', '18.00', 3.90, '<p>絨毛球連收納膠盒，是非常好的小肌肉訓練配件！</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式1：0.8cm 直徑 （數量：100粒）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式2：1.5cm 直徑 （數量：80粒）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式3：2.5cm 直徑 （數量：20粒）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3 歲以上兒童 （請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Fluffy balls (with storage box) is great for training small hand muscles!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style 1: 0.8cm diameter (Qty: 100)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style 2: 1.5cm diameter (Qty: 80)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style 3: 2.5cm diameter (Qty: 20)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 3 years and above (Please use under parental supervision to avoid choking risk)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/172_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/172_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/172_3.jpg,assets/products_image/650/172_4.jpg,assets/products_image/650/172_5.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:25:45', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(173, 14, 0, 'OM5', '20', '人仔牙膠頸繩', 'LEGO Minifigure Teether with Chain', '88.00', 25.20, '<p>感官咀嚼頸繩專為患有焦慮，感覺統合失調，專注力缺乏或過度活躍症，自閉症等等的孩子設計，特別適合尋求口腔覺刺激的孩子。能夠有效為孩子提供豐富的口腔覺刺激，從而協助紓緩情緒，提高專注力，減少磨牙及咬物件的情況。此產品使用最高質量的100％食品級有機矽製成，不含BPA，不含PVC，不含鉛和鄰苯二甲酸鹽，確保安全使用。頸繩可以調教長度。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* 第一次使用之前和每次使用之後，請用溫水和肥皂徹底清洗。<br />\r\n* 這款牙膠較硬，適合尋求口腔覺的孩子使用<br />\r\n* 不要過分地咬住吊墜的角位或凸起的部份，以免造成窒息危險。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：3.3cm寬 x 5.4cm 高<br />\r\n顏色：黃/橙/藍/淺藍/綠（隨機款式一個）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>適合：4歲以上兒童（請在家長監督下使用）</p>\r\n', '<p>This LEGO minifigure teether with chain is designed for children with anxiety, sensory integration disorders, ADHD or autism, etc. It is particularly suitable for children who seek oral sensory stimulation. It provides rich oral sensory stimulation to help relieve emotions, improve attention and reduce teeth grinding and biting objects. It is made in 100% food grade silicone, free of BPA ,PVC phthalates, lead and cadmium. Safe for children use. Come with adjustable chain<strong>.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Wash thoroughly with warm water and soap before and after each use.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Hard in texture and is suitable for children seeking oral stimulation</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Do not chew too hard on the corners or bulging part of the teether as this may cause a choking hazard</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 3.3cm wide x 5.4cm high</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: yellow/orange/blue/light blue/green (colour to be sent in random)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Suitable for: children over 4 years old (please use under parental supervision)</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/173_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/173_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/173_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:26:56', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(174, 4, 0, 'FA4S', '60', '1.5cm絨毛球連盒 (80粒)', '1.5 cm Fluffy balls with storage box (Qty 80)', '20.00', 5.70, '<p>絨毛球連收納膠盒，是非常好的小肌肉訓練配件！</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式1：0.8cm 直徑 （數量：100粒）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式2：1.5cm 直徑 （數量：80粒）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式3：2.5cm 直徑 （數量：20粒）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3 歲以上兒童 （請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Fluffy balls (with storage box) is great for training small hand muscles!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style 1: 0.8cm diameter (Qty: 100)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style 2: 1.5cm diameter (Qty: 80)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style 3: 2.5cm diameter (Qty: 20)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 3 years and above (Please use under parental supervision to avoid choking risk)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/174_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/174_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/174_3.jpg,assets/products_image/650/174_4.jpg,assets/products_image/650/174_5.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:27:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(175, 14, 0, 'OM6', '25', '積木牙膠頸繩', 'Rainbow Teether with Chain', '78.00', 20.20, '<p>彩虹牙膠有吸引人的光亮彩虹顏色，能滿足尋求口腔覺需要，能有效地減少亂放東西入口/咬傷指甲或吮吸拇指的不良習慣，舒緩焦慮，也能協助提高日常專注和集中力。 產品安全無毒，由FDA和CE批准的食品級有機矽製成。 無毒，無BPA，無鉛，乳膠或鄰苯二甲酸鹽。可輕鬆用肥皂和水用手清洗，或可輕鬆放入洗碗機中以除去任何污垢。頸繩可以調教長度。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* 第一次使用之前和每次使用之後，請用溫水和肥皂徹底清洗。<br />\r\n* 這款牙膠較硬，適合尋求口腔覺孩子使用<br />\r\n* 不要過分地咬住吊墜的角位或凸起的部份，以免造成窒息危險。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：2cm x6cm<br />\r\n顏色：紅/橙/黃/綠/藍（隨機款式一個）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>適合：4歲以上兒童（請在家長監督下使用）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Rainbow Teether with chain comes with a rainbow colour which makes it attractive to children. It provides rich oral sensory stimulation to help relieve emotions, improve attention and reduce teeth grinding and biting objects. It can also relive anxiety and help children in improving attention. Made in food grade silicone approved by FDA and CE. Free of BPA , PVC phthalates, lead and cadmium. Can be washed by water and soap or dishwasher safe. Come with adjustable chain<strong>.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Wash thoroughly with warm water and soap before and after each use.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Hard in texture and is suitable for children seeking oral stimulation</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Do not chew too hard on the corners or bulging part of the teether as this may cause a choking hazard</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 2cm x 6cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: red/orange/yellow/green/blue (colour to be sent in random)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Suitable for: children over 4 years old (please use under parental supervision)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/175_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/175_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/175_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:27:55', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(176, 4, 0, 'FA4L', '55', '2.5 cm絨毛球連盒 (20粒)', '2.5 cm Fluffy balls with storage box (Qty 20)', '20.00', 5.50, '<p>絨毛球連收納膠盒，是非常好的小肌肉訓練配件！</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式1：0.8cm 直徑 （數量：100粒）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式2：1.5cm 直徑 （數量：80粒）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式3：2.5cm 直徑 （數量：20粒）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3 歲以上兒童 （請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Fluffy balls (with storage box) is great for training small hand muscles!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style 1: 0.8cm diameter (Qty: 100)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style 2: 1.5cm diameter (Qty: 80)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style 3: 2.5cm diameter (Qty: 20)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 3 years and above (Please use under parental supervision to avoid choking risk)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/176_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/176_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/176_3.jpg,assets/products_image/650/176_4.jpg,assets/products_image/650/176_5.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:28:14', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(177, 7, 0, 'ST5R', '20', '軟身泡泡加粗手柄單件 (紅色)', 'Foam Grip Tubing (Red)', '25.00', 12.01, '<p>Impresa 軟身泡泡加粗手柄使用柔軟，舒適的泡沫填充物製造，不含 BPA、鄰苯二甲酸鹽或乳膠，堅固耐用，可配合各種器具，例如鉛筆、牙刷、餐具使用。加粗的手柄令使用者更容易協調及抓握工具，適合兒童及成人使用。 使用鋒利的刀或剪刀就可以把手柄裁剪成需要的長度。耐用塗層防滑且不吸水，易於清潔（洗碗機可用）。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式：紅色單條/黃色單條/藍色單條/一套6條----每色2條</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：所有管長 30.5cm<br />\r\n直徑： 紅-2.7cm(外) 0.9cm(內)；<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 黃色- 3cm(外) 0.7cm(內)；<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 藍色-3.2cm(外) 1.9cm (內)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Impresa foam grip tubing is made with soft, comfortable foam padding and is BPA, Phthalates or Latex free. Strong and durable to use with a variety of everyday objects such as pencils, toothbrushes and cutlery. Offer a wider grip and provide better control and a secure grip, making it suitable for both children and adults. Customize length by cutting the foam tubing with a sharp knife or scissors. Made with non-slip and non-absorbent material which is easy to clean (dishwasher safe).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Quantity: red x1 / yellow x1 / blue x1 / set of 6 ---- 2 of each colour</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: all tubing 30.5cm long&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Diameter: Red - 2.7cm (outer) 0.9cm (inner)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Yellow- 3cm(outer) 0.7cm(inner).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Blue - 3.2cm (outer) 1.9cm (inner)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/177_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/177_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/177_3.jpg,assets/products_image/650/177_4.jpg,assets/products_image/650/177_5.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:29:02', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(178, 4, 0, 'FA7 ', '30', 'GOMA乒乓球 (8個)', 'Ping Pong Balls (8 pieces)', '25.00', 12.50, '<p>除了玩各樣互動球類遊戲，可以用機械手臂玩具夾夾起/用湯匙舀起乒乓球，訓練上肢力量及控制。也可以用來玩吹氣遊戲，訓練核心肌肉力量及口部肌肉運用。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>顏色： 白色</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：直徑4cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3 歲以上兒童 （幼兒請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ping pong balls can be used for different ball games and with a robot toy grabber/ scooper in training upper limb strength and control. Children can also blow ping pong balls for training core muscle strength and improving oral motor skills.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colour: White</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 4cm diameter</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above (Please use under parental supervision to avoid choking risk)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/178_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:30:18', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(179, 17, 0, 'TA5S', '150', '刺猬環 (3件)', 'Sensory Bangle (a set of 3)', '135.00', 64.92, '<p>Impresa 品牌刺猬環採用100％高品質定製配方材料製成，並具有ASTM F963國際玩具標准證書。 無毒且不含BPAs、鄰苯二甲酸鹽和乳膠，確保安全使用。可以隨意簡單地拉伸、拉動、旋轉、擠壓這些玩具，然後讓它們彈回原來的形狀！成為出色的小工具，滿足觸感需要，有助於鎮定情緒，減輕壓力/焦慮並可以增加注意力。產品耐用及安全，適合不同年齡人士使用。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：外圍直徑約10cm，內圈直徑約5cm所有管長 30.5cm<br />\r\n款式：粉紅色/綠色/藍色（隨機發放一款）/一套三色</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Sensory bangle designed by Impresa is made from 100% high quality materials which is nontoxic, BPA, phthalates and latex free. Safe for children&#39;s use. Certified by ASTM F963 Standard Consumer Safety Specification for Toy Safety. The toy is flexible enough to enable pulling, twisting, and squeezing without changing its original shape. Ideal fidget toy in providing tactile stimulation. Able to calm emotions, reduces stress/anxiety and can enhance attention. Durable and suitable for all ages.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: outer diameter approx. 10cm, inner ring diameter approx. 5cm. All tubes 30.5cm long</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style: pink/green/blue (colour to be sent in random) / three colours in a set&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 3 years and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/179_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/179_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:30:18', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(180, 7, 0, 'ST5Y', '25', '軟身泡泡加粗手柄單件 (黃色)', 'Foam Grip Tubing (Yellow)', '25.00', 12.01, '<p>Impresa 軟身泡泡加粗手柄使用柔軟，舒適的泡沫填充物製造，不含 BPA、鄰苯二甲酸鹽或乳膠，堅固耐用，可配合各種器具，例如鉛筆、牙刷、餐具使用。加粗的手柄令使用者更容易協調及抓握工具，適合兒童及成人使用。 使用鋒利的刀或剪刀就可以把手柄裁剪成需要的長度。耐用塗層防滑且不吸水，易於清潔（洗碗機可用）。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式：紅色單條/黃色單條/藍色單條/一套6條----每色2條</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：所有管長 30.5cm<br />\r\n直徑： 紅-2.7cm(外) 0.9cm(內)；<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 黃色- 3cm(外) 0.7cm(內)；<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 藍色-3.2cm(外) 1.9cm (內)</p>\r\n', '<p>Impresa foam grip tubing is made with soft, comfortable foam padding and is BPA, Phthalates or Latex free. Strong and durable to use with a variety of everyday objects such as pencils, toothbrushes and cutlery. Offer a wider grip and provide better control and a secure grip, making it suitable for both children and adults. Customize length by cutting the foam tubing with a sharp knife or scissors. Made with non-slip and non-absorbent material which is easy to clean (dishwasher safe).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Quantity: red x1 / yellow x1 / blue x1 / set of 6 ---- 2 of each colour</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: all tubing 30.5cm long&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Diameter: Red - 2.7cm (outer) 0.9cm (inner)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Yellow- 3cm(outer) 0.7cm(inner).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Blue - 3.2cm (outer) 1.9cm (inner)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/180_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/180_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/180_3.jpg,assets/products_image/650/180_4.jpg,assets/products_image/650/180_5.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:30:46', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(181, 14, 0, 'OM10', '3', '單向吸管', 'One-way Straw', '18.00', 11.90, '<p>ARK品牌的單向吸管適合口肌弱、吸力弱或者未能維持吸力的人士使用。每根吸管都有一個內置閥門，可以單向控制流體的方向&mdash;&mdash;流體向上流入吸管，但不會倒回杯子。由於液體殘留在吸管頂部，因此吸入的空氣更少，喝水所需的力氣也更少，亦減少咳嗽和窒息，提升個人自理能力。單向吸管 由美國製造，不含鉛、鄰苯二甲酸鹽、PVC、BPA 或乳膠。可用於稀液體（水、牛奶、沒有果肉的果汁等），但不建議用於碳酸飲料。能大致吸到蜜糖質地，但未能吸啜到布甸。</p>\r\n', '<p>One-way Straw designed by ARK makes drinking easier for users with a weak suck, oral motor difficulties or problems generating and maintaining suction. Each straw contains a built-in valve that controls the direction of fluid one-way - fluid flows up into the straw but does not empty back into the cup. Therefore, less air is being ingested and less effort is required to drink. Users tend to experience less coughing and choking while consuming fluids.&nbsp;Made in the USA from materials which is BPA, latex, lead, phthalates and PVC free. Can be used for thin liquids&nbsp; (water, milk, juice without pulp, etc) but is not recommended for carbonated drinks. Can also be used for some thickened liquids like &ldquo;nectar&rdquo; consistency but &ldquo;pudding&rdquo; does not work.</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/181_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:31:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(182, 17, 0, 'TA6', '10', '迷你刺猬滾輪 ', 'Mini Spiky Roller', '38.00', 20.11, '<p>以熱塑性橡膠製成的蛋形尖刺滾輪，不含BPAs、鄰苯二甲酸酯和乳膠，<br />\r\n無毒安全。捏握時沒有聲音，不會騷擾其他人。在雙手之間、腳下滾動或在皮膚上滾動，進行按摩。能夠成為出色的小工具，隨時隨地的滿足觸感需要，有助於鎮定情緒，減輕壓力/焦慮並可以增加注意力。產品耐用及安全，適合兒童、青少年和成人。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：直徑大概為4cmx6cm<br />\r\n款式：藍/綠/紅/黃（隨機發放一款）/一套四色</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童</p>\r\n', '<p>This mini spiky roller is made of thermoplastic rubber, free of BPAs, phthalates and latex. Non-toxic and safe for children&#39;s use. Non disturbing to others as no sound comes out when squeezed. A good tool for hand, foot or body massage and satisfying the need of tactile stimulation. It also help calm emotions, reduces stress/anxiety and can increase attention. Durable and safe. Suitable for children, teenagers and adults.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: approx. 4cm x 6cm in diameter</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style: Blue/Green/Red/Yellow (Colour will vary and picked at random at point of despatch) / Set of 4 colours</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 3 and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/182_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:31:41', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
