(187, 14, 0, 'OM12', '10', '吸管哨子(3條)', 'Whistling Straw(a pack of 3)', '20.00', 9.40, '<p>美國進口吸管哨子，可以用於飲用飲料或吹氣，在不喝水時候通過這個塑料吸管吹響口哨。隨時訓練口肌！&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式：一套三條（白色）<br />\r\n尺寸：約23cm</p>\r\n', '<p>Imported from the USA, this straw can be used for drinking. It also whistles when children blow through them for fun. A great way to train oral motor skills.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style: Set of 3: white colour</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: approx. 23cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/187_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:33:26', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(188, 17, 0, 'TA7', '15', '長刺猬滾輪', 'Long Spiky Roller', '38.00', 16.83, '<p>Impresa 品牌長滾輪由100% 優質熱塑性橡膠製成，通過有害化學物質測試，無毒，具低刺激性，不含BPAs、phthalate和乳膠。捏握時沒有聲音，不會為其他人騷擾。在雙手之間、腳下滾動或在皮膚上滾動，進行按摩。成為出色的小工具，隨時隨地的滿足觸感需要，有助於鎮定情緒，減輕壓力/焦慮並可以增加注意力。產品耐用及安全，適合兒童、青少年和成人。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：7.6cm 長 x 3.6cm 直徑<br />\r\n顏色：紅/黃/藍（隨機發放一款）/一套三色</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童</p>\r\n', '<p>This long spiky roller designed by Impresa is made from 100% high quality thermoplastic, free of BPAs, phthalates and latex. Non-toxic and safe for children&#39;s use. Non disturbing to others as no sound comes out when squeezed. A good tool for hand, foot or body massage and satisfying the need of tactile stimulation. It also help calm emotions, reduces stress/anxiety and can increase attention. Durable and safe. Suitable for children, teenagers and adults.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 7.6cm length x 3.6cm diameter</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colour: Red/Yellow/Blue (Colour will vary and picked at random at point of despatch) / Set of 3 colours</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 3 and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/188_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/188_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/188_3.jpg,assets/products_image/650/188_4.jpg,assets/products_image/650/188_5.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:33:52', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(189, 7, 0, 'ST5S', '145', '軟身泡泡加粗手柄 (6件)', 'Foam Grip Tubing (6 pieces)', '135.00', 72.06, '<p>Impresa 軟身泡泡加粗手柄使用柔軟，舒適的泡沫填充物製造，不含 BPA、鄰苯二甲酸鹽或乳膠，堅固耐用，可配合各種器具，例如鉛筆、牙刷、餐具使用。加粗的手柄令使用者更容易協調及抓握工具，適合兒童及成人使用。 使用鋒利的刀或剪刀就可以把手柄裁剪成需要的長度。耐用塗層防滑且不吸水，易於清潔（洗碗機可用）。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式：紅色單條/黃色單條/藍色單條/一套6條----每色2條</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：所有管長 30.5cm<br />\r\n直徑： 紅-2.7cm(外) 0.9cm(內)；<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 黃色- 3cm(外) 0.7cm(內)；<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 藍色-3.2cm(外) 1.9cm (內)</p>\r\n', '<p>Impresa foam grip tubing is made with soft, comfortable foam padding and is BPA, Phthalates or Latex free. Strong and durable to use with a variety of everyday objects such as pencils, toothbrushes and cutlery. Offer a wider grip and provide better control and a secure grip, making it suitable for both children and adults. Customize length by cutting the foam tubing with a sharp knife or scissors. Made with non-slip and non-absorbent material which is easy to clean (dishwasher safe).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Quantity: red x1 / yellow x1 / blue x1 / set of 6 ---- 2 of each colour</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: all tubing 30.5cm long&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Diameter: Red - 2.7cm (outer) 0.9cm (inner)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Yellow- 3cm(outer) 0.7cm(inner).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Blue - 3.2cm (outer) 1.9cm (inner)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/189_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/189_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/189_3.jpg,assets/products_image/650/189_4.jpg,assets/products_image/650/189_5.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:34:19', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(190, 17, 0, 'TA7S', '75', '長刺猬滾輪 (3件)', 'Long Spiky Rollers (a set of 3)', '105.00', 50.49, '<p>Impresa 品牌長滾輪由100% 優質熱塑性橡膠製成，通過有害化學物質測試，無毒，具低刺激性，不含BPAs、phthalate和乳膠。捏握時沒有聲音，不會為其他人騷擾。在雙手之間、腳下滾動或在皮膚上滾動，進行按摩。成為出色的小工具，隨時隨地的滿足觸感需要，有助於鎮定情緒，減輕壓力/焦慮並可以增加注意力。產品耐用及安全，適合兒童、青少年和成人。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：7.6cm 長 x 3.6cm 直徑<br />\r\n顏色：紅/黃/藍（隨機發放一款）/一套三色</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童</p>\r\n', '<p>This long spiky roller designed by Impresa is made from 100% high quality thermoplastic, free of BPAs, phthalates and latex. Non-toxic and safe for children&#39;s use. Non disturbing to others as no sound comes out when squeezed. A good tool for hand, foot or body massage and satisfying the need of tactile stimulation. It also help calm emotions, reduces stress/anxiety and can increase attention. Durable and safe. Suitable for children, teenagers and adults.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 7.6cm length x 3.6cm diameter</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colour: Red/Yellow/Blue (Colour will vary and picked at random at point of despatch) / Set of 3 colours</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 3 and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/190_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/190_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/190_3.jpg,assets/products_image/650/190_4.jpg,assets/products_image/650/190_5.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:34:25', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(191, 5, 0, 'SK2', '8', '1.9cm彩色圓形貼紙 (144貼)', '\"1.9cm Multicolour Label Stickers (114 stickers)\"', '6.00', 1.69, '<p>可用作小肌肉訓練的貼貼紙練習，訓練手指遠端控制能力及手眼協調。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：圓形直徑約1.9cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式：每張共有10個顏色的貼紙，共144個貼紙</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Playing with stickers can train small hand muscles, improve distal finger control and hand-eye coordination.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: circular shape approx. 1.9cm in diameter</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style: 10 types of colour stickers per sheet, 144 stickers in total</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/191_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/191_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:35:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(192, 17, 0, 'TA8', '210', '軟刺猬球 (5件)', 'Soft Spiky Ball Set (a set of 5)', '160.00', 79.50, '<p>Impresa 品牌軟刺猬球，由熱塑性橡膠製成，無毒不含BPAs、鄰苯二甲酸鹽和乳膠，產品耐用及安全。可以用洗碗機清洗。在雙手之間、腳下滾動或在皮膚上滾動，進行按摩。成為出色的小工具，隨時隨地滿足觸感需要，有助於鎮定情緒，減輕壓力/焦慮並可以增加注意力。刺蝟球富有彈性，適合配合滾動/拋接遊戲使用。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：6.3cm 直徑<br />\r\n套裝包括：五個軟刺蝟球 (紅/黃/綠/藍/紫)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>This soft spiky ball set designed by Impresa is made from high quality thermoplastic, free of BPAs, phthalates and latex. Non-toxic and safe for children&#39;s use. Dishwasher safe.A good tool for hand, foot or body massage and satisfying the need of tactile stimulation. It also help calm emotions, reduces stress/anxiety and can increase attention. The elasticity of the ball also makes it ideal tossing games.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 6.3cm diameter</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Set includes: 5 soft spiky balls (red/yellow/green/blue/purple)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/192_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/192_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:35:17', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(193, 14, 0, 'OM15', '15', '變音笛子', 'Slide Whistle', '28.00', 13.20, '<p>美國進口變音笛子，以塑料製成，通過滑動插件快速改變音符，吹出不同音調，用來進行長時間呼氣練習，訓練孩子口肌/核心肌肉力量。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：長23cm<br />\r\n款色：彩色 （隨機發送一款）* 實物與圖片可能有色差</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Imported from the USA. Made in PVC not easy to deform and crack. Tone changes by pulling down the slide. Can be used for breathing exercises to train chidlren&rsquo;s oral motor skills or core muscle strength.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 23cm long</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colour: Various colour available (colour to be sent at random)* Colour difference may occur between the product and the picture</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/193_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:36:03', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(194, 17, 0, 'TA9', '50', '編織球', 'Tactile Knitted Ball', '48.00', 16.20, '<p>英國進口的Play learn編織球色彩豐富，能提供觸感刺激，適合配合各種滾動/拋擲的遊戲使用。拋在地板上會反彈。容易清潔。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：直徑：8cm。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>This tactile knitted ball designed by Play Learn directly imported from the UK. Colourful design and knitted in texture provide tactile stimulation and are ideal for use with a variety of rolling/tossing games. Bounce back when being thrown on the floor. Easy to clean.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: Diameter: 8cm.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/194_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/194_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:36:15', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(195, 14, 0, 'OM16', '5', '笑臉哨子', 'Smiley Face Whistle', '8.00', 2.00, '<p>美國進口笑臉哨子，以塑料製成，吹響哨並拉動滑桿以改變聲音的音高。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>有趣的聲音為你整天帶來歡樂！<br />\r\n<br />\r\n尺寸：長9.5cm（滑動時長12.7cm）<br />\r\n款色：彩色 （隨機發送一款）* 實物與圖片可能有色差</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Imported from the USA. Made in PVC not easy to deform and crack. Tone changes by pulling down the slide. Great entertainment for children in making interesting sounds.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 9.5cm long (12.7cm when sliding)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colour: Various colour available (colour to be sent at random)* Colour difference may occur between the product and the picture</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/195_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:37:18', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(196, 17, 0, 'TA10', '55', '捏捏彈彈球', 'Squishy Ball', '48.00', 20.44, '<p>擠壓，拉伸，拉扯，拋擲，彈跳的 Impresa彈彈球，滿足觸感需要，有助於鎮定情緒，減輕壓力/焦慮並可以增加注意力。尤其適合有焦慮症，注意力缺陷及過度活躍症，自閉症等人士使用。 100％高品質的熱塑性橡膠製成，台灣製造，無添加劑不含BPAs、鄰苯二甲酸鹽和乳膠。擁有超級抗撕裂性，TPR球非常耐用。經常使用後，建議用洗潔精和溫水清洗。風乾後輕輕塗抹少量嬰兒爽身粉，就能使它們像新的一樣好！</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：5.7cm 直徑<br />\r\n顏色：紅/綠/藍 (隨機發放一款) / 一套三色<br />\r\n<br />\r\n建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童</p>\r\n', '<p>Squishy ball is ideal for children to touch, squish, squeeze or pinch to satisfy tactilte stimulation needs. It can help offer calming effect, stress/anxiety relieving and can increase attention. It is particularly suitable for people with anxiety disorders, ADHD, autism, etc. Made in Taiwan from 100% high quality thermoplastic, additives, BPAs, phthalates and latex free. Tear resistant which make it durable for use. Recommend to wash with detergent and warm water after using for a period of time. Apply a small amount of baby powder to make them as good as new when dry after washing.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 5.7cm diameter</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: Red/Green/Blue (Colour will vary and picked at random at point of despatch) / Set of 3 colours</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/196_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/196_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/196_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:37:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(197, 5, 0, 'SK3S', '3', '0.6 cm單色圓形貼紙 (408貼)', '0.6cm Mono Colour Label Stickers (408 stickers)', '4.00', 0.70, '<p>可用作小肌肉訓練的貼貼紙練習，訓練手指遠端控制能力及手眼協調。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式一：1.9cm直徑 (70貼)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式二：1cm直徑 (165貼)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式三：0.6cm直徑 (408貼)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Playing with stickers can train small hand muscles, improve distal finger control and hand-eye coordination.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style 1: 1.9cm diameter (70 stickers)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style 2: 1cm diameter (165 stickers)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style 3: 0.6cm diameter (408 stickers)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/197_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/197_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/197_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:38:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(198, 17, 0, 'TA10S', '16', '捏捏彈彈球 (3件)', 'Squishy Ball (a set of 3)', '135.00', 61.32, '<p>擠壓，拉伸，拉扯，拋擲，彈跳的 Impresa彈彈球，滿足觸感需要，有助於鎮定情緒，減輕壓力/焦慮並可以增加注意力。尤其適合有焦慮症，注意力缺陷及過度活躍症，自閉症等人士使用。 100％高品質的熱塑性橡膠製成，台灣製造，無添加劑不含BPAs、鄰苯二甲酸鹽和乳膠。擁有超級抗撕裂性，TPR球非常耐用。經常使用後，建議用洗潔精和溫水清洗。風乾後輕輕塗抹少量嬰兒爽身粉，就能使它們像新的一樣好！</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：5.7cm 直徑<br />\r\n顏色：紅/綠/藍 (隨機發放一款) / 一套三色<br />\r\n<br />\r\n建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童</p>\r\n', '<p>Squishy ball is ideal for children to touch, squish, squeeze or pinch to satisfy tactilte stimulation needs. It can help offer calming effect, stress/anxiety relieving and can increase attention. It is particularly suitable for people with anxiety disorders, ADHD, autism, etc. Made in Taiwan from 100% high quality thermoplastic, additives, BPAs, phthalates and latex free. Tear resistant which make it durable for use. Recommend to wash with detergent and warm water after using for a period of time. Apply a small amount of baby powder to make them as good as new when dry after washing.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 5.7cm diameter</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: Red/Green/Blue (Colour will vary and picked at random at point of despatch) / Set of 3 colours</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/198_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/198_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/198_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:38:06', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(199, 14, 0, 'OM17', '5', '火車哨子', 'Train Whistle', '18.00', 4.40, '<p>美國進口火車哨子，以塑料製成，吹嘴是扁平的，有特別設計的擋塊防止嘴巴覆蓋音孔。火車造型及聲音吸引孩子練習！&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：：6.3cm長 x 1.3cm寬。<br />\r\n款色：紅/粉紅/綠/黃/藍（隨機發送一款）* 實物與圖片可能有色差</p>\r\n', '<p>Imported from the USA. Made in PVC not easy to deform and crack. Comes with a flat mouthpiece with a specially designed stopper to prevent the mouth from covering the sound hole. Train design and interesting sound makes it attractive for children.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 6.3cm long x 1.3cm wide.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: red/pink/green/yellow/blue (colour to be sent at random)* Colour difference may occur between the product and the picture</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/199_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:38:34', '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
