(200, 17, 0, 'TA11', '44', '捏捏河豚球', 'Squishy Puffer Ball', '48.00', 20.00, '<p>擠壓、拉伸、拉扯、拋擲、用手指扣著指環彈動&hellip;&hellip;放鬆地玩一下這個柔軟的觸感球，擺脫壓力！除了滿足觸感需要，也有助於鎮定情緒，減輕壓力/焦慮並可以增加注意力。尤其適合有焦慮症，注意力缺陷及過度活躍症，自閉症等人士使用。這款球由高品質的橡膠和無毒材料製成，富有彈性，耐用且安全。質地柔軟光滑,方便舒適。​易於清洗、清潔和存放。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n尺寸：12.7cm 直徑<br />\r\n顏色：粉紅/橙/黃/綠/藍/紫 (隨機發放一款)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Squishy puffer ball is ideal for children to touch, squish, squeeze or pinch to satisfy tactilte stimulation needs. It can help offer calming effect, stress/anxiety relieving and can increase attention. It is particularly suitable for people with anxiety disorders, ADHD, autism, etc. Made from high quality thermoplastic and non-toxic materials, safe and durable for use. Easy to be cleaned and washed.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 12.7cm diameter</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: Pink/Orange/Yellow/Green/Blue/Purple (Colour will vary and picked at random at point of despatch)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/200_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/200_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/200_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:39:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(201, 5, 0, 'SK3M', '3', '1cm單色圓形貼紙 (165貼)', '\"1cm Mono Colour Label Stickers (165 stickers)\"', '4.00', 0.70, '<p>可用作小肌肉訓練的貼貼紙練習，訓練手指遠端控制能力及手眼協調。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式一：1.9cm直徑 (70貼)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式二：1cm直徑 (165貼)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式三：0.6cm直徑 (408貼)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Playing with stickers can train small hand muscles, improve distal finger control and hand-eye coordination.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style 1: 1.9cm diameter (70 stickers)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style 2: 1cm diameter (165 stickers)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style 3: 0.6cm diameter (408 stickers)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/201_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/201_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/201_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:39:06', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(202, 14, 0, 'OM18', '5', '汽笛哨子', 'Siren Whistle', '18.00', 4.50, '<p>美國進口汽笛哨子，以塑料製成，逼真的汽笛聲音鼓勵孩子長時間的呼吸，讓空氣持續流動。呼氣和吸氣時都能發出聲音, 訓練孩子口肌/核心肌肉力量。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n尺寸：5cm長 （吹嘴是1.3cm開口）<br />\r\n款色：粉紅/橙/綠/黃/藍（隨機發送一款）* 實物與圖片可能有色差</p>\r\n', '<p>Imported from the USA. Made in PVC not easy to deform and crack. Producing a siren sound when blowing through or sucking air in encourages children to do breathing exercises to train oral motor skills or core muscle strength.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 5cm long (mouthpiece 1.3cm wide)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: pink/orange/green/yellow/blue (colour to be sent at random)* Colour difference may occur between the product and the picture</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/202_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:39:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(203, 17, 0, 'TA12', '25', '觸感拍尺手環', 'Sensory Bracelet', '58.00', 24.02, '<p>Impresa品牌觸感拍尺手環由優質矽膠製成，通過有害化學物質測試，無毒，具低刺激性，不含BPAs、phthalate和乳膠。可以用力拉直，或直接拍到手腕上彎曲。上面的軟刺隨時隨地提供豐富的觸感刺激。產品耐用及安全，適合兒童、青少年和成人，尤其是患有自閉症，專注力不足和焦慮症人士。可以用洗碗機清潔。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：2.5cm寬x21.5cm長x0.6cm厚<br />\r\n顏色：紅/黃/藍（隨機發放一款）/一套三色<br />\r\n<br />\r\n建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Sensory bracelet designed by Impresa is made from high quality non-toxic silicone, free from BPAs, phthalate and latex. It can be stretched straight or applied directly onto the wrist. The soft spikes on the bracelet provide rich tactile stimulation. Durable and safe for children, teenagers and adults, especially those with autism, attention deficit and anxiety disorder. Dishwasher safe.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 2.5cm wide x 21.5cm long x 0.6cm thick</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: Red/Yellow/Blue (Colour will vary and picked at random at point of despatch)/ Set of 3 colours</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 3 years and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/203_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:40:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(204, 6, 0, 'SS1', '20', '小環形剪刀', 'Small Loop Scissors', '45.00', 21.96, '<p>小環形剪刀可以用手指和拇指，或手指和手掌使用。 輕輕擠壓剪刀開始切割，放手釋放壓力後，剪刀會自動重新打開，協助孩子安全地掌握切割動作。適合握力較弱、手部控制不佳或有運動障礙的兒童使用。 使用環形剪刀剪紙，同時訓練手握力及提升手部關節穩定性。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* 刀片設計較適合使用右手為主力手的學童使用</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：5.5cm 寬 x 13.5 長</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Small loop scissors can be operated using the thumb and finger or just the palm. Only require a gentle squeeze to start cutting. Scissors will open if gently releasing the grip. Easy for children to start learning to use scissors. Suitable for children with a weak hand grip, poor hand control or motor difficulties. Doing cutting practice with small loop scissors can build a stronger hand grip and improve distal motor control.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* The blades are designed to be used by right-handed children&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 5.5cm wide x 13.5 long</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/204_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/204_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:40:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(205, 5, 0, 'SK3L', '5', '1.9cm單色圓形貼紙 (70貼)', '1.9cm Mono Colour Label Stickers (70 stickers)', '4.00', 0.70, '<p>可用作小肌肉訓練的貼貼紙練習，訓練手指遠端控制能力及手眼協調。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式一：1.9cm直徑 (70貼)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式二：1cm直徑 (165貼)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式三：0.6cm直徑 (408貼)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Playing with stickers can train small hand muscles, improve distal finger control and hand-eye coordination.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style 1: 1.9cm diameter (70 stickers)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style 2: 1cm diameter (165 stickers)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style 3: 0.6cm diameter (408 stickers)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/205_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/205_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/205_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:40:28', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(206, 14, 0, 'OM20', '0', '懸浮球哨子', '懸浮球哨子	Floating Ball Pipe', '20.00', 7.70, '<p>美國進口懸浮球哨子，需要穩定地持續吹氣，讓球在空中停留更久，提升肺活量。吹哨子除了能訓練孩子口肌/核心肌肉力量外，也可以提升專注力及自我控制能力。跟朋友和家人競賽，成為一個互動小遊戲。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n建議使用年齡：6歲以上</p>\r\n', '<p>This floating ball pipe is imported from the USA. Children need to blow to the holes and blow the ball up to make it stay in the air. It helps train vital capacity and oral motor skills. An ideal toy to play with friends or family.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 6 years and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/206_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/206_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:41:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
