(208, 17, 0, 'TA13', '45', '觸感鬚鬚球', 'Stringy Ball', '58.00', 24.02, '<p>Impresa 品牌觸感鬚鬚球由優質矽膠製成，通過有害化學物質測試，無毒，具低刺激性，不含BPAs、phthalate和乳膠。隨時隨地擠壓，可以提供豐富的觸感刺激，也可以用來作拋接活動。產品耐用及安全，適合兒童、青少年和成人，尤其是患有自閉症，專注力不足和焦慮症人士。可以使用洗碗機清潔。<br />\r\n* 此產品剛開封時有較強烈的杏仁味道</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：2.5cm寬x21.5cm長x0.6cm厚<br />\r\n顏色：紅/黃/藍（隨機發放一款）/一套三色<br />\r\n<br />\r\n建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Stringy ball designed by Impresa is made from high quality non-toxic silicone, free from BPAs, phthalate and latex. Can provide rich tactile stimulation by squeezing them or used in tossing game. Durable and safe for children, teenagers and adults, especially those with autism, attention deficit and anxiety disorder. Dishwasher safe.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*This product has a strong almond smell when it is first opened</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 2.5cm wide x 21.5cm long x 0.6cm thick</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: Red/Yellow/Blue (Colour will vary and picked at random at point of despatch)/ Set of 3 colours</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 3 years and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/208_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/208_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/208_3.jpg,assets/products_image/650/208_4.jpg,assets/products_image/650/208_5.jpg,assets/products_image/650/208_6.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:42:14', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(209, 6, 0, 'SS2', '40', '大環形剪刀', 'Large Loop Scissors', '45.00', 17.02, '<p>大環形剪刀可以用手指和拇指，或手指和手掌使用。 輕輕擠壓剪刀開始切割，放手釋放壓力後，剪刀會自動重新打開，協助孩子安全地掌握切割動作。適合握力較弱、手部控制不佳或有運動障礙的兒童使用。使用環形剪刀剪紙，同時訓練手握力及提升手部關節穩定性。&nbsp;手掌較小學童可以拿近刀片位置，年紀較大及能力較高的學童可以握手柄較後位置。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* 刀片設計較適合使用左手為主力手的學童使用</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：7.5cm 寬 x 19.5cm&nbsp; 長</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Large loop scissors can be operated using the thumb and finger or just the palm. Only require a gentle squeeze to start cutting. Scissors will open if gently releasing the grip. Easy for children to start learning to use scissors. Suitable for children with a weak hand grip, poor hand control or motor difficulties. Doing cutting practice with small loop scissors can build a stronger hand grip and improve distal motor control. Children with smaller palms are suggested to grip closer to the blade on the loop while older children or children with more mature scissors skills can hold further back on the loop.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* The blades are designed to be used by left-handed children&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 7.5cm wide x 19.5 cm long</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/209_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/209_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:42:40', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(210, 17, 0, 'TA13S', '130', '觸感鬚鬚球(3件)', 'Stringy Balls ( a set of 3)', '165.00', 72.06, '<p>Impresa 品牌觸感鬚鬚球由優質矽膠製成，通過有害化學物質測試，無毒，具低刺激性，不含BPAs、phthalate和乳膠。隨時隨地擠壓，可以提供豐富的觸感刺激，也可以用來作拋接活動。產品耐用及安全，適合兒童、青少年和成人，尤其是患有自閉症，專注力不足和焦慮症人士。可以使用洗碗機清潔。<br />\r\n* 此產品剛開封時有較強烈的杏仁味道</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：2.5cm寬x21.5cm長x0.6cm厚<br />\r\n顏色：紅/黃/藍（隨機發放一款）/一套三色<br />\r\n<br />\r\n建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n', '<p>Stringy ball designed by Impresa is made from high quality non-toxic silicone, free from BPAs, phthalate and latex. Can provide rich tactile stimulation by squeezing them or used in tossing game. Durable and safe for children, teenagers and adults, especially those with autism, attention deficit and anxiety disorder. Dishwasher safe.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*This product has a strong almond smell when it is first opened</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 2.5cm wide x 21.5cm long x 0.6cm thick</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: Red/Yellow/Blue (Colour will vary and picked at random at point of despatch)/ Set of 3 colours</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 3 years and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/210_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/210_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/210_3.jpg,assets/products_image/650/210_4.jpg,assets/products_image/650/210_5.jpg,assets/products_image/650/210_6.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:42:49', '2023-04-16 18:59:25'),
(211, 15, 0, 'TL1', '190', '聽樂治療SOUNDS 耳筒', 'Therapeutic Listening Headphone', '1400.00', 868.00, '<p>這是Vital Sounds 與 Koss Stereophones 合作推出專為Therapeutic Listening&reg; 設計的SOUNDS 耳機。新一代耳機有特別定製的貼合吊帶，重量超輕，配戴舒適，可以長時間使用，兒童及成人均適用。耳筒配有3.5毫米電線，可以插在音樂播放器/手提電話 (如使用lightning/type-C插頭需要額外的轉插線)。耳筒由美國直送，未能提供保養，如產品品質有問題，請於到貨後五日內更換產品。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* 沒有包含聽樂治療音樂，需要按接受過相關訓練的治療師指示，購買或租借合適的音樂</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>This headphone is specifically designed for Therapeutic Listening&reg; by Vital Sounds in collaboration with Koss Stereophones. The unique custom fitting sling and lightweight design allow users to wear it comfortably. Suitable for both children and adults. Comes with a detachable 3.5mm cord which can connect to MP3 or mobile phones (require an additional cable for lightning/type-C). Shipped directly from the USA and does not come with warranty. Please contact and exchange within 5 days of purchase if defects are found in the product.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Music for therapeutic listening is not included and should be purchased or rented as instructed by therapis</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/211_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:43:14', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(212, 5, 0, 'SK5', '115', 'AP噴修膠膜', 'AP Masking Film', '35.00', 15.00, '<p>台灣進口的AP 噴修膠膜有弱黏性，不傷紙，可重複撕貼的特性，令貼紙變成Memo 紙一樣重複使用，把孩子最喜歡的貼紙做成更耐用的玩具。也可以用於美工設計，噴修遮修遮擋，一般產品保護，如手機，計算機，照相機...等各式面板熒幕。本品非供玩具使用，請勿直接黏貼於皮膚上。避免陽光直接照射，請置放於陰涼處。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>示範短片：https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JoKY1d0shVA</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸： 14cmx400cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>AP masking film is imported from Taiwan. It is slightly adhesive without causing damage to paper which makes stickers easy to be stuck or tear off. Make your child&rsquo;s favourite stickers reusable and more durable. It can also be used for artwork design or give a layer of protection for products such as mobile phones, calculators, cameras, etc. This product is not a toy and should not be directly applied to skin. Store in a cool place and keep away from direct sunlight.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Demonstration video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JoKY1d0shVA</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 14cmx400cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/212_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:43:33', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(213, 15, 0, 'TL2', '80', '聽樂治療MP3播放器', 'Therapeutic Listening MP3 Player', '400.00', 264.50, '<p>聽樂治療音樂Mp3播放器 (SanDisk Clip Jam Music player 8GB 黑色)電池壽命長，適合配合聽樂治療芯片使用。附送兩條魔術貼帶，可以收納好電線並將播放器固定在耳筒上使用。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* 設定及指示語言為英語<br />\r\n* 聆聽聽樂治療音樂時，請調整為shuffle模式，以隨機模式播放</p>\r\n', '<p>The SanDisk Clip Jam Music player (8GB black) has a long battery life and is ideal to play music for therapeutic listening. Two velcro straps are included for tidying the headphone cord and attaching the MP3 player to the headphones.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Settings and instructions are in English</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Play in shuffle mode when doing therapeutic listening</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/213_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/213_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:44:16', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(214, 6, 0, 'SS3', '30', '兒童安全剪刀', 'Child Safety Scissors', '25.00', 10.90, '<p>台灣品牌雄獅兒童安全剪刀採用無金屬刀片設計，不導電，刀尖以圓角設計，讓幼兒安全使用，可以剪到紙張但不會刺傷手指。 握柄使用人體工學圓弧造型，讓幼兒長時間使用亦感舒適。 動物造型非常可愛！</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：12x6.3x1cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式：大嘴鳥/鯨魚/鱷魚 （隨機款式1件）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：2.5歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Taiwanese brand Simbalion child safety scissors are designed without metal blades that do not conduct electricity and have blunted ends to make them safe for children to use. Small and ergonomic designed handles are easy for children to grip and maneuver. Animal designs are cute and attractive to children.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 12x6.3x1cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style: Bird / Whale / Crocodile (style to be sent in random)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 2.5 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/214_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/214_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/214_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:44:21', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(215, 5, 0, 'SK6', '20', '動物造型貼紙 (10張)', 'Animals Stickers (10 pieces)', '28.00', 12.40, '<p>每隻動物都有不同的面部表情和配件。孩子們可以創造自己喜歡的風格。配件貼紙可以輕鬆撕下，重複黏貼到主體上，不怕黏錯。把完成的動物貼到各種的物件上，成爲特別的作品。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>此工具可以訓練手眼協調和手指靈活度。也足以讓孩子創造自己的動物世界，使他們忙碌，外出時帶著幾張，讓孩子安靜地專注起來。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸： 每張 11x16cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式： 20款動物，隨機發放其中10款 （每款有12～20張小貼紙）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Each piece of sticker includes different facial expressions and outfits for each animal. Children can create how the animal looks by putting stickers of facial expressions and outfits onto each animal. The stickers are easy to be stuck or tear off which is reusable for children to create different animals.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Stickers are great for developing hand-eye coordination and finger dexterity. It is also a great way to keep children attentive and quiet when going out by keeping them busy designing their own animal world.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 11x16cm each</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style: 20 types of animals, 10 types of animals to be sent in random (12-20 small stickers each)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/215_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/215_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:44:43', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(216, 17, 0, 'TA15', '45', '夜光魷魚吸盤匙扣  ', 'Glow-in-The-Dark Fidget Squids', '88.00', 33.63, '<p>Impresa品牌魷魚形狀的觸覺玩具，魷魚觸手上有吸盤，可以貼在幾乎任何光滑的表面上。用手指尖提起剝開吸盤，能聽到「啪」的清脆爆裂聲音。把魷魚放在光源下放置幾分鐘，在漆黑的環境中它就會發光，成為黑暗中的玩具！ 把匙扣扣在書包上，可以隨時隨地提供觸感刺激，滿足感覺需要。安全無毒物料，不含BPAs。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n尺寸：17.8cm x 8.9cm<br />\r\n顏色：灰色/青色/藍色（隨機發放一款）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>This glow-in-the-dark fidget squid comes with suction cups on the tentacles which can stick to almost any smooth surface. Pop sound comes out when lifting up one end of the suction cups to peel. The toy can glow in the dark after putting under light for few minutes. It also comes with a keychain that children can carry the toy along even when going to school. Offer tactile stimulation at anytime. Made from safe and non-toxic material, free of BPAs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 17.8cm x 8.9cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: grey/cyan/blue (Colour will vary and picked at random at point of despatch)</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/216_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/216_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/216_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:45:23', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(217, 15, 0, 'TL3', '15', '聽樂治療耳筒替換電線', 'Therapeutic Listening Replacement Cord', '75.00', 41.00, '<p>耳機電線經長期折疊容易損壞需要替換。專門用於 SOUNDS 耳機的原裝替換線。長度約1.2米標準耳機線，帶有標準 3.5 毫米鍍金插頭。</p>\r\n', '<p>Headphone cords are prone to damage over time. SOUNDS headphone replacement cord in 1.2m with 3.5mm plug</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/217_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:45:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(218, 5, 0, 'SK10', '35', '工程車印章', 'Car Stamp Set', '40.00', 22.22, '<p>孩子最愛的工程車印仔套裝，是訓練前三指力量和手眼協調的好工具。印章不含 BPA、無毒，通過了 CPSIA 和 ASTM 測試。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n尺寸：高3.8厘米 ；直徑2.5厘米</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式： 一套6款工程車</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：2歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Car stamp set is a great tool for training tripod grasp and hand-eye coordination. The stamp is BPA free, non-toxic and has passed the CPSIA and ASTM tests.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 3.8cm high; 2.5cm diameter</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style: 6 types of car in a set</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 2 years and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/218_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:46:02', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(219, 6, 0, 'SS4', '25', '彈弓輔助剪刀', 'Spring Adaptive Scissors', '36.00', 12.77, '<p>Maped Koopy彈弓輔助剪刀由國際知名的人體工學專家團隊創建，採用不鏽鋼刀片能良好地切割紙張。中間有彈弓能隨時撥動開關，撥開後按下手柄並鬆手，剪刀會自動打開，適合幼兒學習剪紙時使用。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：約12.7cm 長</p>\r\n\r\n<p>顏色：黑白&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：2.5歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Maped Koopy spring adaptive scissors are designed by a team of internationally renowned ergonomic experts. Its stainless-steel blade cut paper well. Metal blades with a spring-assisted mechanism can be activated at any time. Blades open automatically using spring action when gently releasing the grasp to assist cutting.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: approx. 12.7cm long</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colour: black and white&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 2.5 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/219_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/219_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:46:54', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(220, 15, 0, 'WB1', '500', '1磅重力海獅公仔', '1 lb Weighted Toy Sea Lion', '520.00', 240.00, '<p>超柔軟毛絨的重力海獅公仔，利用深層壓力刺激療法的原理，為有需要的兒童，特別是受感統失調影響的兒童，提供本體感覺，有效達致舒緩情緒及冷靜作用。如果孩子在睡覺時遇到困難,重力公仔將使他們感到更加平靜和放鬆,並更快入睡。它也可以成為一個腰枕，並在工作時支撐背部。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n尺寸：60cm ; 重量：1lb<br />\r\n<br />\r\n建議使用磅數：體重約10磅以上&nbsp; (以體重約10%的磅數來選擇重力墊)</p>\r\n', '<p>This weighted toy sea lion is particularly designed for children with sensory processing disorders. It makes use of benefits of weighted therapy as weight can provide a calming effect helping attention span and reducing excessive fidgeting. Ideal for use during bedtime or as a lumbar support when sitting upright.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 60cm; Weight: 1lb</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended weight: approx. 10lb or more (approx 10% of the user&rsquo;s body weight)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/220_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:47:56', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(221, 5, 0, 'SK11', '10', '動物印章', 'Animal stamp', '6.00', 2.01, '<p>可愛的動物印章，是訓練前三指力量和手眼協調的好工具。印章不含 BPA、無毒，通過了 CPSIA 和 ASTM 測試。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：高3.8厘米 ；直徑2.5厘米</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式：陸地生物/海洋生物/飛鳥（隨機款式1件）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：2歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Animal stamp is a great tool for training tripod grasp and hand-eye coordination. The stamp is BPA free, non-toxic and has passed the CPSIA and ASTM tests.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 3.8cm high; 2.5cm diameter</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style: Land animals / Sea animals / Bird (style to be sent in random)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 2 years and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/221_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/221_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/221_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:48:27', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(222, 15, 0, 'WB2', '910', '2磅重力啡熊公仔', '2lb Weighted Toy Bear', '520.00', 248.00, '<p>重力啡熊公仔由柔軟的棉和加重的豆子製成，可以放置在任何地方，用深層壓力刺激療法的原理，為有需要的兒童，特別是受感統失調影響的兒童，提供本體感覺，有效達致舒緩情緒及冷靜作用。如果孩子在睡覺時遇到困難，重力公仔將使他們感到更加平靜和放鬆，並更快入睡。它也可以成為一個腰枕，並在工作時支撐背部。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>** 加重填充動物是真空包裝,打開包裝後,請拍打絨毛身體。<br />\r\n正常情況下，需要24 小時才能恢復完整。放左陽光下會恢復得更快。&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n尺寸：48cm 長 ；重量：2lb</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用磅數：體重約15磅以上 (以體重約10%的磅數來選擇重力墊)</p>\r\n', '<p>This weighted toy bear is made from soft cotton and weighted beans to give sensory relief to children. It is particularly designed for children with sensory processing disorders. It makes use of benefits of weighted therapy as weight can provide a calming effect helping attention span and reducing excessive fidgeting. Ideal for use during bedtime or as a lumbar support when sitting upright.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>** It is vacuum sealed in the delivery. Please rub the fur of the toy bear upon removing the vacuum sealing package&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It will take 24 hours to make the toy soft again. Putting under the sun may help with it become fluffy again</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 48cm long; Weight: 2lb</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended weight: approx. 15lb or more (approx 10% of the user&rsquo;s body weight)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/222_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:49:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(223, 5, 0, 'SK12', '30', '時鐘原子印', 'Clock Stamp', '10.00', 3.40, '<p>用原子印蓋印可以訓練手指力量，上面有能吸引孩子練習的數字排列。年紀較大的孩子可以用時鐘印章來學習時間。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n款式：藍/淺藍/寶藍/粉紅/黃（隨機顏色1件）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：原子印高7.5cm ； 印章直徑約2.7cm<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：2歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Stamping with clock stamp can build finger strength and it is designed with numbers to enhance children&rsquo;s motivation to practice. Older children can use the clock stamp to learn telling the time.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style: blue/light blue/navy blue/pink/yellow (colour sent in random)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 7.5cm high; approx. 2.7cm diameter</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 2 years and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/223_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:49:53', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(224, 6, 0, 'SS5L', '35', '左手四孔輔助剪刀', 'Dual-control Scissors (Left-handed)', '38.00', 9.32, '<p>這款英國進口，特別設計的剪刀有四個孔，能良好地切割紙張，讓成人可以同時握著剪刀，教導孩子安全地正確使用工具。兒童剪刀採用安全的鈍尖設計，添加彈弓協助學童學習剪刀的開合控制。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* 刀片設計較適合使用左手為主力手的學童使用</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>顏色：藍色</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：15&nbsp;厘米 （刀片長度 5厘米)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3歲以上學童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Imported from the UK. Double loops on each handle of this specially designed scissors allow parents and children to simultaneously complete the cutting action. Parents can use loops closest to the blade to assist children with the control of the scissors. The scissors have blunted ends to make them safe for children to use and come with a spring-assisted mechanism which is easier for children to learn scissors skills.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* The blades are designed to be used by left-handed children&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colour: Blue</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 15cm (blade length 5cm)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/224_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/224_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:50:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(225, 5, 0, 'SK15', '345', '手指畫顏料連印章', 'Washable Finger Paints with Stamps', '98.00', 54.40, '<p>台灣品牌雄獅手指畫顏料由可洗式顏料、水、抑菌劑、甘油製成，安全無毒，不傷肌膚。扭開蓋子，即可用手指沾上顏料畫畫，發揮小創意。 瓶蓋上方的造型海綿，沾取顏料可印出不同圖形。可水洗手指畫顏料只要以清水或用洗手液，輕鬆洗淨不殘留。 顏料還特別添加天然苦味劑，避免兒童舔食。提供豐富的觸感輸入，同時訓練手眼協調等能力。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>套裝：20g x 10色</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：2.5歲以上兒童（請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Simbalion washable finger paint is made of washable paint, water, antibacterial agent and glycerin which is safe and non-toxic for children&#39;s use. Children can do finger painting by dipping their fingers into the paints. The sponge on the top of the cap can be dipped into the paint to stamp different shapes. This washable paint is easily washed off with water or soap. This paint also comes with a naturally bitter taste to prevent children from licking it. Provide children with rich tactile input and develop hand-eye coordination at the same time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Set: 20g x 10 colours</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 2.5 years and above (please use under parental supervision to avoid choking hazard)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/225_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/225_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/225_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:51:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(226, 15, 0, 'WB4D', '1900', '4磅動物重力墊（小狗）', '4lb Weighted Animal Lap Pad   (Puppy)', '520.00', 337.70, '<p>SENSORY4U的動物重力墊採用深層壓力刺激療法的原理，為有需要的兒童，特別是受感統失調影響的兒童，提供本體感覺，有效達致舒緩情緒及冷靜作用。重力墊可以作被子/加重膝墊使用，協助提升睡眠質素/安坐能力。請拆卸玻璃珠填充墊後手洗清潔。可以放在微波爐加熱，提升舒適感。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：56cm 長x43cm 寬；重量；4lb<br />\r\n款式：小狗/樹懶</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用磅數：體重約30磅或以上 (以體重約10%的磅數來選擇重力墊)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>The SENSORY4U weighted animal lap pad is particularly designed for children with sensory processing disorders. It makes use of benefits of weighted therapy as weight can provide a calming effect helping attention span and reducing excessive fidgeting. It can be used to apply deep pressure to the lap when the user is sitting down or sleeping. Effective in enhancing sleeping quality or attention span. Can be hand washed after removing plastic beads. Microwave safe to provide warmth.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 56cm long x 43cm wide; Weight: 4lb</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style: Puppy / Sloth</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended weight: approx. 30lbs or more (approx 10% of the user&rsquo;s body weight)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/226_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/226_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:51:34', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(227, 6, 0, 'SS5R', '30', '右手四孔輔助剪刀', 'Dual-control Scissors (Right-handed)', '38.00', 9.32, '<p>這款英國進口，特別設計的剪刀有四個孔，能良好地切割紙張，讓成人可以同時握著剪刀，教導孩子安全地正確使用工具。兒童剪刀採用安全的鈍尖設計。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* 刀片設計較適合使用右手為主力手的學童使用</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>顏色：紅色</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：15&nbsp;厘米 （刀片長度 5厘米)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3歲以上學童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Imported from the UK. Double loops on each handle of this specially designed scissors allow parents and children to simultaneously complete the cutting action. Parents can use loops closest to the blade to assist children with the control of the scissors. The scissors have blunted ends to make them safe for children to use.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* The blades are designed to be used by right-handed children&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colour: Red</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 15cm (blade length 5cm)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 3 years and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/227_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/227_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:51:48', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(228, 15, 0, 'WB4S', '1930', '4磅動物重力墊（樹懶）', '4lb Weighted Animal Lap Pad   (Sloth)', '520.00', 337.70, '<p>SENSORY4U的動物重力墊採用深層壓力刺激療法的原理，為有需要的兒童，特別是受感統失調影響的兒童，提供本體感覺，有效達致舒緩情緒及冷靜作用。重力墊可以作被子/加重膝墊使用，協助提升睡眠質素/安坐能力。請拆卸玻璃珠填充墊後手洗清潔。可以放在微波爐加熱，提升舒適感。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：56cm 長x43cm 寬；重量；4lb<br />\r\n款式：小狗/樹懶</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用磅數：體重約30磅或以上 (以體重約10%的磅數來選擇重力墊)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>The SENSORY4U weighted animal lap pad is particularly designed for children with sensory processing disorders. It makes use of benefits of weighted therapy as weight can provide a calming effect helping attention span and reducing excessive fidgeting. It can be used to apply deep pressure to the lap when the user is sitting down or sleeping. Effective in enhancing sleeping quality or attention span. Can be hand washed after removing plastic beads. Microwave safe to provide warmth.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 56cm long x 43cm wide; Weight: 4lb</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style: Puppy / Sloth</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended weight: approx. 30lbs or more (approx 10% of the user&rsquo;s body weight)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/228_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/228_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:53:20', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(229, 6, 0, 'SS7', '30', '左手剪刀', 'Left-handed Scissors', '28.00', 8.71, '<p>這款剪刀適合提昇剪紙技巧的兒童適用，帶有柔軟舒適握柄，符合人體工學；帶不銹鋼刀片的鈍頭剪刀具有耐磨性，能長時間使用。刀片上有厘米小尺子可以量度剪紙長度。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：13.8cm 長 x 5.6 寬<br />\r\n顏色：藍色/紫色 （隨機款式1件）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3歲以上學童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>These scissors are suitable for children who want to improve their scissors skills. Come with a soft and comfortable grip and stainless steel blades which is ideal for long term use. Centimeter measurements are marked on blades to measure the length of the paper cut.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 13.8cm long x 5.6 wide</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colour: Blue/Purple (colour to be sent in random)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 3 years and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/229_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:54:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(230, 15, 0, 'WB4B', '1820', '4磅重力黑狗仔墊', '4lb Weighted Black Dog Lap Pad', '680.00', 360.00, '<p>BARMY重力黑狗仔墊有超柔軟毛絨材質，利用深層壓力刺激療法的原理，為有需要的兒童，特別是受感統失調影響的兒童，提供本體感覺，有效達致舒緩情緒，冷靜作用。如果孩子在睡覺時遇到困難,重力公仔將使他們感到更加平靜和放鬆,並更快入睡。重力墊裝在堅固的 PVC 袋中，配有堅固的手柄，方便攜帶。外套可拆卸和清洗。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：48cm x 64cm；重量：4lb</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用磅數：體重約30磅或以上 (以體重約10%的磅數來選擇重力墊)</p>\r\n', '<p>BARMY weighted dog lap pad is made from plush fabric material. It is particularly designed for children with sensory processing disorders. It makes use of benefits of weighted therapy as weight can provide a calming effect helping attention span and reducing excessive fidgeting. Ideal for providing deep pressure in keeping children feeling calm and relaxed during bedtime. Lap pad comes with a PVC tote bag with handles to carry lap pad anywhere you want. The cover is removable and washable.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 48cm x 64cm; Weight: 4lb</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended weight: approx. 30lb or more (approx 10% of the user&rsquo;s body weight)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/230_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:54:27', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(231, 17, 0, 'TA16', '6', '金屬手指環 (2件)', 'Spiky Metallic Ring (2 colours)', '18.00', 3.93, '<p>這些輕巧的觸感小玩具由100％優質不銹鋼製成，安全耐用。套在手指上，簡單地上下滾動或者用其他手指觸摸指環的表面，可以取得豐富的觸感刺激，同時不會造成對別人的打擾。適合兒童甚至成人使用。這些觸感手指環有助於鎮定情緒、舒緩焦慮緊張、減輕壓力並提昇專注力。細小輕巧的指環可隨身攜帶！</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：直徑約 2.5 厘米<br />\r\n顏色： 金/銀/紅/藍/綠（隨機發放兩件）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：4 歲以上兒童（請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n', '<p>These lightweight spiky metallic rings are made from 100% high quality stainless steel and are safe and durable. Simply putting them on fingers or doing a hand massage can provide rich tactile stimulation. Suitable for children and even adults. Ideal tools for calming emotions, relieving anxiety and stress and improving attention. Small and light weight easy to carry around!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: approx. 2.5 cm diameter</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: Gold/Silver/Red/Blue/Green (2 colours will be picked at random at point of dispatch)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 4 and above (please use under parental supervision to avoid choking hazard)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/231_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/231_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/231_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:56:21', '2023-04-16 18:56:50'),
(232, 15, 0, 'WB4L', '2000', '4.4磅重力蜥蜴公仔', '4.4lb Weighted Toy Lizard', '680.00', 466.50, '<p>讓可愛柔軟的Manimo加重蜥蝪公仔，成為孩子的小伙伴。適合日常使用，在家中、學校、車中... 攜帶去任何孩子喜歡去的地方。採用深層壓力刺激療法原理，讓有需要的兒童，特別是受感統失調影響的兒童使用。提供本體感覺，有效達致舒緩情緒及冷靜作用。把加重動物放在膝蓋、肩膀、胸部或腿上，用於放鬆，促進睡眠。使用優質Lycra面料製成，填充無毒聚乙烯珠子，經久耐用。可手洗清潔。天氣炎熱時，可以把動物公仔放到冰箱裏，取出即可享受冰涼感覺！<br />\r\n<br />\r\n款式：藍色蜥蝪<br />\r\n尺寸：72cmx37cmx6.5cm；重量：4.4 lb</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用磅數：體重約30磅或以上 (以體重約10%的磅數來選擇重力墊)</p>\r\n', '<p>This Manimo weighted toy lizard is a good companion to children. Ideal for everyday use at home, school, in the car, etc. It is particularly designed for children with sensory processing disorders. It makes use of benefits of weighted therapy as weight can provide a calming effect helping attention span and reducing excessive fidgeting. It can be used to apply deep pressure to different body parts to let children relax and promote sleep. Made from high quality Lycra fabric and filled with non-toxic polyethylene beads. Can be handwashed and put in fridge to make it cool during summer.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Design: Blue lizard</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 72cmx37cmx6.5cm; Weight: 4.4 lb</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended weight: approx. 30 lbs or more (approx 10% of the user&rsquo;s body weight</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/232_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/232_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:58:18', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(233, 17, 0, 'TA17', '30', '珍寶彈力條', 'Jumbo Stretchy String', '18.00', 5.33, '<p>珍寶彈力條，讓你隨時隨地拉扯、擠壓、彎曲！成爲滿足觸感需要的Fidget toys! 也可以用來玩抛接游戲和成為阻力帶訓練手力。這些感官玩具由無毒、無過敏性材料製成，不含 BPAs、鄰苯二甲酸鹽和乳膠。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：直徑 33 cm （最長延伸到3m）<br />\r\n顏色：粉紅/橙/黃/綠/藍/紫（隨機發放一件）<br />\r\n* 注意此產品有色差，請參考實物圖</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童<br />\r\n（請在家長監督下使用，避免纏繞頸部導致窒息）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Jumbo stretchy string are ideal for children to pull, squish or twist anywhere you want. A great fidget toys to satisfy tactilte stimulation needs. It is also ideal for tossing game or used as resistance bands to build hand muscle strength. Made from non-toxic, non-allergenic materials and are free from BPAs, phthalates and latex.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 33 cm diameter (can be stretched up to 3m)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: pink/orange/yellow/green/blue/purple (Colour will vary and picked at random at point of despatch)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Please note that there are colour differences in this product, please refer to the photo of the product&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 3 years and above&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(Please use under parental supervision to avoid choking due to entanglement around the neck)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/233_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/233_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 18:59:04', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(234, 17, 0, 'TA18', '30', '迷你波子隧道 (4件)', 'Mini Marble Tunnel Fidgets (4 colours)', '40.00', 13.35, '<p>迷你波子隧道適合兒童，青少年甚至成年人在休閒時間或焦慮狀況下使用，也有助於ADHD / ADD / OCD專注力缺乏及過度活躍症，自閉症，感覺統合障礙，抑鬱症和焦慮症人士保持專注和舒緩情緒。隨時隨地玩耍, 打發時間，減輕壓力。適合任何地方使用！可水洗和風乾。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>定價：尺寸：10.5cmx2.5cm<br />\r\n顏色：紅/橙/黃/綠/藍/紫/粉紅/黑/白（隨機發放四件）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童 （請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>This mini marble tunnel fidgets is suitable for children, teenagers or adults to use during free time or is also useful for people with ADHD / ADD / OCD, autism, sensory integration disorder, depression or anxiety disorders to stay focused and soothe their emotions. Play anywhere, anytime to reduce stress. Can be washed by hands.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Pricing: Size: 10.5cmx2.5cm&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: red/orange/yellow/green/blue/purple/pink/black/white (4 colours will be picked at random at point of dispatch)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above (please use under parental supervision to avoid choking hazard)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/234_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/234_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/234_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 19:00:38', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(235, 15, 0, 'WB5K', '2500', '5磅籃球重力墊', '5lb Weighted Basketball Lap Pad', '520.00', 322.00, '<p>FRIENDLY CUDDLE 的籃球重力墊，採用深層壓力刺激療法原理，為有需要的兒童，特別是受感統失調影響的兒童，提供本體感覺，有效達致舒緩情緒，冷靜作用。此重力墊由優質材料製成，加固縫線有助於防止撕裂和撕裂，專為終身使用和舒適而設計。可作被子/加重膝墊使用，協助提升睡眠質素/安坐能力。在移動時，微珠不會發出噪音。產品通過美國CPSC安全測試。外套可以輕易脫下，用洗衣機清洗。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：直徑 53.5cm；重量；5lb</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用磅數：體重約40磅或以上 (以體重約10%的磅數來選擇重力墊)</p>\r\n', '<p>This FRIENDLY CUDDLE weighted basketball lap pad is particularly designed for children with sensory processing disorders. It makes use of the benefits of weighted therapy as weight can provide a calming effect helping attention span and reducing excessive fidgeting. It is made from high quality materials with reinforced stitching to help prevent rips and tears for long term use. It can be used to apply deep pressure to the lap when the user is sitting down or sleeping. Effective in enhancing sleeping quality or attention span. Micro beads will not produce noise when moving around.&nbsp;This product has passed US CPSC standard. The cover is removable and machine washable.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 53.5cm diameter; Weight: 5lb</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended weight: approx. 40lb or more (approx 10% of the user&rsquo;s body weight)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/235_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/235_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 19:01:47', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(236, 17, 0, 'TA19', '25', '扭扭鎖鏈', 'Fidget Chain', '20.00', 5.29, '<p>每個扭扭鎖鏈都有24個連接鎖扣，每一個鎖扣位都可以扭轉和鎖定在不同的位置，以多種方式構建出不同的狀態和形狀，鼓勵兒童發揮手眼協調、雙手協調、手指靈活度等小肌肉技巧，此外，激發兒童在仿砌或創造不同圖案時候的視覺空間及執行能力。不停的扭動更是適合手動覺尋求刺激的兒童，滿足雙手活動的感覺需要，也是感官玩具的好選擇。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：26.8cmx1cm<br />\r\n顏色：藍+橙/橙+綠/綠+藍&nbsp; （隨機發放一款）<br />\r\n<br />\r\n建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童（請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Each chain has 24 links and can be snapped and clicked in different positions to create different shapes or patterns in a variety of ways. Help strengthen hand-eye coordination, bilateral hand coordination and finger dexterity. It can also develop visual-spatial skills and executive function when building and shaping the chain. Frequent snapping and use of the chain can also provide tactile stimulation to kids in need of stimulation. Is an ideal sensory toy.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 26.8cmx1cm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: Blue + Orange / Orange + Green / Green + Blue (Colour will vary and picked at random at point of despatch)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above (please use under parental supervision to avoid choking hazard)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/236_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/236_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/236_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 19:01:47', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(237, 17, 0, 'TA24', '90', '鯊魚扭扭關節玩具', 'Wiggle Shark', '180.00', 90.22, '<p>日本進口，採用安全優質材料，&nbsp;以先進的3D打印技術製成的鯊魚扭扭玩具，內部堅固，可自由彎曲，不易掉落和折斷。這款減壓玩具在搖動時會發出可以令人放鬆的聲音。19個關節非常靈活，可以360度旋轉。每個接駁位都可以單獨拆卸和重新安裝成喜歡的顏色。鯊魚玩具重量輕省，攜帶方便到任何地方使用，滿足觸感及手動感需要，可以成為長時間陪伴孩子的好朋友！&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：20 x 5.5 x 7 cm; 重量：90 g</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：6歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Imported from Japan and made from safe and high quality materials. Made by 3D printing technology making it strong and flexible for toy use without breaking easily. Produce soothing sound when being wiggled. Consists of 19 flexible joints and can be rotated 360 degrees. Each joint can be individually taken out and reassembled in the colour of your choice. Lightweight and easy to carry, making it a great tactile toy!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 20 x 5.5 x 7 cm; Weight: 90 g</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 6 years and above&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/237_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/237_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 19:02:44', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(238, 17, 0, 'PF8', '70', 'Playfoam春季套裝', 'Playfoam Spring Set', '68.00', 12.75, '<p>Educational Insight出品的 Playfoam 春季套裝，每個套裝包括4塊彩色迷你泡棉磚塊，可以按著需要和興趣捏成不同的形狀，發揮創意。台灣製造柔軟無毒的泡泡棉物料，不粘手，可以隨身攜帶。提供豐富的觸覺感覺刺激，幫助發展精細的小肌肉技巧。開封後建議使用密封盒收納避免乾燥。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n款式：綠/藍/粉紅/橙 （隨機發放一款）<br />\r\n<br />\r\n建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童（請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n', '<p>Educational Insight Spring Set, each set includes,<br />\r\n1. 4 pieces of colourful playfoam bricks<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Children can learn numbers/counting/letters/animals by placing the foam on the cardboards. They can squeeze playfoam into different shapes according to their needs and interests. Made in Taiwan, the soft, non-toxic material is non-stick and can be carried around. Provides rich tactile stimulation to help develop fine smotor skills and learn the correct way to form letters. Is recommended to store in an airtight box to avoid drying out once opened</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style: Green/Blue/Pink/Orange (randomly distributed)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above (for young children, please use under parental supervision to choking risk )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/238_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/238_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/238_3.jpg,assets/products_image/650/238_4.jpg,assets/products_image/650/238_5.jpg,assets/products_image/650/238_6.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 19:03:20', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(239, 15, 0, 'WB15X', '0', '重力緊身背心 (XS) ', 'Compression Vest (XS)', '720.00', 447.00, '<p>Special Supplies 重力緊身背心提供充分的本體覺刺激，讓孩子可以冷靜，減少多動/活躍及焦慮情緒，變得更專注、平靜和放鬆。背心重量可以隨個人需要調節，添加或移除 &frac12; 或 &frac14; 磅小沙包*。背心柔軟、透氣、專為舒適地包覆肩膀和身體中部而設計，有良好的支撐性協助保持直立坐姿，適合活動/安坐時穿著，在任何地方都可以穿着。可用洗衣機清洗。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* 大號,中號,小號： 2個 &frac12;磅 及 4個&frac14;磅沙包<br />\r\n* 加小號： 2個 &frac12;磅 及 2個&frac14;磅沙包<br />\r\n<br />\r\n【購買前先量度肩膊到腰(長)x圍繞胸口一周(寬)尺寸】<br />\r\n加小碼 14寸長x24寸寬<br />\r\n小碼&nbsp; 17寸長x30寸寬<br />\r\n中碼&nbsp; 20寸長x36寸寬<br />\r\n大碼&nbsp; 24寸長x42寸寬</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 如果沒有完美吻合的尺寸，建議買大一個尺寸，收緊時，最多可以減5寸。請在預訂前仔細量度尺寸！因衛生問題也不設退換其他尺寸。</p>\r\n', '<p>Special Supplies Compression Vest provides proprioceptive input which allows children to calm down and become more focused and relaxed. Weight of the vest is adjustable by adding or removing a &frac12; or &frac14; lbs sandbag. The vest is made of breathable and flexible neoprene which offers good support at the sides and shoulder. Ideal in maintaining an upright sitting position can be&nbsp; used in doing different activities. Machine washable.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Large, Medium, Small: 2 x &frac12;lb and 4 x &frac14;lb sandbags</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Extra Small: 2 x &frac12;lb and 2 x &frac14;lb sandbags</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please measure from shoulder to waist (length) x around the chest (width) before purchase</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Extra small 14&quot; long x 24&quot; wide</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Small 17&quot; long x 30&quot; wide</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Medium 20&quot; long x 36&quot; wide</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Large 24&quot; long x 42&quot; wide</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please go with the larger size when in doubt as the vest can be adjusted to 5&rsquo;&rsquo;smaller than the chest size listed above. Please measure accurately for the correct size before purchase. Not exchangeable due to hygienic reasons.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/239_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 19:04:15', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(240, 17, 0, 'TA30', '550', 'Bunchems 蓬蓬球400粒套裝', 'Bunchems Ball Set (Qty 400)', '420.00', 207.44, '<p>蓬蓬球上有很多軟身倒鈎，可以互相黏在一起，隨意變換創造出不同圖案。不會黏手，卻能提供豐富的觸感刺激。組裝過程，也可以訓練手眼協調，手指靈活性及手指力量。蓬蓬球可以黏到魔術貼的毛毛表面及絲巾上，有配合不同訓練的玩法。也可以做成不同大小的球，玩各類拋接遊戲。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>注意: 需要在成人監督下使用。不要靠近頭髮！！！！！ 如果小朋友有長頭髮的話，請先束起頭髮。如不慎被纏繞到頭髮，請在頭髮上塗抹潤髮乳/植物油/髮油，待頭髮變得足夠潤滑後，再慢慢取出。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童（請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Each Bunchem ball has flexible ft hooks that allow them to stick to one another without the use of glue. Provide endless possibilities for kids to build while providing rich tactile stimulation. It can also provide training on hand-eye coordination, finger dexterity and finger strength. It can also be attached to Velcro or silk scarves for a variety of training purposes. It can also be made into different sizes of balls for different kinds of throwing and catching games.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Note: Adult supervision is required. Keep away from hair ！！！！！Please tie the hair up if your child has long hair. Apply hair conditioner/vegetable oil/hair oil to hair and wait until hair is sufficiently moisturized to slowly remove bunchems out of hair if they tangled with hair.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 3 years and above (please use under parental supervision to avoid choking risk)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/240_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/240_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 19:04:29', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(241, 15, 0, 'WB15M', '0', '重力緊身背心 (M) ', 'Compression Vest (M)', '720.00', 447.00, '<p>Special Supplies 重力緊身背心提供充分的本體覺刺激，讓孩子可以冷靜，減少多動/活躍及焦慮情緒，變得更專注、平靜和放鬆。背心重量可以隨個人需要調節，添加或移除 &frac12; 或 &frac14; 磅小沙包*。背心柔軟、透氣、專為舒適地包覆肩膀和身體中部而設計，有良好的支撐性協助保持直立坐姿，適合活動/安坐時穿著，在任何地方都可以穿着。可用洗衣機清洗。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* 大號,中號,小號： 2個 &frac12;磅 及 4個&frac14;磅沙包<br />\r\n* 加小號： 2個 &frac12;磅 及 2個&frac14;磅沙包<br />\r\n<br />\r\n【購買前先量度肩膊到腰(長)x圍繞胸口一周(寬)尺寸】<br />\r\n加小碼 14寸長x24寸寬<br />\r\n小碼&nbsp; 17寸長x30寸寬<br />\r\n中碼&nbsp; 20寸長x36寸寬<br />\r\n大碼&nbsp; 24寸長x42寸寬</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 如果沒有完美吻合的尺寸，建議買大一個尺寸，收緊時，最多可以減5寸。請在預訂前仔細量度尺寸！因衛生問題也不設退換其他尺寸。</p>\r\n', '<p>Special Supplies Compression Vest provides proprioceptive input which allows children to calm down and become more focused and relaxed. Weight of the vest is adjustable by adding or removing a &frac12; or &frac14; lbs sandbag. The vest is made of breathable and flexible neoprene which offers good support at the sides and shoulder. Ideal in maintaining an upright sitting position can be&nbsp; used in doing different activities. Machine washable.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Large, Medium, Small: 2 x &frac12;lb and 4 x &frac14;lb sandbags</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Extra Small: 2 x &frac12;lb and 2 x &frac14;lb sandbags</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please measure from shoulder to waist (length) x around the chest (width) before purchase</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Extra small 14&quot; long x 24&quot; wide</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Small 17&quot; long x 30&quot; wide</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Medium 20&quot; long x 36&quot; wide</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Large 24&quot; long x 42&quot; wide</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please go with the larger size when in doubt as the vest can be adjusted to 5&rsquo;&rsquo;smaller than the chest size listed above. Please measure accurately for the correct size before purchase. Not exchangeable due to hygienic reasons</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/241_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/241_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/241_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 19:04:49', '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
