(242, 17, 0, 'TA31', '70', 'Bunchems 蓬蓬球單色筒', 'Bunchems Cone', '25.00', 5.00, '<p>蓬蓬球上有很多軟身倒鈎，可以互相黏在一起，隨意變換創造出不同圖案。不會黏手，卻能提供豐富的觸感刺激。組裝過程，也可以訓練手眼協調，手指靈活性及手指力量。蓬蓬球可以黏到魔術貼的毛毛表面及絲巾上，有配合不同訓練的玩法。也可以做成不同大小的球，玩各類拋接遊戲。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>注意: 需要在成人監督下使用。不要靠近頭髮！！！！！ 如果小朋友有長頭髮的話，請先束起頭髮。如不慎被纏繞到頭髮，請在頭髮上塗抹潤髮乳/植物油/髮油，待頭髮變得足夠潤滑後，再慢慢取出。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式： 紅/綠/藍/紫（隨機發放一款）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童（請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>Each Bunchem ball has flexible ft hooks that allow them to stick to one another without the use of glue. Provide endless possibilities for kids to build while providing rich tactile stimulation. It can also provide training on hand-eye coordination, finger dexterity and finger strength. It can also be attached to Velcro or silk scarves for a variety of training purposes. It can also be made into different sizes of balls for different kinds of throwing and catching games.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Note: Adult supervision is required. Keep away from hair ！！！！！Please tie the hair up if your child has long hair. Apply hair conditioner/vegetable oil/hair oil to hair and wait until hair is sufficiently moisturized to slowly remove bunchems out of hair if they tangled with hair.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style: red/green/blue/purple (Colour will vary and picked at random at point of despatch)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 3 years and above (please use under parental supervision to avoid choking risk)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/242_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 19:05:39', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(243, 17, 0, 'PF4A', '265', 'Playfoam動物學習套裝小盒', 'Playfoam Shape learning Set (Animals style)', '78.00', 22.75, '<p>Educational Insight出品的 Playfoam 形狀學習套裝，每款包括2塊彩色泡泡棉磚 、13 張雙面彩色卡片，可重複使用。孩子可以將泡泡棉放在卡紙上練習用來學習數字/數數/字母/動物。另外，可以按著需要和興趣捏成不同的形狀，發揮創意。台灣製造柔軟無毒的泡泡棉物料，不粘手，可以隨身攜帶。提供豐富的觸覺感覺刺激，幫助發展精細的小肌肉技巧。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式：數字/數數/字母/動物&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童（幼兒請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n', '<p>Educational Insight Playfoam Shape Learning Set, each set includes,<br />\r\n1. 2 pieces of colourful playfoam bricks<br />\r\n2. 3 double-sided cards</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Children can learn numbers/counting/letters/animals by placing the foam on the cardboards. They can squeeze playfoam into different shapes according to their needs and interests. Made in Taiwan, the soft, non-toxic material is non-stick and can be carried around. Provides rich tactile stimulation to help develop fine smotor skills and learn the correct way to form letters. Is recommended to store in an airtight box to avoid drying out once opened</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style: numbers/counting/letters/animals&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above (for young children, please use under parental supervision to choking risk )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/243_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/243_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/243_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 19:05:39', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(244, 15, 0, 'WB15S', '0', '重力緊身背心 (S) ', 'Compression Vest (S)', '720.00', 447.00, '<p>Special Supplies 重力緊身背心提供充分的本體覺刺激，讓孩子可以冷靜，減少多動/活躍及焦慮情緒，變得更專注、平靜和放鬆。背心重量可以隨個人需要調節，添加或移除 &frac12; 或 &frac14; 磅小沙包*。背心柔軟、透氣、專為舒適地包覆肩膀和身體中部而設計，有良好的支撐性協助保持直立坐姿，適合活動/安坐時穿著，在任何地方都可以穿着。可用洗衣機清洗。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* 大號,中號,小號： 2個 &frac12;磅 及 4個&frac14;磅沙包<br />\r\n* 加小號： 2個 &frac12;磅 及 2個&frac14;磅沙包<br />\r\n<br />\r\n【購買前先量度肩膊到腰(長)x圍繞胸口一周(寬)尺寸】<br />\r\n加小碼 14寸長x24寸寬<br />\r\n小碼&nbsp; 17寸長x30寸寬<br />\r\n中碼&nbsp; 20寸長x36寸寬<br />\r\n大碼&nbsp; 24寸長x42寸寬</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 如果沒有完美吻合的尺寸，建議買大一個尺寸，收緊時，最多可以減5寸。請在預訂前仔細量度尺寸！因衛生問題也不設退換其他尺寸。</p>\r\n', '<p>Special Supplies Compression Vest provides proprioceptive input which allows children to calm down and become more focused and relaxed. Weight of the vest is adjustable by adding or removing a &frac12; or &frac14; lbs sandbag. The vest is made of breathable and flexible neoprene which offers good support at the sides and shoulder. Ideal in maintaining an upright sitting position can be&nbsp; used in doing different activities. Machine washable.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Large, Medium, Small: 2 x &frac12;lb and 4 x &frac14;lb sandbags</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Extra Small: 2 x &frac12;lb and 2 x &frac14;lb sandbags</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please measure from shoulder to waist (length) x around the chest (width) before purchase</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Extra small 14&quot; long x 24&quot; wide</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Small 17&quot; long x 30&quot; wide</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Medium 20&quot; long x 36&quot; wide</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Large 24&quot; long x 42&quot; wide</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please go with the larger size when in doubt as the vest can be adjusted to 5&rsquo;&rsquo;smaller than the chest size listed above. Please measure accurately for the correct size before purchase. Not exchangeable due to hygienic reasons.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/244_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 19:05:42', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(245, 15, 0, 'WB15L', '0', '重力緊身背心 (L) ', 'Compression Vest (L)', '720.00', 447.00, '<p>Special Supplies 重力緊身背心提供充分的本體覺刺激，讓孩子可以冷靜，減少多動/活躍及焦慮情緒，變得更專注、平靜和放鬆。背心重量可以隨個人需要調節，添加或移除 &frac12; 或 &frac14; 磅小沙包*。背心柔軟、透氣、專為舒適地包覆肩膀和身體中部而設計，有良好的支撐性協助保持直立坐姿，適合活動/安坐時穿著，在任何地方都可以穿着。可用洗衣機清洗。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* 大號,中號,小號： 2個 &frac12;磅 及 4個&frac14;磅沙包<br />\r\n* 加小號： 2個 &frac12;磅 及 2個&frac14;磅沙包<br />\r\n<br />\r\n【購買前先量度肩膊到腰(長)x圍繞胸口一周(寬)尺寸】<br />\r\n加小碼 14寸長x24寸寬<br />\r\n小碼&nbsp; 17寸長x30寸寬<br />\r\n中碼&nbsp; 20寸長x36寸寬<br />\r\n大碼&nbsp; 24寸長x42寸寬</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 如果沒有完美吻合的尺寸，建議買大一個尺寸，收緊時，最多可以減5寸。請在預訂前仔細量度尺寸！因衛生問題也不設退換其他尺寸。</p>\r\n', '<p>Special Supplies Compression Vest provides proprioceptive input which allows children to calm down and become more focused and relaxed. Weight of the vest is adjustable by adding or removing a &frac12; or &frac14; lbs sandbag. The vest is made of breathable and flexible neoprene which offers good support at the sides and shoulder. Ideal in maintaining an upright sitting position can be&nbsp; used in doing different activities. Machine washable.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Large, Medium, Small: 2 x &frac12;lb and 4 x &frac14;lb sandbags</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Extra Small: 2 x &frac12;lb and 2 x &frac14;lb sandbags</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please measure from shoulder to waist (length) x around the chest (width) before purchase</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Extra small 14&quot; long x 24&quot; wide</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Small 17&quot; long x 30&quot; wide</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Medium 20&quot; long x 36&quot; wide</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Large 24&quot; long x 42&quot; wide</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please go with the larger size when in doubt as the vest can be adjusted to 5&rsquo;&rsquo;smaller than the chest size listed above. Please measure accurately for the correct size before purchase. Not exchangeable due to hygienic reasons</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/245_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/245_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/245_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 19:06:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(246, 17, 0, 'TA35', '10', 'Wikki Stix蠟繩包8條', 'Wikki Stix pack', '15.00', 1.86, '<p>每個WikkiStix 蠟繩包包括：<br />\r\n1. 4種顏色，共8條 15cm 的蠟繩<br />\r\n2. 連線遊戲活動紙</p>\r\n\r\n<p>美國製造的蠟繩安全無毒，符合兒童安全法規。打了蠟的紗線，只要用手指輕輕按壓，就可以粘在光滑的表面上或互相黏合，沒有漿糊膠水，非常整潔。可以做成各種2D，3D的造型，也可以拼砌出不同字母字詞。除了提供觸感刺激，訓練雙手協調和手指靈活性外，同時學習寫前和書寫技巧。是可以讓孩子專心地忙碌一陣子的小遊戲！</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款色：一包/十包 （蠟繩顏色隨機）<br />\r\n<br />\r\n建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童（請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n', '<p>A great little game to keep your child occupied for a while!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Each WikkiStix Wax Pack includes :<br />\r\n1. Eight WikkiStix in 4 colours （15cm）<br />\r\n2. Joining dots activity game sheets</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wikki Stix are made of hand-knitting yarn enhanced with a microcrystalline, food-grade non-toxic wax and made in the USA which conforms to child safety standards. Just press them down with light fingertip pressure on any smooth surface and they will stick to each other without using any glue. They can be used in making different 2D or 3D patterns. They are perfect for training bilateral hand or eye-hand coordination and finger dexterity apart from providing tactile stimulation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colour: 1 pack / 10 packs (random colours of wax string)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 3 years and above (please use under parental supervision to avoid choking risk)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/246_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/246_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/246_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 19:07:57', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(247, 15, 0, 'WBB3', '1450', '3磅重力被', '3lb Weighted Blanket', '458.00', 237.80, '<p>重力毯採用深層壓力刺激療法的原理，讓有需要的兒童，特別是受感統失調影響的兒童使用，能夠提供本體感覺，有效達致舒緩情緒，冷靜作用。可作被子/加重膝墊使用，協助提升睡眠質素/安坐能力。由超柔軟的稀薄材料製成，透氣且容易清洗。較小的方形設計和精細的縫製可防止重量轉移和重量珠子漏出，確保在使用時壓力均勻分佈。使用者可能需要約7-10日時間才能適應壓力。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n尺寸 20x23寸; 重量 : 3lb<br />\r\n<br />\r\n建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童 (19-40磅)<br />\r\n(以體重約10%的磅數來選擇重力墊)</p>\r\n', '<p>Weighted blanket makes use of the benefits of weighted therapy to provide proprioceptive input for children, in particular offer a claming effect for those with sensory processing disorders. It can be used as a blanket or put on the lap to enhance attention while sitting or sleeping quality. Made from ultra-soft material which is breathable and easy to clean.&nbsp; Square design with fine stitching ensuring even distribution of pressure and leakage of weighted beads. It may take approximately 7-10 days for the user to adjust to the pressure.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size 20x23&quot;; Weight : 3lb</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age : Children 3 years old and above (19-40lbs) (approx 10% of the user&rsquo;s body weight)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/247_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/247_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/247_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 19:08:27', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(248, 1, 0, 'TA35S', '100', 'Wikki Stix蠟繩包8條 (10件)', 'Wikki Stix packs (a set of 10)', '98.00', 18.56, '<p>每個WikkiStix 蠟繩包包括：<br />\r\n1. 4種顏色，共8條 15cm 的蠟繩<br />\r\n2. 連線遊戲活動紙</p>\r\n\r\n<p>美國製造的蠟繩安全無毒，符合兒童安全法規。打了蠟的紗線，只要用手指輕輕按壓，就可以粘在光滑的表面上或互相黏合，沒有漿糊膠水，非常整潔。可以做成各種2D，3D的造型，也可以拼砌出不同字母字詞。除了提供觸感刺激，訓練雙手協調和手指靈活性外，同時學習寫前和書寫技巧。是可以讓孩子專心地忙碌一陣子的小遊戲！</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款色：一包/十包 （蠟繩顏色隨機）<br />\r\n<br />\r\n建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童（請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n', '<p>A great little game to keep your child occupied for a while!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Each WikkiStix Wax Pack includes :<br />\r\n1. Eight WikkiStix in 4 colours （15cm）<br />\r\n2. Joining dots activity game sheets</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wikki Stix are made of hand-knitting yarn enhanced with a microcrystalline, food-grade non-toxic wax and made in the USA which conforms to child safety standards. Just press them down with light fingertip pressure on any smooth surface and they will stick to each other without using any glue. They can be used in making different 2D or 3D patterns. They are perfect for training bilateral hand or eye-hand coordination and finger dexterity apart from providing tactile stimulation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colour: 1 pack / 10 packs (random colours of wax string)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 3 years and above (please use under parental supervision to avoid choking risk)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/248_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/248_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/248_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 19:08:33', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(249, 17, 0, 'PF4C', '265', 'Playfoam計數學習套裝小盒', 'Playfoam Shape learning Set (Number style)', '78.00', 22.75, '<p>Educational Insight出品的 Playfoam 形狀學習套裝，每款包括2塊彩色泡泡棉磚 、13 張雙面彩色卡片，可重複使用。孩子可以將泡泡棉放在卡紙上練習用來學習數字/數數/字母/動物。另外，可以按著需要和興趣捏成不同的形狀，發揮創意。台灣製造柔軟無毒的泡泡棉物料，不粘手，可以隨身攜帶。提供豐富的觸覺感覺刺激，幫助發展精細的小肌肉技巧。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式：數字/數數/字母/動物&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童（幼兒請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n', '<p>Educational Insight Playfoam Shape Learning Set, each set includes,<br />\r\n1. 2 pieces of colourful playfoam bricks<br />\r\n2. 3 double-sided cards</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Children can learn numbers/counting/letters/animals by placing the foam on the cardboards. They can squeeze playfoam into different shapes according to their needs and interests. Made in Taiwan, the soft, non-toxic material is non-stick and can be carried around. Provides rich tactile stimulation to help develop fine smotor skills and learn the correct way to form letters. Is recommended to store in an airtight box to avoid drying out once opened</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style: numbers/counting/letters/animals&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above (for young children, please use under parental supervision to choking risk )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/249_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/249_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/249_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 19:09:47', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(250, 17, 0, 'TA40S', '40', '魔法白雪 (32g)', 'Magic Snow Powder (32g)', '48.00', 19.68, '<p>SnowWonder 品牌人造雪由美國製造，未使用中國聚合物，安全無毒。在雪粉中加入水，立即會膨脹爆發，非常柔軟，視乎濕度可以持續數天或數週。適合全年使用的玩雪觸感活動 ！！&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>重量：小包雪粉約重32g ； 大包雪粉約重75g</p>\r\n\r\n<p>使用方法：<br />\r\n32g 雪粉可加入約1.25公升水 ---&gt; 1 加侖的白雪 (20cm直徑x6cm厚)<br />\r\n75g雪粉可以加入約2.5公升水 ---&gt; 2加侖的白雪&nbsp; (40cm直徑x6cm厚)<br />\r\n* 加入冷水，有冰涼的感覺～<br />\r\n* 參考以上比例做出的白雪比較鬆散；如想要用雪造型，需要加入更多的水，讓雪呈現半透明形狀，會更易捏成不同造型</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童（請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>SnowWonder artificial snow is made in the USA without the use of Chinese polymers. Safe and non-toxic. When water is added to the snow powder, it immediately expands and explodes. Soft snow is an ideal tactile game to play year-round.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Weight:<br />\r\nSmall packet weights approximately 32g;<br />\r\nLarge packet weights approximately 75g</p>\r\n\r\n<p>How to use:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>32g of snow powder can be added to approx. 1.25 litres of water ---&gt; 1 gallon of snow (20cm diameter x 6cm thick)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>75g of snow powder can be added to approx. 2.5 litres of water ---&gt; 2 gallons of snow (40cm diameter x 6cm thick)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Add cold water for a cold sensation<br />\r\n* If you want to shape the snow, you need to add more water to make it translucent. That will be easier to make different shapes.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 3 years and above (please use under parental supervision to avoid choking risk)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/250_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/250_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/250_3.jpg,assets/products_image/650/250_4.jpg,assets/products_image/650/250_5.jpg,assets/products_image/650/250_6.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 19:10:02', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(251, 15, 0, 'WBB5', '2000', '5磅重力被', '5lb Weighted Blanket', '488.00', 206.70, '<p>加重毛毯由100％的棉質材料製成，質料柔軟親膚。較小的方形設計和精細的縫製可防止重量轉移和橡皮珠子漏出，確保在使用時壓力均勻分佈。重力毯提供豐富的深層壓力刺激，重力的感覺能有效提供豐富的本體感覺，能夠讓受感統失調影響的兒童提昇安坐能力，提昇睡眠質素。除了睡覺之外，還可以覆蓋在膝蓋或肩膀上，用於沙發休息、工作、學習、閱讀等等，能帶來舒適的感覺。手洗更耐用。使用者可能需要約7-10日時間才能適應壓力。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸36x48寸; 重量 : 5lb</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：5歲以上兒童 (40-60磅)<br />\r\n(以體重約10%的磅數來選擇重力墊)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>This weighted blanket is made from 100% cotton which is soft to skin. The square design with fine stitching ensures even distribution of pressure and prevent leakage of weighted beads. It provides proprioceptive input for children, in particular offering a calming effect for those with sensory processing disorders. It can be used as a blanket or put on the lap to enhance attention while sitting or sleeping quality. Hand washable.&nbsp; It may take approximately 7-10 days for the user to adjust to the pressure.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size 36x48&quot;; Weight : 5lb</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age : Children 5 years old and above (40-60lbs) (approx 10% of the user&rsquo;s body weight)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/251_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/251_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 19:10:15', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
