(254, 15, 0, 'WBB7', '3160', '7磅重力被', '7lb Weighted Blanket', '488.00', 296.00, '<p>這款7磅壓力被，採用2合1雙面設計。絲滑柔軟的水晶天鵝絨比普通毯子更柔軟，另一邊貂毛的凹陷點加強觸感刺激，提升安全感，達到放鬆冷靜的效果。重力毯提供豐富的深層壓力刺激，重力的感覺能有效提供豐富的本體感覺，能夠讓受感統失調影響的兒童提昇安坐能力，提昇睡眠質素。除了睡覺之外，還可以覆蓋在膝蓋或肩膀上，用於沙發休息、工作、學習、閱讀等等，能帶來舒適的感覺。毯子可愛透氣，適合四季使用。7層堅固的結構，以較小的口袋和雙針縫合，可以均勻分散玻璃珠，防止溢出，承受日常使用的皺褶。可機洗，低溫烘乾，不可熨燙。使用者可能需要約7-10日時間才能適應壓力。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸40x61寸; 重量 : 7lb</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：6歲以上兒童 (60-80磅)<br />\r\n(以體重約10%的磅數來選擇重力墊)&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>This 7lb weighted blanket features a 2-in-1 reversible design. Made from smooth and silky velvet which is softer than a normal blanket and the dimples on the other side can provide tactile stimulation to children. It provides proprioceptive input for children, in particular offering a calming effect for those with sensory processing disorders. It can be used as a blanket or put on different body parts to enhance attention while sitting or sleeping quality. It is made of breathable material which is ideal to be used in all seasons. Machine washable, tumble dry on low heat, not ironable. It may take approximately 7-10 days for the user to adjust to the pressure.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size 40x61&quot;; Weight : 7lb</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age : Children aged 6 and above (60-80lb)&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(approx 10% of the user&rsquo;s body weight)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/254_1.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 19:11:37', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(255, 17, 0, 'PF4E', '265', 'Playfoam英文字學習套裝小盒', 'Playfoam Shape learning Set (Letters style)', '78.00', 22.75, '<p>Educational Insight出品的 Playfoam 形狀學習套裝，每款包括2塊彩色泡泡棉磚 、13 張雙面彩色卡片，可重複使用。孩子可以將泡泡棉放在卡紙上練習用來學習數字/數數/字母/動物。另外，可以按著需要和興趣捏成不同的形狀，發揮創意。台灣製造柔軟無毒的泡泡棉物料，不粘手，可以隨身攜帶。提供豐富的觸覺感覺刺激，幫助發展精細的小肌肉技巧。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>款式：數字/數數/字母/動物&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童（幼兒請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n', '<p>Educational Insight Playfoam Shape Learning Set, each set includes,<br />\r\n1. 2 pieces of colourful playfoam bricks<br />\r\n2. 3 double-sided cards</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Children can learn numbers/counting/letters/animals by placing the foam on the cardboards. They can squeeze playfoam into different shapes according to their needs and interests. Made in Taiwan, the soft, non-toxic material is non-stick and can be carried around. Provides rich tactile stimulation to help develop fine smotor skills and learn the correct way to form letters. Is recommended to store in an airtight box to avoid drying out once opened</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Style: numbers/counting/letters/animals&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above (for young children, please use under parental supervision to choking risk )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/255_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/255_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/255_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 19:13:18', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(256, 17, 0, 'TA49', '385', '顏色和形狀感官墊', 'Color and Shape Pad', '288.00', 136.00, '<p>顏色和形狀感官墊能提供豐富的觸覺和視覺刺激，鼓勵感官探索，同時訓練手眼協調及增強精細運動技能。把自己選擇的液體，例如水、凝膠、刮鬍膏、甘油等&hellip;從閥門注入感官墊，然後讓孩子們用手指引導形狀，完成8 張雙面活動卡上的遊戲。套裝包括 4 種不同的形狀，有圓形、方形、矩形和三角形，每一種圖形有 6 種不同顏色。可更換液體重複使用。&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>感官墊同時是一張加重墊，可放置在孩子的膝蓋上，提供本體覺刺激，幫助孩子平靜下來，緩解焦慮及提升專注力。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n商品尺寸：12 x 9.65 x 1.5 吋<br />\r\n重量：370g</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>The colour and shape sensory mats provide rich tactile and visual stimulation to encourage sensory exploration, while training eye-hand coordination and enhancing fine motor skills. Fill the sensory mat with a liquid of your own&nbsp; choice, such as water, gel, shaving cream, glycerine, etc... through the valve and let the children guide the shapes with their hands to complete the game on the 8 double-sided activity cards. The set includes 4 different shapes - round, square, rectangle and triangle. Each shape comes in 6 different colours. The liquid can be changed and the activity set can be reused.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The sensory pad is also a weighted pad that can be placed on the child&#39;s lap to provide proprioceptive stimulation to help child calm down, relieve anxiety and improve concentration.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Product size: 12 x 9.65 x 1.5 inches<br />\r\nWeight: 370g</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/256_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/256_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/256_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 19:13:57', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(257, 17, 0, 'PF3', '470', 'Playfoam數數學習套裝大盒', '\"Playfoam Shape and Counting set\"', '218.00', 76.00, '<p>Educational Insight出品的 Playfoam 形狀和學習計數套裝，包括8塊彩色泡泡棉磚 、10 張雙面數字閃卡和 3 張額外彩色卡片，可重複使用。孩子可以將泡泡棉放在卡紙上練習用來學習數數， 尤其適合有數數/抽象邏輯思考困難的幼兒。 另外，可以按著需要和興趣捏成不同的形狀，發揮創意。台灣製造柔軟無毒的泡泡棉物料，不粘手，可以隨身攜帶。提供豐富的觸覺感覺刺激，幫助發展精細的小肌肉技巧。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童（幼兒請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n', '<p>Educational Insight Playfoam Shape and Learn Counting Set includes:<br />\r\n1.&nbsp; 8 pieces of colourful playfoam bricks<br />\r\n2. 10 double-sided number flashcards<br />\r\n3. 3 extra colourful game cards</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Children can place the foam on the cardboards and practice shaping the letters according to the direction of the strokes. They can squeeze playfoam into different shapes according to their needs and interests. Made in Taiwan, the soft, non-toxic material is non-stick and can be carried around. Provides rich tactile stimulation to help develop fine smotor skills and learn the correct way to form letters. Is recommended to store in an airtight box to avoid drying out once opened</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above (for young children, please use under parental supervision to choking risk )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/257_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/257_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/257_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 19:14:45', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(258, 17, 0, 'PF2', '440', 'Playfoam英文字學習套裝大盒', 'Playfoam Alphabets set', '218.00', 119.17, '<p>Educational Insight出品的 Playfoam字母學習套裝，包括8塊彩色泡泡棉磚塊和13張印有字母的雙面卡片。孩子可以將泡泡棉放在卡紙上練習根據筆畫方向塑造出不同字母，也可以按著需要和興趣捏成不同的形狀。台灣製造，柔軟無毒的泡泡棉物料，不粘手，可以隨身攜帶。提供豐富的觸覺感覺刺激，幫助發展精細的小肌肉技巧，並學習正確的字母形成方法。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童（幼兒請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n', '<p>Educational Insight Playfoam Alphabet Learning Set includes:<br />\r\n1. 8 pieces of colourful playfoam bricks<br />\r\n2. 13 double-sided letter cards</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Children can place the foam on the cardboards and practice shaping the letters according to the direction of the strokes. They can squeeze playfoam into different shapes according to their needs and interests. Made in Taiwan, the soft, non-toxic material is non-stick and can be carried around. Provides rich tactile stimulation to help develop fine smotor skills and learn the correct way to form letters. Is recommended to store in an airtight box to avoid drying out once opened.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above (for young children, please use under parental supervision to choking risk )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/258_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/258_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/258_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 19:16:12', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(259, 17, 0, 'TA51', '1200', '觸感分辨圈圈矽膠地墊', 'TickiT Silishapes set', '880.00', 434.70, '<p>TickiT Silishapes 觸感圈圈套裝有5個小圓墊，5個大圓墊，可提供觸感刺激及訓練觸感分辨能力，更可用作踏步墊或坐墊，適合室內或室外使用。 經久耐用的防滑矽膠圈，可以用肥皂和水輕鬆清潔。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸：大圓墊 （25cm直徑）/小圓墊 （8cm直徑）<br />\r\n產品重量：大約1.2kg</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>The TickiT Silishapes set comes with 5 small and 5 large mats. Children can step or sit on the mats for tactile stimulation and tactile discriminating training. The durable, non-slip silicone mats can be easily cleaned with soap and water. Suitable for indoor or outdoor uses.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: Large round mat (25cm diameter) / Small round mat (8cm diameter)<br />\r\nProduct weight: approx. 1.2kg</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/259_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/259_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 19:17:47', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(260, 17, 0, 'PF1', '30', 'Playfoam單色球', 'Playfoam', '48.00', 9.58, '<p>Educational Insights 的泡泡棉玩具，台灣製造，柔軟無毒。可以自由地壓扁，擠壓和塑造成不同的形狀，按著需要和興趣發揮創意。泡泡棉物料不粘手，可以隨身攜帶。提供豐富的觸覺感覺刺激，幫助發展精細的小肌肉技巧。開封後建議使用密封盒收納避免乾燥。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>顏色：藍色/紫色/橙色/綠色&nbsp; （隨機發放一款）<br />\r\n包裝重量：31g</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童（幼兒請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n', '<p>- Educational Insights brand of playfoam is made in Taiwan<br />\r\n- Soft and non-toxic<br />\r\n- Non-stick and can be carried around<br />\r\n- Can be flattened, squeezed and molded into different shapes to suit different needs and interests<br />\r\n- Provide rich tactile stimulation inputs<br />\r\n- Help develop fine motor and pre-writing skills<br />\r\n- Is recommended to store in an airtight box to avoid drying out once opened</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colours: Blue/Purple/Orange/Green (randomly distributed)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Package weight: 31g</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above (for young children, please use under parental supervision to choking risk )</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/260_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/260_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/260_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 19:18:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(261, 17, 0, 'TA52', '630', '觸感分辨遊戲板', 'Touch & Match Board', '350.00', 200.17, '<p>木板有12 種顏色和紋理，可以讓孩子配對出一樣顏色或質地的木頭。<br />\r\n挑戰蒙著眼睛玩加強觸感分辨能力。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>尺寸: 為 22cm 長 X 17cm寬 x3.5深。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>The game board comes in 12 different&nbsp; colours and textures. Children need to match the same colour/ texture of the wooden pieces with the board.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Try to challenge the child by playing blindfolded to enhance tactile differentiation!&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 22cm long x 17cm wide x 3.5 deep.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: 3 years old and above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/261_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/261_2.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 19:18:40', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(262, 17, 0, 'TAK1', '1010', '動力沙1kg', 'Kinetic sand 1KG', '228.00', 104.57, '<p>動力沙由無毒安全的天然沙製成，於瑞士生產，經測試顯示低致敏性，不含小麥、麩質和酪蛋白。把動力沙放在雙手感受它的流動，提供豐富的觸感刺激。 配合其他模具，透過堆砌及擠壓動力沙,，發揮小創意，創造出不同的藝術品。把沙子鋪平在盤子上畫寫，利用多感官學習法增強記憶。不會黏手，容易清潔，不會變乾，可以重複使用。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>包裝尺寸：6.3cmx9.1cmx18.8；重量：1kg</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童（請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>- Made from non-toxic and safe natural sand<br />\r\n- Made in Switzerland<br />\r\n- Hypoallergenic. Wheat, gluten and casein free<br />\r\n- Provide rich tactile stimulation<br />\r\n- Stack and squeeze the sand to create different artworks<br />\r\n- Lay the sand flat and write on it to enhance memory using a multi-sensory<br />\r\nlearning method.<br />\r\n- Non-sticky, easy to clean, does not dry out and can be used again and again.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Package size: 6.3cmx9.1cmx18.8; Weight: 1kg</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 3 years and above (please use under parental supervision to avoid choking risk)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/262_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/262_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/262_3.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 19:19:40', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(263, 17, 0, 'TAK2', '575', '動力沙沙灘套裝', 'Kinetic Sand Beach Set', '218.00', 93.87, '<p>沙灘體驗套裝，讓孩子足不出戶卻親臨了沙灘一樣！</p>\r\n\r\n<p>動力沙由無毒安全的天然沙製成,，於瑞士生產，經測試顯示低致敏性，不含小麥、麩質和酪蛋白。把動力沙放在雙手感受它的流動，提供豐富的觸感刺激。配合其他模具，透過堆砌及擠壓動力沙，發揮小創意，創造出不同的藝術品。把沙子鋪平在盤子上畫寫，利用多感官學習法增強記憶。不會黏手，容易清潔，不會變乾，可以重複使用。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>套裝包括：<br />\r\n1. 12oz動力沙<br />\r\n2. 五個城堡模具<br />\r\n3. 四個沙耙工具<br />\r\n4. 收納盒子</p>\r\n\r\n<p>建議使用年齡：3歲以上兒童（請在家長監督下使用，避免吞食）</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>The Beach Experience Kit brings children to the beach without leaving home!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Made from non-toxic and safe natural sand<br />\r\n- Made in Switzerland<br />\r\n- Hypoallergenic. Wheat, gluten and casein free<br />\r\n- Provide rich tactile stimulation<br />\r\n- Stack and squeeze the sand to create different artworks<br />\r\n- Lay the sand flat and write on it to enhance memory using a multi-sensory<br />\r\nlearning method.<br />\r\n- Non-sticky, easy to clean, does not dry out and can be used again and again.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Set includes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. 12oz kinectic sand<br />\r\n2. Five x castle molds<br />\r\n3. Four x sand raking tools<br />\r\n4. Storage box</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended age: children aged 3 years and above (please use under parental supervision to avoid choking risk)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'assets/products_image/650/263_1.jpg,assets/products_image/650/263_2.jpg,assets/products_image/650/263_3.jpg,assets/products_image/650/263_4.jpg', 1, '2023-04-16 19:20:21', '0000-00-00 00:00:00');

